description.en: Simply designed and super convenient for hot drinks, the TMAX coffee mug is ideal for use at home, work or coffee shops. Inspired by the new TMAX scooter that reshapes urban travel, this mug features a cool black body and removable lid, with a black silicone sleeve grip to protect the hands and make carrying easy. White Yamaha and ‘Nothing but the Max’ logos on the body and sleeve give an understated and striking identity.
description.sl-SI: Skodelica za kavo TMAX je preprosto zasnovana in izredno priročna za uživanje v toplih napitkih doma, v službi ali v kavarnah. Navdih za skodelico je skuter TMAX, ki spreminja koncept urbane vožnje, zato ima eleganten črn lonček, odstranljiv pokrovček in silikonsko držalo za zaščito rok ter enostavno prenašanje. Bela logotipa Yamaha in ‘Nothing but the Max’ na lončku in držalu poskrbita za nezamenljivo prepoznavnost na nevsiljiv način.

description.en: With its 3-wheel layout, the Tricity 300 gives a new feeling of stability and confidence, making it an ideal vehicle for all year riding, even with cold and bad weather. So now you’ve got a scooter that you can use in a range of conditions, we thought we’d create the Winter Pack featuring a water-resistant apron as well as a grip heater. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your Tricity 300.

description.en: The Adventure riding jacket and pants are available as a set and can be zipped together. The set is available in a version for men and women. Designed for long distance riding comfort with high level of protection. The set has removable thermal lining and fixed waterproof lining that give all-weather flexibility. The fabric is a mix of polyester, polyamide, polyurethane and nylon. The jacket has 6 exterior and 4 interior pockets. The pants have 2 cargo pockets. This Adventure set is built to handle the longest and toughest rides.

Tkanina je mešanica poliestra, poliamida, poliuretana in najlona. Jakna ima 6 zunanjih in 4 notranje žepe. Hlače imajo 2 velika žepa. Ta komplet Adventure je ustvarjen za najdaljše in najzahtevnejše vožnje.

But they are also in itself a great front end upgrade and option to improve responsiveness and performance of the fork. Öhlins offers a wide range of linear springs to suit each individual type of bike, rider weight and personal preferences for installation into the standard front fork.

Pametni telefon preprosto potisnite v etui, zavihajte odprtino in zaprite jeziček. Tako telefon ostane zaščiten pred dežjem, znojem, udom in prahom, hkrati pa še vedno omogoča enako uporabnost zaslona na dotik.
description.en: With the UNIVERSAL PHONE CASE, you can use just about any smartphone on any SP Connect mount to secure your phone to bicycles, cars, motorbikes, golf carts, etc. with its twist-lock mechanism to install. Simply push the smartphone into the case roll up the opening and close the tab. This way your phone remains protected from rain, sweat, ud, and dust, still offering the same touchscreen usability.

To je prava izbira, če iščete zamenjavo za tovarniško vgrajene drsnike, ostre drsnike za kompakten sneg ali drsnike za večjo varnost in vodljivost. So popolna rešitev za turne vožnje.

Whether looking for a replacement factory runner, a cutting edge in hard-packed snow and ice, or to improve safety & handling, this is the right option. They are perfect for trail touring.

A gritty urban look for the new generation of Hyper Naked rider.

name.sl-SI: Paket 'Sport Pack Pro Titanium' za MT-09

description.sl-SI: Vrhunski videz in zmogljivosti so za MT-09 standardne, zdaj pa ga lahko nadgradite s paketom 'Sport Pack Pro Titanium', ki je zasnovan tako, da bo vaš motocikel še bolj izstopal. Za dopolnitev hitre in vznemirljive izkušnje vožnje z modelom MT-09, titanov popolni izpušni sistem Akrapovič poudarja ikonično rjovenje agregata CP3 ter čisti adrenalin, ki ga doživljamo z vsakim zasukom plina. Skupaj z ogledali na krmilu v obliki romba, črno obarvanim kratkim vizirjem in elegantnim nosilcem registrske tablice ti skrbno izbrani dodatki izboljšajo agresiven in športen videz vašega motornega kolesa. Blazinice za rezervoar in stranski oprijem – zasnovane posebej za MT-09 – izboljšajo nadzor in stabilnost pri vožnji v ovinkih, hkrati pa ščitijo rezervoar pred praskami. Ste pripravljeni, da svojo vožnjo popeljete na naslednjo raven?
description.en: Class-leading looks and performance are standard on the MT-09, but now you can take it to the next level with the Sport Pack Pro Titanium, designed to make your bike stand out from the crowd even more. To complement the fast and thrilling experience of riding the MT-09, the titanium Akrapovič Full Exhaust System accentuates the CP3’s iconic roar, emphasising the pure adrenaline delivered with every twist of the throttle. Together with the diamond-shaped bar end mirrors, black-tinted fly screen and a sleek licence plate holder, these carefully selected accessories enhance your bike’s sharp and sporty looks. Finally, the tank pad and side grip pads—designed specifically for the MT-09—improve control and stability when tackling corners, while also protecting the tank from scratches. Are you ready to push your ride to the next level?

You may want to use your NMAX throughout the year for your commutes. And we want to make sure you ride with utmost comfort, which not only makes your ride pleasurable but also a whole lot more comfortable. In order to keep you protected from the elements, we created the Winter pack for NMAX, consisting of an apron and a grip heater. While the Apron protects your feet from the rain and cold winds, it also has a reflective logo that increases your visibility. The grip heater get plenty warm, to keep your hands toasty. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your NMAX.
description.sl-SI: Mogoče se boste želeli s svojim NMAX voziti celo leto. Želimo poskrbeti, da se boste vozili kar se da udobno, zaradi česar ne bo vožnja le v užitek, ampak bo tudi precej bolj udobna. Da bi vas zaščitili pred vremenom, smo ustvarili zimski paket za NMAX, ki je sestavljen iz predpasnika in grelnika ročk. Predpasnik ščiti noge pred dežjem in hladnim vetrom ter je opremljen z odsevnim logotipom, zaradi katerega boste bolj opazni. Grelnik ročk pa se segreje in poskrbi, da so roke tople. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš model NMAX.

Posebni gel prodre naravnost v blato in umazanijo ter ju nežno sprosti, zaradi česar kolo enostavno sperete. S posebno mešanico so vse površine bleščeče obdelane in brez ostankov, vključno z ogljikom – zasnova, prijazna oblogi, ohranja zmogljivost zavor.

name.sl-SI: Dirkaški komplet GYTR® prve stopnje – modelno leto 2019–trenutni model

description.en:
The GYTR® Racing Kit stage 1 (MY19-Current) includes all mandatory equipment based on the FIA (Fédération Internationale de l’Automobile) T4 regulations for Side-by-Sides. Equipped with this kit, the YXZ1000R is ready to compete in most competitions under National Sports Authorities and FIM.
Thanks to the plug-and-play design, no welding or modifications to the chassis are required. Together with the full assembly instructions, this allows any Yamaha SSV dealer or experienced mechanic to finish installation in about 16 hours.
The GYTR Racing Kit opens up a new world of Rally racing and offers a strong base for further improving skills and vehicle performance, for entry-level and experienced drivers.
This Stage 1 kit is developed for models with a rear-mounted radiator and is suitable for YXZ1000R models after and including MY2019.

The kit contains:
description.sl-SI:
Dirkaški komplet GYTR® prve stopnje (modelno leto 2019–trenutni model) vključuje vso potrebno opremo na osnovi FIA (Fédération Internationale de l’Automobile) pogojev T4 za modele Side-by-Side. Model YXZ1000R, opremljen s tem kompletom, je pripravljen za tekmovanje v večini tekmovanj pod okriljem nacionalnih športnih organov in FIM.
Zahvaljujoč preprosti zasnovi ni potrebno varjenje ali izvajanje modifikacij na šasiji. V kompletu s popolnimi navodili za sestavljanje lahko vsak prodajalec Yamahe SSV ali izkušen mehanik zaključi namestitev v približno 16-ih urah.
Dirkaški komplet GYTR odpira nov svet reli dirkanja ter ponuja močno podlago za nadaljnje izboljšanje spretnosti in zmogljivosti vozila, tako začetnikom kot tudi izkušenim voznikom.
Ta komplet prve stopnje je razvit za modele z zadaj nameščenim hladilnikom in je primeren za YXZ1000R od vključno modelnega leta 2019 naprej.

description.en:
Chains live a tough, dangerous and extremely stressful life! Road dust, grit and debris cling to the chain lubricant, creating a deadly ‘grinding paste’ that can considerably reduce the life of both the chain and the drive sprockets.
This quick and effective spray removes the dirt and heavy grease deposits while still protecting the O-rings and fighting corrosion for the future, and remember, a clean chain is a smoother-running chain.
description.sl-SI:
Verige za časa svoje življenjske dobe delujejo v težkih, nevarnih in zelo stresnih okoliščinah. Cestni prah, pesek in ostanki, ki se držijo maziva za verige, ustvarijo smrtno nevarno »pasto za brušenje«, ki lahko znatno skrajša življenjsko dobo verige in pogonskih zobnikov.
To hitro in učinkovito pršilo odstrani umazanijo in večje obloge maščobe, pri tem pa vseeno ščiti O-tesnila in se bori proti koroziji. Ne pozabite, če je veriga čista, bolj gladko teče.

The city is the XMAX's natural habitat and with the Urban Accessories Pack you can take the practicality of your XMAX a notch higher. Besides providing enhanced wind protection from the high screen, the pack also takes care of your luggage needs with a 45L top case with matching colour plate set and carrier – keeping your belonging safe and secure. And a backrest for the top case makes sure the passenger has an equally comfortable ride. To protect you from the scratches and the scruffs, the city throws up, the pack contains the XMAX scratch protector. Available from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your XMAX.

description.en: The perfect tee for fans of the 6-time WorldSBK Champion, the Jonathan Rea Men’s T-Shirt is designed to help you show support for Jonny in his first season with Yamaha. Strong embroidered Yamaha branding on the chest, backstripe graphic and shoulder piping combine for an eye-catching REVS look.
Enhance the coolness of your Yamaha with this titanium slip-on muffler. It not only enhances the looks of the bike but also generates a performance increase.

By smoothing out the YZ250’s power delivery the GYTR® Heavy Flywheel delivers a less aggressive hit when you twist the throttle. Its increased inertia mass helps to keep momentum through corners and makes the bike more usable – especially in muddy and sandy conditions.

description.sl-SI:
Ohranite svojo naložbo v najboljšem stanju in jo zaščitit pred vremenskimi vplivi. 
Ta prevleka zagotavlja neprekosljivo zaščito pred bledenjem in posledicami vremenskih dejavnikov. Ima sistem Vacu-Hold za pripenjanje brez trakov, ki odpravlja napihovanje in plapolanje prevleke. Zato se popolnoma prilega obliki vašega WaveRunnerja. Poleg tega je zaskočni zatezni sistem Dual 304 iz nerjavnega jekla z enostavnim sproščanjem vnaprej pripravljen, da ga lahko po enostavni namestitvi takoj uporabite.
description.en:
Keep your investment looking its best, and protect it from the elements. 
This cover provides the ultimate protection against fading and the elements. It comes with the Vacu-Hold strapless tow system, eliminating billowing and buffeting. Therefore, the cover conforms to the shape of your WaveRunner. Moreover, the EZ Release Dual 304 Stainless Steel Ratchet Tightening System is pre-tensioned and ready to ratchet upon an easy installation.

name.sl-SI: Moški pulover s kapuco Hyper Naked

description.en: Slick and ready for the streets, the Hyper Naked hoodie for men is presented in stealth black with stunning cyan highlights in sync with the new MT machines. Constructed in an organic cotton and recycled polyester blend for maximum comfort, this hoodie features a large front panel printed with the iconic MT logo. Faded blue sleeve graphics give motion to the silhouette, with 3D DSOJ logos on the inner sleeve and side. A lined hood gives weather protection while a kangaroo pocket offers room for essentials. A staple piece for the urban explorer.
description.sl-SI: Moški pulover s kapuco Hyper Naked v nočno črni barvi ima vpadljive poudarke v cian modri, ki se skladajo z novimi motorji serije MT. Mešanica ekološko pridelanega bombaža in recikliranega poliestra zagotavlja maksimalno udobje. Na sprednji strani puloverja je velika grafika z ikoničnim logotipom MT. Bleda grafika na modrih rokavih daje puloverju specifično podobo, na notranjem rokavu in na strani pa sta 3D-logotipa DSOJ. Podložena kapuca nudi zaščito pred vremenskimi vplivi, velik sprednji žep pa zagotavlja prostor za najnujnejše. Obvezna oprema za urbanega raziskovalca.
V svoj TRACER 9 prinesite zaščito v pustolovskem slogu s robustnimi ščitniki motorja. Konstrukcija jeklenih cevi zagotavlja močan okvir, ki zmanjša poškodbe v primeru padca.
description.en: Bring adventure-style protection to your TRACER 9 with the sturdy Engine Guards. Steel tube construction delivers a strong frame that minimises damage in case of a fall.

description.sl-SI: Moška motoristična jakna kolekcije Hyper Naked, prežeta z duhom cestne vožnje, je prefinjen in privlačen izdelek v dveh odtenkih sive barve s poudarki v cian modri. Trpežen zunanji sloj iz poliestra in poliuretana ima ščitnike za ramena in komolce za brezskrbnost na cesti, z odsevnimi trakovi na rokah in snemljivo kapuco za dodatno vidljivost na cesti. Štirje zunanji in dva notranja žepa ponujajo dovolj prostora za bistvene stvari, medtem ko odstranljiva toplotna podloga z mrežico pod pazduho omogoča udobje v spreminjajočih se podnebjih. Prezračevalne zaplate omogočajo dodatno udobje na sedežu, natisnjeni logotipi Yamaha, MT in DSOJ pa krepko poudarijo urbani slog te privlačne jakne.
description.en: Infused with the street riding spirit, the Hyper Naked Men’s Riding Jacket is a subtle and striking item in two-tone grey with cyan highlights. A durable polyester-polyurethane shell features shoulder and elbow protectors for peace of mind on the road, with reflective strips on the arms and detachable hood for extra road visibility. Four outer and two inner pockets offer ample room for essentials, while the removable thermal lining with underarm mesh allows comfort in changing climates. Ventilation panels allow further comfort in the saddle, while printed Yamaha, MT and DSOJ logos add a flourish of urban style to this super-cool jacket.

name.sl-SI: Dirkalni komplet GYTR® prve stopnje – modelno leto 2016–2018

description.en:
The GYTR® Racing Kit Stage 1 (MY16-MY18) includes all mandatory equipment based on the FIA (Fédération Internationale de l’Automobile) T4 regulations for Side-by-Sides. Equipped with this kit, the YXZ1000R is ready to compete in most competitions under National Sports Authorities and FIM.
Thanks to the plug-and-play design, no welding or modifications to the chassis are required. Together with the full assembly instructions, this allows any Yamaha SSV dealer or experienced mechanic to finish installation in about 16 hours.
The GYTR Racing Kit opens up a new world of Rally racing and offers a strong base for further improving skills and vehicle performance, for entry-level and experienced drivers.
This Stage 1 kit is developed for models with a front-mounted radiator and is suitable for YXZ1000R models from MY2016 – MY2018.

This kit includes:
description.sl-SI:
Dirkaški komplet GYTR® prve stopnje (modelno leto 2016–2018) vključuje vso potrebno opremo na osnovi FIA (Fédération Internationale de l’Automobile) pogojev T4 za modele Side-by-Side. Model YXZ1000R, opremljen s tem kompletom, je pripravljen za tekmovanje v večini tekmovanj pod okriljem nacionalnih športnih organov in FIM.
Zahvaljujoč preprosti zasnovi ni potrebno varjenje ali izvajanje modifikacij na šasiji. V kompletu s popolnimi navodili za sestavljanje lahko vsak prodajalec Yamahe SSV ali izkušen mehanik zaključi namestitev v približno 16-ih urah.
Dirkaški komplet GYTR odpira nov svet reli dirkanja ter ponuja močno podlago za nadaljnje izboljšanje spretnosti in zmogljivosti vozila, tako začetnikom kot tudi izkušenim voznikom.
Ta komplet prve stopnje je razvit za modele s spredaj nameščenim hladilnikom in je primeren za YXZ1000R od modelnega leta 2016 do modelnega leta 2018.

description.en: Take your Ténéré to next level with the GYTR Performance Kit. Boosting power by up to 9 HP, this upgrade features a lightweight race exhaust system from Akrapovič, as well as the GYTR ECU and air filter kit that further enhance performance. And for improved control in the most challenging terrain, the GYTR footrest set is designed to facilitate grip and reduce mud cumulation. The final component in the Performance kit is a clutch cover upgrade, with a GYTR branded billet aluminium split cover allowing easy access to the clutch's inner workings for quick servicing between rally stages. Easy to install by retaining stock components, it's the must-have enhancement for your off-road racing experience.

description.en: An essential of any MX rider’s wardrobe, the MX Men’s Jersey is a lightweight and flexible must-have for your days in the dirt. A moisture wicking blend of polyester and elastane ensures constant comfort in all conditions, with mesh inserts for extra air flow and ventilation. Ergonomic sleeves with stretch cuffs give you an optimum riding position, with a seamless taped neck for effortless movement. Sublimated Yamaha, Alpinestars and GYTR branding completes a classic motocross look.

Izdelan je iz poliestra in elastana, ki odvajata vlago, zagotavlja nenehno udobje v vseh razmerah ter vključuje mrežaste dele za dodaten pretok zraka. Ergonomski rokavi z raztegljivimi manšetami omogočajo najugodnejši vozni položaj, izrez z lepljenimi šivi pa lahkotno gibanje. Sublimirani logotipi Yamaha, Alpinestars in GYTR dopolnjujejo klasičen motokrosistični videz.

name.en: Öhlins Cartridge Kit NIX30 for R7
name.sl-SI: Komplet vložkov Öhlins NIX30 za R7

description.en: The Road&Track 30 mm front fork cartridge kit from Öhlins is based on experience gained from World Supersport and  Superstock Championships. It doesn’t matter if you are heading for a National Road Racing title or if you are taking your bike to the local race track. This cartridge kit will give you loads of performance, stable damping characteristics and fantastic comfort. The kit has a unique design with compression damping and the adjustment on the left leg and rebound damping and the adjustment on the right leg – so all adjustments are made at the top together with the spring preload.
description.sl-SI: Komplet vložkov za sprednje vilice Road&Track 30 mm Öhlins temelji na izkušnjah, pridobljenih na svetovnem prvenstvu Supersport in prvenstvih Superstock. Ni pomembno, ali se borite za naslov državnega prvaka v motociklizmu ali pa z motornim kolesom dirkate na lokalnem dirkališču. Ta komplet vložkov vam zagotavlja boljše zmogljivosti, zanesljivo blaženje in izredno udobje. Komplet ima edinstveno zasnovo s kompresijskim blaženjem in nastavitvijo za levo nogo ter povratnim blaženjem in nastavitvijo za desno nogo – vse nastavitve lahko prilagajate na zgornjem delu, hkrati z nastavitvijo trdote vzmetenja.

Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your motorcycle.

description.en: Made out of heavy duty plastic, these bags are designed to hold shape and stand up on their own. After a day of boating, cleanse your engine with fresh water. Paket Style daje vašemu modelu R7 še privlačnejši profil na cesti in poskrbi za še večje navdušenje nad tem kompaktnim supersport motorjem.  Ta paket originalnih dodatkov vsebuje sistem hitrega prestavljanja, ki omogoča prestavljanje brez sklopke za še hitrejše in enakomernejše pospeševanje. Zatemnjen športni vizir in lahek nosilec registrske tablice dajeta vašemu R7 še bolj dinamičen videz – stranske obloge rezervoarja za gorivo pa omogočajo boljši nadzor nad motociklom. Za osvetlitev poskrbijo natančno zasnovani zaporedni LED-smerniki spredaj in zadaj, ki zagotavljajo boljšo vidljivost in estetsko privlačnost. Ščitnik ročice sprednje zavore v dirkaškem slogu pa kaže na čistokrvno dirkaško DNK. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo v paketu Style za R7 z veseljem namestil na vaše motorno kolo.
description.en: The Style Pack gives your R7 an even sharper profile on the street and increases the thrill factor of this slim-lined Supersport!  This Genuine Accessories pack comes with a quick shifter that enables clutchless gear shifting for even faster and smoother acceleration. The dark-smoked sport screen and lightweight license plate holder give a more dynamic look to your R7 – while the tank side grip pads provide you with extra controllability. Illuminate your journey with precision-engineered Sequential LED Blinker sets on both front and rear, for enhanced visibility and aesthetic appeal. While the racing-style billet front brake lever guard shows its pure race-bred DNA. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit the high quality Genuine Accessories in this R7 Style Pack to your motorcycle.

Uporabite protivibracijski modul SP Connect™, da dodatno zmanjšate vibracije za različne frekvenčne razpone. Razvoj tega novega izdelka je odziv na kompleksnost novejših modelov pametnih telefonov, pri katerih so fotoaparati sestavljeni iz močno občutljivih sestavnih delov. Posebej razviti elastomer blaži premike v vseh smereh in zaustavi do 60 % vibracij (npr. iz agregata motocikla), ki bi lahko vplivale na mehanski stabilizator slike fotoaparata. Vaš pametni telefon je tako zaščiten in ostaja stabilen ter varno nameščen, tako da lahko med potjo navigacijo preprosto uporabljate.
description.en: Use the SP Connect™ Anti Vibration Module to further reduce vibrations for a variety of frequency ranges. The development of this new product is a reaction to the complexity of newer smartphone models, whose camera systems consist of increasingly sensitive components. The specially developed elastomer inlay dampens in all directions and stops up to 60% of vibrations (e.g. from the motorcycle engine) that could affect the mechanical image stabilizer of the camera. This not only protects your smartphone, but it remains stable and securely mounted so that you can easily navigate while on the road.

description.en: The ultimate Travel gear for your TRACER 9 to hit the road in full functional style. The High screen, the Add-on Wide Screen and Heated Comfort Seat provide the extra comfort for those long endless roads. The Top Case gives you the perfect tool to take your belongings along with you on your endeavors combined with the stylish Side Cases of the TRACER 9 GT. Charge your phone easily with the USB Charger while you , keep an eye on your tire pressure with the Tire Pressure Monitoring tool. The pack also has a dedicated GPS stay to help you clamp your GPS securely. The Side Stand Extension gives your motorcycle more stability on any surface when parked, the Radiator Guard protects your radiator against those pesky stones and loose gravel that are in your trail, while the Engine guard gives protection against unintended falls. The LED Fog Lights increase visibility in bad weather conditions for optimal safety. While you enjoy your ride, we made sure your passenger is pampered as well. They will enjoy the comfort of the Passenger Comfort Seat and the Backrest.
description.sl-SI: Najboljša potovalna oprema za vaš TRACER 9. Odpravite se na pot z uporabnim slogom. Visok zaščitni vizir, dodaten širok zaščitni vizir, ogrevane ročke in ogrevan udoben sedež za več udobja na dolgih neskončnih cestah. Zgornji kovček je v kombinaciji s stranskima kovčkoma TRACER 9 GT popolno orodje za prevoz lastnine na popotovanjih. Telefon lahko enostavno napolnite s polnilnikom USB med uporabo orodja za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah. Paket ima tudi namenski nosilec za GPS, ki omogoča varno pritrditev navigacije. Zaradi podaljška stranskega nosilca je parkirani motocikel stabilnejši na vseh površinah, zaščita hladilnika ščiti hladilnik pred nadležnimi kamenčki in peskom, ki se znajdejo na poti, zaščita agregata pa nudi zaščito pred neželenimi padci. Za boljšo varnost poskrbijo LED meglenke, ki izboljšajo vidljivost v slabem vremenu. Poskrbeli smo, da med vožnjo ne boste uživali le vi, ampak tudi sopotnik. Sopotniki lahko uživajo v udobju, ki ga nudita udoben sovoznikov sedež in naslonjalo.

Touchscreen material and Amara fabric allow smartphone use and visor cleaning. A perfect item for enjoying and controlling your tide in the cold.

Zaščita za členke 1. stopnje se brezhibno prilega za neovirano gibanje in varnost, vodoodporni sloj pa zagotavlja dodatno zaščito pred vremenskimi vplivi. Material, primeren za zaslon na dotik, in tkanina Amara omogočata uporabo pametnega telefona in čiščenje vizirja. Popolna izbira za prijetno vožnjo v hladnem vremenu.

Fuel your passion for paddling with the Yamaha Telescopic Paddle. Its adaptable design and effortless adjustment let you focus on the joy of the journey.

Effortlessly adjust your paddle length from 50 to 114 cm with a simple twist for optimal paddling in any situation. 
The lightweight design allows convenient storage under boat seats or in WaveRunner compartments thanks to the aluminium shaft that cleverly hides inside the blade. 
Built to last, the paddle features a corrosion-resistant aluminium shaft, a hassle-free locking mechanism, and a high-impact moulded blade and boat hook handle.

Nadgradite svoj TRACER 9 GT+ s 'Travel Pack Pro' za neprimerljivo udobje in funkcionalnost. Visok vizir in dodaten širok zaščitni vizir omogočata boljšo zaščito pred vetrom, ogrevan udoben sedež in sedež za sopotnika pa zagotavljata udobno vožnjo. Ostanite obveščeni s sistemom za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah (TPMS) in kompletom za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah. Zaščitite motorno kolo s ščitnikom hladilnika in zaščito agregata 'Explorer' ter povečajte vidljivost s kompletom meglenk LED. Zavarujte opremo z nosilno ploščo za zgornji kovček, zgornjim kovčkom in naslonom. Ta paket združuje vrhunske funkcije za vrhunsko potovalno izkušnjo.
description.en: Upgrade your TRACER 9 GT+ with the Travel Pack Pro for unmatched comfort and functionality. The High Screen and Add-On Wide Screen enhance wind protection, while the Heated Comfort Seat and Passenger Seat ensure a cozy ride. Stay informed with the TPMS and Tire Pressure Monitoring Kit. Protect your bike with the Radiator Guard, Explorer Engine Guard, and add visibility with the LED Fog Light Kit. Secure your gear with the Top Case Mounting Plate, Top Case, and Backrest. This pack combines premium features for a superior travel experience.

Ténéré 700 is built to take you off the beaten track and move you over to new horizons. The Explorer Pack contains the complete ensemble of accessories to support this journey of discovery. The aluminium side cases with 72L capacity ensure you have enough space to pack up and go at a moment's notice. To carry even extra luggage, the Explorer Pack features an easily mountable mono seat rack, with flat surface, that allows faster setting up of additional bags. With all that luggage, it's imperative to have good bike stability when parked and that's why the Explorer Pack is equipped with a center stand. For added protection, the pack also features a skid plate and an engine guard, so your Ténéré 700 can withstand those long-distance travels. Are you ready to make the next horizon yours?
description.sl-SI: Ténéré 700 je ustvarjen, da vas odpelje z običajnih cest in vam odpre nove svetove. Paket Explorer vsebuje vso dodatno opremo, ki jo potrebujete za take raziskovalne izlete v neznano. Aluminijasta kovčka s prostornino 72 litrov vam zagotavljata dovolj prostora za prtljago, zato se lahko na pot odpravite brez posebnih priprav. Paket Explorer vsebuje še prtljažnik za dodatno prtljago za enojni sedež, ki ga lahko preprosto namestite, na njegovo ravno površino pa lahko hitro pritrdite dodatne torbe. Vsa ta količina prtljage zahteva tudi stabilno parkiranje, zato je paket Explorer opremljen tudi s sredinskim stojalom. Za dodatno zaščito paket vključuje še ščitno ploščo in ščitnik motorja, da vaš Ténéré 700 prenese tudi najdaljša potovanja. Ste pripravljeni, da osvojite naslednje obzorje?

This kit includes:

The Tricity is an embodiment of convenience, making commuting simple, easy and fun. With such high dose of practicality, the Urban pack is aimed at increasing the options for Customers to offer additional comfort and space through its various accessories. The high screen provides greater protection against wind, meaning your journeys will never be tiring or uncomfortable. To increase the storage space, we included the rear carrier and the new 34L top case, which also increases the style quotient of the Tricity. There’s no style without substance and  we have thought about the passenger’s comfort as well and hence we include the backrest pad for the top case. We wanted to provide an easy way for our customers to recharge their devices on the go, and hence have included the USB charging port. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your Tricity.
description.sl-SI: Tricity je simbol udobja, zato je vsakodnevna vožnja preprosta in zabavna. Paket 'Urban' je izredno praktičen in z različnimi dodatki uporabniku omogoča boljše udobje med vožnjo in več prostora. Visok vizir poskrbi za boljšo zaščito pred vetrom, kar pomeni, da vaša vožnja nikoli ne bo utrujajoča ali neudobna. Da bi povečali prostor za shranjevanje, smo dodali zadnji nosilec in novi 34-litrski zgornji kovček, ki izboljšata videz vašega skuterja Tricity. Poskrbeli smo, da lahko sopotnik uživa v udobju in se vozi s stilom, zato smo dodali blazino za naslon za zadnji kovček. Strankam smo želeli omogočiti enostaven način polnjenja svojih naprav med vožnjo, zato smo dodali vrata USB za polnjenje. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš Tricity.

description.en: Yamaha is offering all the components of the Hard Cab Enclosure System separately for added customer convenience. Accessing the cargo area with ease is one of the key factors in the fully functional Wolverine X4. This glass rear window opens utilizing familiar gas struts like those of a SUV to hold the glass up while the window is open (window must be closed while in drive).The fully lockable window keeps your items secure from unwanted company. When paired with the Rear Cargo Box that maximizes rear cargo space, you get a truly versatile package ready to conquer the outdoors!

Ena ključnih značilnosti polnofunkcionalnega modela Wolverine X4 je preprost dostop do prtljažnega prostora. To stekleno zadnje okno se odpre s pomočjo že poznanih plinskih vzmeti, kot so tiste pri športnih terencih, ki zadržijo steklo v zgornjem položaju, ko je okno odprto (med vožnjo mora biti okno zaprto). Ker se da okno v celoti zakleniti, so vaši predmeti varni pred nepridipravi. Če poleg tega uporabljate še zadnji tovorni kovček, ki poveča prtljažni prostor zadaj, je vaš vsestranski paket opreme pripravljen na dogodivščine na prostem!

description.sl-SI: Izboljšajte svojo izkušnjo na Yamahinih WaveRunnerjih serije FX! Ta komplet vam omogoča, da imate pijačo na dosegu roke, medtem ko se peljete s svojimi najdražjimi. Obstoječi nosilec lahko dopolnite tako, da zamenjate pritrditveni nosilec za zvočnik/GPS, ali pa skuter nadgradite s kompletom.

description.en: Outlet suitable to charge your electronic equipment such as mobile phones.

description.en: The city is the XMAX's natural habitat and with the Urban Accessories Pack you can take the practicality of your XMAX a notch higher. Besides providing enhanced wind protection from the high screen, the pack also takes care of your luggage needs with a 34L top case with matching colour plate set and carrier – keeping your belonging safe and secure. And a backrest for the top case makes sure the passenger has an equally comfortable ride. To protect you from the scratches and the scruffs, the city throws up, the pack contains the XMAX scratch protector. Available from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your XMAX.
description.sl-SI: Mesto je XMAX-ovo naravno okolje, s kompletom dodatne opreme Urban pa lahko še bolje izkoristite XMAX-ovo praktičnost. Poleg izboljšane zaščite pred vetrom z visokim vizirjem paket poskrbi tudi za vaše potovalne potrebe s 34-litrskim zgornjim kovčkom z ujemajočim se kompletom barvnih ploščic in nosilcem, ki ščiti vaše osebne predmete. Naslon za zgornji kovček pa poskrbi, da bo tudi sopotnik užival v enako udobni vožnji. Za zaščito pred praskami in odrgninami komplet vključuje zaščito pred praskami XMAX. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaše vozilo XMAX.
Ta originalna Yamaha trda sprednja vrata so zasnovana za najvišjo stopnjo trpežnosti, udobja in funkcije.

description.en:
Yamaha motorcycles are meant to be used all year long and that is why it is important to have accessories that make every day usage a breeze. 
The Urban Pack contains a rear carrier along with a 39L top case, to keep your valuables securely and with ease. While the motorcycle charges you up with energy, the USB outlet is there to charge your electronic devices.
And finally, there is a higher sport screen to protect you from the urban elements the city throws at you!
description.sl-SI:
Yamahina motorna kolesa so namenjena uporabi skozi vse leto, zato je pomembno, da imate dodatno opremo, ki omogoča enostavno vsakodnevno uporabo. 
Paket Urban Pack vključuje zadnji nosilec in 39-litrski kovček, v katerem lahko varno in enostavno shranjujete dragocene predmete. Motocikel z energijo napolni vas, USB-vtičnica pa vaše elektronske naprave. 
Tu je še višji športni vizir, ki vas ščiti pred elementi urbanega okolja!

description.en: A stylish eyewear piece for sunny days, the Paddock Blue sunglasses for adults are Yamaha Racing fashion at its best. The black polycarbonate frame ensures a lightweight but strong build, and tinted blue lenses with UV400 protection help protect the eyes. White Yamaha Racing logos on the contrast-coloured racing blue arms give a cool and sporty look, and a black carry pouch allows easy storage and portability.

description.en: Comfortable, adaptable and stylish, the Paddock Blue Men’s Sweater is a teamwear classic for wearing to race events, the gym and more. A soft blend of polyester  and cotton, it features a full-length zip and fixed hood with a tight closure. Self-fabric hem and cuffs give the sweater a seamless look, with colour contrast black sleeves and external pockets for essentials. Embroidered chest branding and back graphic in white set this garment off.
description.sl-SI: Udobna, prilagodljiva in stilska moška jopa Paddock Blue je klasično oblačilo ekipe za nošnjo na dirkalnih prireditvah, v telovadnici in povsod drugod. Izdelana je iz poliestra in bombaža, ima zadrgo po celotni dolžini in fiksno kapuco, ki jo lahko tesno zapnete. Obšivi in manšete iz enakega materiala poskrbijo za brezhiben videz jope, rokavi so v kontrastni črni barvi, zunanji žepi pa omogočajo prostor za vaše predmete. Izvezen logotip na prsih in bela grafika na hrbtu oblačilo dokončno izpopolnita.

Paket Gravel je namenjen tistim, ki avanturistično gredo izven urejenih poti in izzovejo svoj motor na več cestah in poteh.
description.en: Create a more buff dual-road style for your TRACER 9 with soft side bags, strong engine guards, extra fog lights and a radiator guard. The Gravel Pack is meant for those who adventurously go beyond the beaten track and challenge their machine on multiple roads and paths.

description.sl-SI: Originalni del

Ženska jakna kolekcije REVS, zasnovana za zaščito pred zimskimi vremenskimi razmerami, z zunanjo plastjo in podlogo iz poliestra zagotavlja odpornost proti vodi in vetru ter hkrati udobje. Zasnovana v kontrastu črne in rdeče barve REVS, ta udobna jakna ima zapiranje z zadrgo po celotni dolžini, ščitnik za brado in nastavljive manšete za prilagajanje vremenskim razmeram. Fiksna kapuca, sešita iz treh tretjin, in sprednji žepi z zadrgo ščitijo pred vremenskimi vplivi, izvezeni napis Yamaha na prsih, grafika navpične črte zadaj in obrobe na ramenih pa zajemajo samo bistvo sloga REVS.
description.en: Designed to protect from the winter elements, the REVS Women’s Outerwear Jacket offers water and wind resistance with comfort inside a polyester shell and lining. Designed in REVS black and red colour contrast, this comfort fit jacket features a full-length zip closure, chin guard and adjustable cuffs for adapting to the weather. A 3-panel lined fixed hood and zippered front pockets helps shield you from the elements, while embroidered Yamaha branding on the chest, backstripe graphic and white shoulder piping capture the latest REVS essence.

description.en: Ease your commute with the XMAX Keyless Urban Pack, which gives you the added  convenience of our Keyless Top Case 45L along with the Rear Carrier, Top Case Mounting Plate, E-locking Mechanism Kit and Switch, Top Case Coloured Plates and Top Case Backrest.

This heavy-duty, durable cargo box allows you to take along your essentials for the ride or the job. Doubles as a non-insulated cooler with integrated drain plug for those long workdays or outings into the woods. Designed to fit perfectly in-between the bed rails and attaches using OE bed box mounting bolts. Works great with or without Yamaha's bed mat (sold separately).

name.sl-SI: Ščitniki pred udarci kamnov za Wolverine X2

description.en: Take on the toughest, gnarliest trails but still protect your Wolverine X2. Yamaha’s accessory Rock Sliders provide frame rail protection for the under-door area. Utilizing a full length, plated substructure, these Rock Sliders provide stylish looks while being robust enough to take on the abuse from trail obstacles. For the utmost protection, pair these Rock Sliders with our accessory Front Bash Plate, Front A-Arm Guards and Skid Plate, all sold separately. A perfect combination to armor up your Wolverine X2 for your next trail or work adventure.
description.sl-SI: Podajte se na najtežje, najbolj zahtevne poti, a svoje vozilo Wolverine X2 zaščitite. Yamahini ščitniki pred udarci kamnov zagotavljajo zaščito območja pod vrati v obliki letev na ogrodju. S kromirano podstrukturo po celotni dolžini ti ščitniki pred udarci kamnov poskrbijo za stilsko dovršen videz, a so hkrati dovolj robustni, da ščitijo pred ovirami na poti. Za najboljšo zaščito poleg ščitnikov pred udarci kamnov uporabite tudi dodatni sprednji ščitnik pred udarci, zaščito sprednje A-roke in ščitno ploščo; vsi omenjeni dodatki so na prodaj ločeno. Odlična kombinacija za ojačanje vašega modela Wolverine X2 za naslednjo pot ali delovno avanturo.

description.en: Designed in Yamaha’s classic racing blue with contrasting leg stripes, the Paddock Blue Women’s Jogging Pants are comfortable and great for relaxed daily wear. Hlače imajo tajliran kroj in elastični pas, na dnu hlačnic je tudi prefinjena odprtina na zadrgo za zračenje. Izvezen logotip Yamaha Racing poskrbi za popoln mestni slog.

And a backrest for the top case makes sure the passenger has an equally comfortable ride. To protect you from the scratches and the scruffs, the city throws up, the pack contains the XMAX scratch protector. Urban Pack Content: High Screen | Rear Carrier | 39L Top Case (incl. Outer and inner pockets allow room for essential items, with stitched Yamaha branding capturing the essence of the Sport Heritage range’s past.
description.sl-SI: Motoristična jakna Sports Heritage za moške je privlačen kos Yamahine opreme za vožnjo po navdihu sloga retro ter je v zapečeni oranžni in beli barvi videti naravnost osupljivo. Izdelana je iz 100-odstotnega bivoljega usnja z bombažno podlogo ter voznikom motornih koles Sport Heritage ponuja slog in varnost s snemljivim ščitnikom Warrior za komolce in ramena. V zunanjih in notranjih žepih je na voljo veliko prostora za vse pomembne predmete, s prešitim logotipom Yamaha pa pride do izraza slavna preteklost segmenta Sport Heritage.

description.en: Front axle protector compatible with optional style accent rings

description.en: A precision fork and shock pump with an easy-to-read dial gauge for accurate pressure readings up to 360 psi / 24.8 bar. An air release button and Pressure-Rite connector makes setting proper pressure easy and eliminates air loss when disconnecting, while the flexible hose takes stress off the valve stem when pumping.
description.sl-SI: Natančne vilice in amortizerji z merilnikom, ki omogoča preprosto odčitavanje, za natančno merjenje tlaka do 360 psi/24,8 bara. Gumb za sprostitev zraka in priključek Pressure-Rite omogočata preprosto nastavitev ustreznega tlaka in odpravljata izgubo zraka pri odklopu, gibljiva cev pa razbremeni steblo ventila pri črpanju.

name.sl-SI: Moška majica Racing Heritage s kratkimi rokavi

description.en: An essential for the Yamaha Racing fan, the Racing Heritage men t-shirt carries the iconic Yamaha racing design. Perfect for everyday wear this Racing heritage t-shirt comes in black or white. The comfortable blend of organic cotton and elastane allows for great mobility, and this t-shirt features the racing heritage red speed block graphic across the chest. Yamaha branding on the chest and sleeve express Yamaha’s rich racing heritage and give an all-round racers’ look.
description.sl-SI: Osnoven kos za vse privržence Yamahinega dirkaštva: moška majica Racing Heritage v ikoničnem videzu sloga Yamaha Racing. Majica Racing Heritage je na voljo v črni ali beli barvi ter je idealna za vsakodnevno uporabo. Udobna mešanica ekološko pridelanega bombaža in elastana omogoča odlično gibljivost, čez sprednji del majice pa se razteza klasična rdeča grafika 'Speedblock'. Yamahini logotipi na prsih in rokavih izražajo bogato dirkalno dediščino Yamahe in poskrbijo za prepoznaven dirkaški videz.

name.sl-SI: Ženska majica s kratkimi rokavi s podobo skuterja

description.en: Explore the city in style with the Scooter graphic t-shirt for women. Grey with a bright, colourful printed aligned with the new Yamaha scooter range, this t-shirt’s organic cotton and viscose blend gives maximum comfort and movement for everyday wear. The MOVE LIVE LOVE print is a core element of this garment’s look, with a central pop-up style Yamaha graphic adding a wonderful flourish.
description.sl-SI: Raziščite mesto v slogu – z žensko majico z grafiko skuterja. Siva majica s kratkimi rokavi ima živahno barvito grafiko, ki se ujema z Yamahino novo serijo skuterjev. Izdelana je iz ekološko pridelanega bombaža in viskoze, zato omogoča maksimalno udobje in gibljivost pri vsakodnevni uporabi. Glavni element majice je slogan MOVE LIVE LOVE v živahnih barvah in oblačkih, ki Yamahini grafiki dodajo urban videz.

name.sl-SI: Obesek za ključe Faster Sons XSR

description.en: Whether you ride them or just love them, the Faster Sons XSR Keyring is made for the XSR fan. An icon of Yamaha Sport Heritage, the retro cutting-edge XSR models are timeless classics that this keyring pays homage to. A 2D XSR keyring in PVC is attached to a metal keychain for a useful novelty that keeps keys attached with a Faster Sons flair.
description.sl-SI: Obesek za ključe Faster Sons XSR je izdelan za ponosne lastnike in ljubitelje motornih koles XSR. Vrhunski retro modeli XSR, ikona Yamahine serije Sport Heritage, so brezčasna klasika, ki se ji poklanjamo s tem obeskom za ključe. Dvodimenzionalni obesek za ključe XSR iz PVC-ja je pritrjen na kovinski obroček in je uporaben dodatek v duhu kolekcije Faster Sons.

description.en: Keep yourself hydrated from home to the track with the Paddock Blue Water Bottle. With 750ml capacity, the bottle features level markers with motivational text to help you stay topped up throughout the day. A flip up plastic straw makes drinking on the go easy, with Yamaha Racing branding and Racing Blue shades giving an eye-catching look.
description.sl-SI: Keep yourself hydrated from home to the track with the Paddock Blue Water Bottle. With 750ml capacity, the bottle features level markers with motivational text to help you stay topped up throughout the day. A flip up plastic straw makes drinking on the go easy, with Yamaha Racing branding and Racing Blue shades giving an eye-catching look.

Zagotovite si vse potrebno za vožnjo s kompletom TMAX 'Urban Pack 45L', ki ga sestavljajo zadnji nosilec TMAX, 45-litrski zgornji kovček s kompletom ključev za cilindrično ključavnico, plošča za zgornji kovček in hrbtni naslon za zgornji kovček. Nepogrešljiv paket za vsakodnevne voznike, ki potrebujejo dodaten prostor za shranjevanje in funkcionalnost.
description.en: Own every ride with the TMAX Urban Pack 45L, consisting of the Rear Carrier TMAX, 45L Top Case  with Key Cylinder Set and Top Case Plate, and Top Case Backrest. An essential pack for the regular commuter that needs extra storage and function.
Aluminium radiator cover enhances the modern look of your Yamaha.
description.sl-SI: Aluminijast pokrov hladilnika poudarja sodoben videz vaše Yamahe.

description.en: Silencer plate to replace the original plate.
description.sl-SI: Ploščica dušilnika, ki nadomešča originalno ploščico.

description.en: Keep your ski ropes safe and your WaveRunner or boat engine protected with the Yamaha Rope Float. This ingenious accessory helps prevent ropes from getting tangled in the propeller or ingested by the jet pump. Simply thread the rope through the centre of the closed-cell foam tube before attaching it to the tow eye. The durable nylon cover protects the float and boasts a stylish Yamaha logo silk-screened on one side.

This rugged tubular Front Brush Guard is designed to provide additional protection while you venture on and off the trail. It is designed to seamlessly integrate with the front profile of the UMX while adding tough, aggressive styling. Helps protect the grill, hood and cowl while complementing the bold styling of your Yamaha. Perfectly complements tubular rear brush guard (sold separately). The kit includes front brush guard, mounting hardware, and detailed installation instructions.

name.en: Öhlins Front Fork Spring 9,5N/mm for NIX30 Kit
name.sl-SI: Vzmeti za sprednje vilice Öhlins z 9,5 N/mm za komplet NIX30

description.en: Öhlins front fork springs are developed specifically for Öhlins cartridge NIX30 kits and front forks. But they are also in itself a great front end upgrade and option to improve responsiveness and performance of the fork. Öhlins offers a wide range of linear springs to suit each individual type of bike, rider weight and personal preferences for installation into the standard front fork.
description.sl-SI: Vzmeti za sprednje vilice Öhlins so zasnovane posebej za komplet vložkov Öhlins NIX30 in sprednje vilice. Poleg tega poskrbijo tudi za odlično nadgradnjo sprednjega dela ter možnost za izboljšanje odzivnosti in zmogljivosti vilice. Öhlins zagotavlja širok nabor linearnih vzmeti, ki so primerne za vsako posamezno vrsto motornega kolesa, težo voznika in osebne želje za namestitev v standardne sprednje vilice.
Komplet stranskih zaščit iz gume z visoko gostoto za XSR900, ki vam zagotavlja boljši oprijem na motornem kolesu, ko vozite po vijugastih cestah.
description.en: High density rubber Side Pad Set for XSR900, providing you with that extra grip on your bike when handling through the twisty roads.

Charger for all types of batteries.  New durable design to make it easy to handle, with unique mounting system on the back for quick connection to CS accessories. It can be left safely connected for long periods during maintenance charging.
description.sl-SI: Polnilnik za vse vrste akumulatorjev.  Nova trpežna zasnova za enostavno upravljanje, z edinstvenim sistemom namestitve na hrbtni strani za hitro povezavo z dodatki CS. Med vzdrževalnim polnjenjem lahko ostane varno povezan tudi dalj časa.

description.en: Engineered to sit on the back, rather than on the neck, and with an added pad, this vest provides increased comfort. Made of high-quality materials it ensures your safety while you enjoy boating.
description.sl-SI: Ta jopič, ki je zasnovan za opiranje na hrbet namesto na vrat in z dodano podlogo, zagotavlja povečano udobje. Narejen je iz visokokakovostnih materialov in zagotavlja vašo varnost, medtem ko uživate v vožnji s čolnom.

name.en: Weather Cover for Yamaha Phone Cases

description.sl-SI: Zaščitite pametni telefon pred dežjem, znojem, prahom ali blatom z uporabo ZAŠČITE PRED VREMENOM skupaj z ovitkom za telefon Yamaha. Poveča odpornost na udarce, zaslon na dotik pa ostane povsem uporaben. Opomba: Debele zaščite za zaslon ali rokavice lahko v kombinaciji z zaščito pred vremenom omejijo uporabnost zaslona na dotik. Zaščita pred vremenom lahko dodatno vpliva na delovanje domačega gumba na mobilnih telefonih iPhone 8, 8 Plus, 7 in 7 Plus. Težavo lahko rešite z vklopom programskega domačega gumba (Assistive Touch).
description.en: Protect your smartphone from rain, sweat, dust or mud by using the WEATHER COVER together with the YAMAHA Phone Case. It adds shock resistance and the touch screen remains fully functional.Note: Thick screen protectors or gloves can limit the usability of your touchscreen in combination with the Weather Cover. The Weather Cover can further affect the homebutton functionality of iPhone 8, 8 Plus, 7 & 7 Plus. This can be compensated by enabling the software homebutton (Assistive Touch).

name.sl-SI: Otroški pulover s kapuco na zadrgo kolekcije REVS

description.sl-SI: Pri otroški jopici s kapuco na zadrgo kolekcije se slog REVS sreča z vsakodnevnim udobjem. Ujema se s sodobno obliko jop s kapuco na zadrgo za odrasle. Izdelana je iz mešanice bombaža in poliestra, ki omogoča udobje in toploto tudi pri aktivnostih na prostem. Fiksna podložena kapuca, zaščita za brado in rebrasti patenti na zapestjih omogočajo še več udobja, pika na i pa sta izvezeni napis Yamaha na prsih in grafika navpične črte zadaj.
description.en: REVS style meets everyday comfort in the REVS Kid’s Zip Hoodie. Aligned with the contemporary shape of the adult zip hoodies, this cotton and polyester mix keeps things comfortable and warm for outdoor use. A fixed lined hood, chin guard and ribbed cuffs add extra comfort, with embroidered Yamaha chest branding and backstripe graphic that tie the garment together.

description.sl-SI: Yamalube® FC-W 10W-30 je univerzalno olje vrhunske zmogljivosti za visokozmogljive 4-taktne izvenkrmne motorje. Edinstvena formula za uporabo v pomorstvu, posebej razvita za zahtevno morsko okolje, zagotavlja večjo varčnost goriva in nemoteno delovanje.

description.en: Yamalube Motorcycle Chain Spray is available in a handy 56ML size can for additional lubrication on longer rides. Developed for O-ring and X-ring chains on road machines, its special sticky formula provides a fling resistant lubricating film that can withstand extremely high pressures, enabling your motorcycle to achieve peak performance and optimum fuel efficiency.
description.sl-SI: Pršilo Yamalube za verigo motornega kolesa je na voljo v priročni 56-mililitrski pločevinki za dodatno podmazovanje na daljših vožnjah. Razvito za verigi O-ring in X-ring terenskih motorjev, posebna lepljiva formula zagotavlja podmazano folijo, odporno na udarce, ki lahko prenese izjemno visoke pritiske, kar omogoča vašemu motornemu kolesu doseganje najvišjih zmogljivosti ter optimalno učinkovitost goriva.

description.en: Additional extension to the standard rear rack to keep your belongings secured.

description.sl-SI: Enodelni sedež za reli bo v vas prebudil dirkaški adrenalin na motornem kolesu Ténéré 700. Z boljšim oprijemom in terenskim slogom uživajte v optimiziranem položaju vožnje in boljšem ravnotežju.
description.en: Channel Ténéré 700's rallying adrenaline with the one-piece Rally Seat. With more grip and off-road styling, enjoy an optimised riding position and better balance.

description.en: The high air flow kit offers increased air flow to the engine for boost in power.
description.sl-SI: Komplet za visok pretok zraka nudi večji pretok zraka v motor za več moči.

name.sl-SI: Set zaporednih LED utripalk spredaj 220 mm

description.en: Introducing Yamaha's Front Sequential LED Blinker Set – A brilliant symphony of safety and style. Illuminate your journey with precision-engineered LEDs that deliver a captivating sequential light display, enhancing both visibility and aesthetic appeal. Crafted to seamlessly integrate with your Yamaha, this blinker set not only signals your turns but also makes a bold statement on the road. Elevate your riding experience with the perfect blend of innovation and design – Yamaha's Front Sequential LED Blinker Set.
description.sl-SI: Predstavljamo Yamahin komplet sprednjih zaporednih LED smernikov - sijajna simfonija varnosti in sloga. Osvetlite svoje potovanje z natančno izdelanimi diodami LED, ki zagotavljajo očarljiv zaporedni svetlobni prikaz, s čimer izboljšujejo vidljivost in estetski videz. Ta komplet smernikov, ki je zasnovan tako, da se brezhibno ujema z vašo Yamaho, ne signalizira le vaših zavojev, temveč daje tudi drzno izjavo na cesti. Izboljšajte svojo izkušnjo vožnje s popolno kombinacijo inovacij in oblikovanja - Yamahinim kompletom sprednjih sekvenčnih LED smernikov.

Dodajte slog in zaščito svoji Yamahi R9 z zaščitno blazinico visoke gostote za rezervoar. Ta originalna komponenta, izdelana iz trdne in trpežne gumijaste zmesi, ima 3D obliko, zaključeno z logotipom R9, ki izboljša slog vašega motornega kolesa, hkrati pa je opremljena z lepilom 3M VHB, da ostane trdno pritrjena na vaš rezervoar za gorivo.
description.en: Add style and protection to your Yamaha R9 with the High Density Rubber Tank Pad. Engineered from a tough and durable rubber compound, this genuine component features a 3D design finished with an R9 logo to enhance the style of your motorcycle, while being supported by 3M VHB adhesive to remain secure to your fuel tank.

description.sl-SI: Ženska motoristična jakna Sport Touring, zasnovana za delovanje v vseh letnih časih, je tehničen in zelo natančen izdelek za neustrašne raziskovalce. Trdna zunanjost iz poliestra in poliuretana v dvobarvni sivi barvi je vodoodporna in vsebuje odstranljivo podlogo za nastavljivo udobje v mešanih pogojih. Ščitniki za ramena in komolce nudijo samozavest in brezskrbnost pri vožnji, medtem ko 6 žepov ponuja veliko prostora za predmete. Nastavljiv pas in zapestja vam omogočajo, da z lahkoto spremenite prileganje, medtem ko prezračevalne zadrge nudijo odlično zračnost. Za popolno potovalno opravo jo kombinirajte s športno-potovalnimi motorističnimi hlačami in rokavicami.
description.en: Designed to perform in all seasons, the Sport Touring Women’s Riding Jacket is a technical and high-precision item for intrepid explorers. A tough polyester and polyurethane outer in two-tone grey is waterproof and contains a removable lining for adjustable comfort in mixed conditions. Shoulder and elbow protectors offer confidence and peace of mind when riding, while 6 pockets offer substantial space for items. Adjustable waist and wrists allow you to alter the fit with ease, while ventilation zippers offer excellent breathability. Pair with the Sport Touring Riding Pants and Gloves for the perfect road trip outfit.

The Style Pack gives your R7 an even sharper profile on the street and multiplies this compact Supersport’s high thrill factor! This Genuine Accessories pack comes with a quick shifter that enables clutchless gear shifting for even faster and smoother acceleration. The dark-smoked sport screen and lightweight license plate holder give a more dynamic look to your R7 – while the tank side grip pads provide you with extra controllability. And the racing-style billet front brake lever guard shows its pure race-bred DNA.  Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit the high quality Genuine Accessories in this R7 Style Pack to your motorcycle
description.sl-SI: Paket Style daje vašemu R7 še lepši profil na cesti in pomnoži faktor navdušenja tega kompaktnega motocikla razreda Supersport. Ta paket originalnih dodatkov vsebuje sistem hitrega prestavljanja, ki omogoča prestavljanje brez sklopke za še hitrejše in enakomernejše pospeševanje. Zatemnjen športni vizir in lahek nosilec registrske tablice dajeta vašemu R7 še bolj dinamičen videz – stranske obloge rezervoarja za gorivo pa omogočajo boljši nadzor nad motociklom. Ščitnik ročice sprednje zavore v dirkaškem slogu pa kaže na čistokrvni dirkaški DNK.  Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo v paketu Style za R7 z veseljem namestil na vaše motorno kolo.

name.en: Hard Cab Rear Door Kit RMAX™4

description.en: These Genuine Yamaha Hard Cab Rear Doors are designed to deliver the highest levels of durability, comfort and function.
description.sl-SI: Ta originalna Yamaha trda sprednja vrata so zasnovana za najvišjo stopnjo trpežnosti, udobja in funkcije.

Zagotovite si vse potrebno za mestno vožnjo s kompletom NMAX 'Urban Pack 34L', ki ga sestavljajo visok vizir NMAX, zadnji nosilec NMAX, 34-litrski zgornji kovček s kompletom ključev za cilindrično ključavnico, plošča za zgornji kovček in hrbtni naslon za zgornji kovček. Nepogrešljiv paket za vsakodnevne voznike, ki potrebujejo dodaten prostor za shranjevanje in funkcionalnost.
description.en: Conquer every urban ride with the NMAX Urban Pack 34L, consisting of the High Screen NMAX, Rear Carrier NMAX, 34L Top Case  with Key Cylinder Set , Top Case Plate, and Top Case Backrest. An essential pack for the regular commuter that needs extra storage and function.

Colourful, comfortable and easy to throw on, the Paddock Blue Men’s Hoodie is a relaxed piece of Streetwear for everyday wear. Made from cotton and polyester  in a slick French Terry finish, colour blocks of racing blue, black and white set off the garment’s look with retro tape down the arms and shoulders. A lined hood with draw cord, ribbed hem and elastic cuffs offer comfort in all climates, with staple iconic Yamaha Racing branding.
description.sl-SI: Barvit, udoben in preprost pulover Paddock Blue za moške je oblačilo kolekcije Streetwear sproščenega videza za vsakodnevno uporabo. Izdelan je iz bombaža in poliestra z elegantnim zunanjim slojem iz francoskega frotirja, obarvan je z motivi v dirkaško modri, črni in beli barvi, ki oblačilo izpopolnijo s trakom v retro slogu na rokavih in ramenih. Podložena kapuca z vrvico, rebrasti obšivi in elastične manšete zagotavljajo udobje v vseh razmerah, vključen je tudi značilni ikonski logotip Yamaha Racing.

description.en: Sturdy and lightweight, it adds comfort and storage to your vessel.
description.sl-SI: Lahek in trpežen sedež zagotavlja dodatno udobje in prostor za shranjevanje na plovilu.

description.en: Packed with features for enjoying long-distance journeys, the Adventure rally jacket is a rugged must-have for the intrepid explorer. Presented in the iconic Yamaha Racing Blue with grey and black panelling and fluorescent yellow lining, this jacket offers plenty of essentials storage with seven external and two interior pockets. Ventilation panels, a thermal liner and a removable waterproof membrane allow combinations for optimal comfort in all weather conditions, with a built-in water bladder for keeping topped up on the road. Protectors in the outershell give extra confidence in the saddle, with adjustable sleeve straps to further finesse comfort levels.
description.sl-SI: Jakna Adventure Rally je oblikovana za uživanje na potovanjih po dolgih razdaljah in je nepogrešljiv kos oblačila za neustrašne raziskovalce. Jakna je na voljo v ikonski modri barvi ekipe Yamaha Racing s sivimi in črnimi našitki ter fluorescentno rumeno oblogo, poleg tega ponuja veliko prostora za shranjevanje s sedmimi zunanjimi in dvema notranjima žepoma. Prezračevalne zaplate, toplotna obloga in odstranljiva vodoodporna membrana omogočajo kombinacijo za optimalno udobje v vseh vremenskih razmerah, prav tako je vgrajen vodni mehur, da vam na poti ne bo zmanjkalo tekočine. Ščitniki v zunanjem sloju vam dajejo več samozavesti na sedežu motorja, z nastavljivimi trakovi na rokavih za nadaljnjo izboljšanje udobja na vseh ravneh.

description.en: Technical and designed with protection and comfort at the front, the Paddock Blue Women’s Knitted Gloves are stylish and lightweight. Preprosto jih lahko vzamete s sabo na kratke vožnje, rokavice se ponašajo s tremi pleteninami v modri in beli barvi, površinami za zračenje, toplotno zaščito in ščitniki za členke za varno prileganje. Jakna je izdelana iz 100-odstotnega bivoljega usnja v črni barvi, ima bombažno podlogo s potiskom in zagotavlja varnost s snemljivim ščitnikom Warrior za komolce in ramena. description.en: Quick-shift system, increasing bike control and making gear change easier.

With its off-road credentials, the Ténéré 700 is meant to be ridden dirty! To give you and your motorcycle that edge of the seat adrenaline rush, the Rally Pack offers some of the most exciting and sporty Yamaha Genuine Accessories. Giving you the freedom to change riding position dynamically, the rally seat increases the authentic rally look of your Ténéré 700. To make it also sound like a true rally machine, the Akrapovič slip-on gives a throaty-rich exhaust note. Taking your bike off road can push the drive-train to its edges, and this is why the chain guide, chain guard and radiator protector are there to safeguard important elements of your Ténéré 700. For a sharp and dynamic look, the Rally Pack also includes number plate holder, tank pad and LED blinkers. The Rally Pack is your ticket to the ultimate sideways drifting action!
description.sl-SI: S svojim terenskim značajem je Ténéré 700 ustvarjen za agresivno vožnjo! Paket Rally vsebuje izbor najbolj vznemirljive in športne Yamahine originalne dodatne opreme, da vam bo na polno poganjal adrenalin po žilah. Rally sedež, ki vam omogoča spreminjanje položaja med vožnjo, še dodatno poudarja pristen rally videz vašega motorja Ténéré 700. Da pa bo tudi zvenel kot pravi rally motor, Akrapovičev dušilnik skrbi za grlene tone izpuha. Vožnja po brezpotjih lahko pomeni preizkušnjo samih meja pogonskega sistema, zato vodilo verige, ščitnik verige in ščitnik hladilnika varujejo pomembne dele vašega motorja Ténéré 700. Za drzen in dinamičen videz paket Rally vključuje nosilec registrske tablice, zaščito za rezervoar in LED-smernike. Paket Rally je vaša vstopnica v svet brezkompromisne akcije z bočnim zdrsavanjem!

description.en:
There is a reason why there is a word sport in “Sport Touring” - while you can comfortably munch miles on the Tracer 900, you can equally set corners alight with the nimble and agile handling. 
To explore this sporty side of the Tracer 900, we put together the Sport Pack. 
It does so in two ways, a) Looks b) Functionality.  
Step up to the sport dimension!
description.sl-SI:
S športno-potovalnim motornim kolesom Tracer 900 se lahko odpravite na daljšo vožnjo ali pa s spretnim upravljanjem polagate ovinke, saj je ta model zelo okreten. 
Za raziskovanje športne plati modela Tracer 900 smo oblikovali komplet Sport Pack. 
Pri tem je poskrbljeno za videz in funkcionalnost. 
Privoščite si športno vožnjo.

name.en: CAPIT Tire Warmer Suprema Spina M/XL
name.sl-SI: Grelnik pnevmatik Suprema Spina M/XL CAPIT

description.en: Tire warmers allow you to get full performance from your machine right from the starting line, and without having to do several laps to warm up your tires.
description.sl-SI: Grelniki pnevmatik omogočajo popolne zmogljivosti vašega motorja takoj od začetka, brez potrebe po dodatnih vožnjah za ogrevanje pnevmatik.

description.en: The new TRACER 9 Sport Pack provides the right sporty finish for your TRACER 9. The Sport Pack gives your bike that bit extra to personalize your motorcycle to your ideal image. Slide through your gears with the Quick Shifter while the Knee Pads provide the extra grip for your knees when shredding corners. The sleek License Plate Holder sharpens up the rear and the stylishly designed Side Sliders protect your engine from any unfortunate moments.
description.sl-SI: Novi paket Sport za TRACER 9 zagotavlja pravo športno obdelavo vašega TRACER 9. Paket Sport daje motociklu tisto nekaj več, s čimer lahko prilagodite svoj motocikel po svoji želji. Hitro prestavljanje Quick Shifter vam omogoča hitro menjavo prestav, kolenske blazinice pa dajejo dodatni oprijem kolenom med nagibanjem v ovinkih. Z elegantnim nosilcem registrske tablice je zadek videti lepše, moderno zasnovani stranski ščitniki pa ščitijo motor pred neželenimi trenutki.

description.en: Created for comfort and shade on hot sunny days, the Paddock Blue Bucket Hat Black is a simple and eye-catching standout of the Streetwear range. Made from 100% cotton  in one size fits all, it features inner custom taping and embroidered Yamaha branding. A simple and easy to carry item for sunny days out.

Made from 100% cotton  in one size fits all, it features inner custom taping and embroidered Yamaha branding. A simple and easy to carry item for sunny days out.

Izdelan je iz recikliranega poliestra in bombaža, tkanina hitreje odvaja vlago in ima mrežaste dele za zračnost. Natisnjena logotipa Yamaha in Alpinestars izdelek ikonsko zaključujeta.

Paket Racer Pack, ki je zasnovan na podlagi Caferacerja, vsebuje dirkaške pokrove in naslone za noge, stranske obloge rezervoarja za gorivo, aluminijaste stranske zaščitne ploščice in zelo moderen nosilec registrske tablice 2.0.

The tight-fitted shirt offers excellent ventilation, insulation and protection, perfect for training days. The high-tech Drylight fabric provides quick perspiration absorption, ensuring great comfort while wearing. And the special Durafit design provides more protection to exposed areas. Tesno prilegajoča se majica nudi odlično prezračevanje, izolacijo in zaščito ter je popolna za treninge. description.en: Crafted in black and red from organic and recycled fabrics, the REVS zip hoodie for men gives maximum form and function outdoors. A 3-panel hood with integrated stoppers helps keep out the elements with bonded zippered front pockets to keep your hands warm. A blend of organic cotton and recycled polyester make this a standout piece, with strong Yamaha branding on the chest, back and sleeve combined in a typically eye-catching REVS look.
description.sl-SI: Moški pulover s kapuco REVS na zadrgo v črno-rdeči barvi, izdelan iz ekološko pridelanih in recikliranih tkanin, omogoča odličen videz in funkcionalnost pri nošnji na prostem. Tridelna kapuca z integriranimi zapirali pomaga ohranjati toploto, sprednja varjena žepa z zadrgo pa zagotavljata tople roke. To vpadljivo oblačilo je izdelano iz mešanice ekološko pridelanega bombaža in recikliranega poliestra, z izrazito Yamahino grafiko na prsih, hrbtu in rokavu pa je dosežen klasičen izstopajoč videz linije REVS.

Moška avanturistična motoristična jakna, ki je zasnovana za večsezonsko uporabo, je lahka in zračna ter zagotavlja dovolj zaščite za samozavestno vožnjo. Zasnovana je v klasičnih modrih in zemeljsko rjavih odtenkih, ima vodoodporno membrano Drystar, ki se lahko uporablja kot notranja ali zunanja plast, odstranljive rokave za udobje in zračenje ter več notranjih in zunanjih žepov za nujne potrebščine. Zaščita za ramena in komolce stopnje 2 zagotavlja zaščito, z nastavljivim pasom in rokavi za optimalno udobje. Zložljive sprednje in zadnje prezračevalne zaplate skrbijo za odlično zračenje, dolga zadrga v pasu pa omogoča pritrditev jakne na avanturistične motoristične hlače. Popolna jakna za neustrašnega raziskovalca!
description.en: Designed for multi-season use, the Adventure Men’s Riding Jacket is lightweight and breathable, with ample protection for confident riding. Created in classic blue and earthy brown tones, it features a waterproof Drystar membrane can be used as internal or external layer, removable sleeves for comfort and breathability, and multiple inner and outer pockets for essentials. Level 2 shoulder and elbow protection affords protection, with adjustable waist and sleeves for optimal comfort. Foldable front and back ventilation panels offer excellent breathability, with a long waist zip for attaching the jacket to the Adventure Riding Pants. The perfect jacket for the intrepid explorer!
Stainless mesh radiator guard, providing added protection from rocks and other road debris.

Športni paket povzdigne vašo Yamaho XMAX na naslednjo raven sloga skuterja. Športni paket XMAX vsebuje športni vizir XMAX, nosilec registrske tablice in njegov pokrov, sprednje in zadnje zavorne ročice, izdelane izključno za Yamaha XMAX.
description.en: The Sport Pack takes your Yamaha XMAX to the next level of scooter style. The XMAX Sport Pack comprises the XMAX Sport Screen, License Plate Holder and its cover, front and rear brake levers and end grips, all made exclusively for the Yamaha XMAX.

The XMAX is personification of what a sporty scooter should be. However we always trying to push the boundary and with the Sport pack for the XMAX, we aim to take it to an even higher level. Intensify the sporty spirit of your XMAX with the Sports pack. The sports pack contains sports screen, license plate holder, aluminium end grip and aluminium foot panel – the perfect combination of sports style and flair.  And the Sports Pack is just the beginning: truly personalize your XMAX by adding other accessories from the vast selection of XMAX Genuine accessories as well.
description.sl-SI: XMAX je točno tak, kot bi moral biti športni skuter. Vendar pa vedno poskušamo premikati meje in s kompletom Sport za XMAX ga želimo popeljati na še višjo raven. Še intenzivnejši športni duh XMAX-a s kompletom Sport. Komplet Sport vključuje športni vizir, nosilec registrske tablice, aluminijaste ročaje in aluminijaste plošče stopalk – popolna kombinacija športnega sloga in elegance.  Komplet Sport je šele začetek: izbirate lahko med širokim naborom originalne dodatne opreme XMAX in popolnoma personalizirate svoj XMAX.

description.sl-SI: Nadgradite svoj TRACER 7 s športnim paketom za dinamično izkušnjo vožnje, ki združuje slog in zmogljivosti. Zaporedni smerniki LED dajejo vašemu motornemu kolesu sodoben videz, hkrati pa izboljšajo vidljivost na cesti. Sistem za hitro prestavljanje CP2 zagotavlja gladko in hitro menjavo prestav. Zaščitite motorno kolo s stranskimi zaščitami in dopolnite športno estetiko s poenostavljenim nosilcem registrske tablice. Komplet TRACER 7 'Sport Pack' vključuje vse, kar potrebujete za nadgradnjo vožnje z natančnostjo in slogom.
description.en: Upgrade your TRACER 7 with the Sport Pack for a dynamic riding experience that combines style and performance. The Sequential LED Blinkers give your bike a modern look while enhancing visibility on the road. The Quick Shifter CP2 ensures smooth and fast gear changes. The TRACER 7 Sport Pack delivers everything you need to elevate your ride with precision and style.

description.en: Elegant and sleek, the Racing Heritage softshell for men is an instant reminiscence of historic Yamaha racing design. The recycled polyester and elastane fabrics provide great comfort and mobility, and this off-white softshell is highlighted with a bold printed red speed block graphic across the chest. Inner fleece lining ensures extra warmth, while a black zipper contrasts with red zipped pockets. Strong white Yamaha branding on the chest and Yamaha Racing Heritage Club logo on the arm sets off the whole look.
description.sl-SI: Elegantna in dovršena softshell jakna Racing Heritage za moške predstavlja spomin na zgodovinski Yamahin dirkalni videz. Softshell jakna iz recikliranega poliestra in elastana zagotavlja odlično udobje in mobilnost, je umazano bele barve in ima drzno natisnjeno grafiko 'Speedblock' čez cel prsni koš. Notranja podloga iz flisa zagotavlja dodatno toplino, medtem ko črna zadrga predstavlja kontrast žepoma z rdečo zadrgo. Poudarjen bel Yamahin logotip na prsih in logotip Yamaha Racing Heritage Club na rokavu zaključita celotno podobo.

description.en: The city is the XMAX's natural habitat and with the Urban Accessories Pack you can take the practicality of your XMAX a notch higher. Besides providing enhanced wind protection from the high screen, the pack also takes care of your luggage needs with a 50L top case and carrier – keeping your belonging safe and secure. And a backrest for the top case makes sure the passenger has an equally comfortable ride. To protect you from the scratches and the scruffs the city throws up, the pack contains the XMAX scratch protector. Urban Pack Content: High Screen | Rear Carrier | 50L Top Case (incl. Lock Key Set) | Backrest for 50L Top Case | Scratch protector

Komplet TRACER 9 'Travel Pack Pro' je vrhunski sklop opreme za voznike, ki zahtevajo udobje, priročnost in vsestranskost. Visok vizir in dodaten širok zaščitni vizir zagotavljata odlično zaščito pred vetrom, ogrevan udoben sedež in sopotnikov sedež pa prinašata udobje med dolgimi vožnjami. V opremo so vključeni sistem za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah (TPMS) in ogrevane ročke, da lahko vozite samozavestno ne glede na vremenske razmere. Zgornji kovček in stranska kovčka ponujajo dovolj prostora za shranjevanje vseh vaših bistvenih stvari, medtem ko polnilnik USB in vtičnica držala ohranjata vaše naprave pripravljene in dostopne.

Nosilec za GPS omogoča enostavno uporabo navigacije, zaradi ščitnika hladilnika in zaščite agregata 'Explorer' pa je vožnja še bolj brezskrbna. Komplet meglenk LED in nosilec za meglenke zagotavljata optimalno vidljivost v vseh pogojih. Zavarujte vso svojo opremo z nosilno ploščo za zgornji kovček, kompleti nosilcev in kompletom ključev za cilindrično ključavnico za hiter dostop. S paketom TRACER 9 'Travel Pack Pro' je vsaka pustolovščina brezhibna mešanica sloga, udobja in funkcionalnosti.
description.en:
The TRACER 9 Travel Pack Pro is the ultimate setup for riders who demand comfort, convenience, and versatility. The High Screen and Add-On Wide Screen provide excellent wind protection, while the Heated Comfort Seat and Passenger Seat keep both you and your passenger comfortable during long rides. Equipped with a Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS) and Heated Grips, you can ride confidently, no matter the weather. The Top Case and Side Cases offer ample storage for all your essentials, while the USB Charger and Holder Socket keep your devices ready and accessible.

Navigate easily with the GPS Stay, and ride with peace of mind knowing your bike is protected by the Radiator Guard and Explorer Engine Guard. The LED Fog Light Kit and Fog Light Stay ensure optimal visibility in any conditions. Secure all your gear with the Top Case Mounting Plate, Stay Kits, and Key Cylinder Set for quick access. With the TRACER 9 Travel Pack Pro, every adventure is a seamless blend of style, comfort, and function.

description.en: The Yamaha R-Series Leather Racing Suit is designed to provide you all the freedom of movement you need, to give you that edge on the race track. Manufactured from flexible cowhide and featuring aramid-reinforced arm and leg panels, removable knee and elbow sliders as well as an aerodynamic hump, this CE certified one-piece suit offers superior abrasion resistance and maximum protection. The micro-perforation in the front panels combined with mesh lining offer plenty of ventilation to keep you cool and comfortable under pressure.
description.sl-SI: Usnjena dirkalna obleka Yamaha R-Series je zasnovana tako, da vam zagotavlja vso svobodo gibanja, ki jo potrebujete za prednost na dirkališču. Ta enodelni kombinezon s certifikatom CE, ki je narejen iz gibljivega kravjega usnja, ščitniki za roke in noge, snemljivi ščitniki za kolena in komolce ter aerodinamična zaščita za hrbet pa imajo ojačitev iz aramida, je odlično odporen proti abraziji in ponuja največjo zaščito. Mikro-perforacija na sprednjih panelih v kombinaciji z mrežasto podlogo zagotavlja obilico prezračevanja, da vam bo v zahtevnih razmerah prijetno in udobno.

Taillights are included in both upgrade kits.
description.sl-SI: Z zadnjimi lučmi UMX je vaš UMX viden ponoči ali v razmerah z nizko osvetlitvijo. Opremljene so s ščitnikom iz materiala GORE-TEX®, ki preprečuje poškodbe zaradi vlage ali kondenzacije. Za funkcije zavornih luči in smernikov je potreben vrhunski nadgradni komplet luči (J0G-H4503-T0-00) ali ultra vrhunski nadgradni komplet luči (J0G-H4503-S0-00); oba sta naprodaj ločeno. Zadnje luči so vključene v oba nadgradna kompleta.

description.en: Ténéré 700 is built to take you off the beaten track and move you over to new horizons. The Explorer Pack contains the complete ensemble of accessories to support this journey of discovery. The aluminium side cases with 72L capacity ensure you have enough space to pack up and go at a moment's notice. To carry even extra luggage, the Explorer Pack features an easily mountable mono seat rack, with flat surface, that allows faster setting up of additional bags. With all that luggage, it's imperative to have good bike stability when parked and that's why the Explorer Pack is equipped with a center stand. For added protection, the pack also features a skid plate and an engine guard, so your Ténéré 700 can withstand those long-distance travels. Are you ready to make the next horizon yours?
description.sl-SI: Ténéré 700 je ustvarjen za to, da vas odpelje z običajnih cest in vam odpre nova obzorja. Paket Explorer vsebuje vso dodatno opremo, ki jo potrebujete za takšne raziskovalne izlete v neznano. Aluminijasta kovčka s prostornino 72 litrov vam zagotavljata dovolj prostora za prtljago, zato se lahko na pot odpravite brez posebnih priprav. Paket Explorer vsebuje še prtljažnik za dodatno prtljago za enojni sedež, ki ga lahko preprosto namestite, na njegovo ravno površino pa lahko hitro pritrdite dodatne torbe. Vsa ta količina prtljage zahteva stabilno parkiranje, zato je paket Explorer opremljen tudi s sredinskim stojalom. Za dodatno zaščito paket vključuje še drsno ploščo in ščitnik motorja, da vaš Ténéré 700 prenese tudi najdaljša potovanja. Ste pripravljeni, da osvojite naslednje obzorje?

Na voljo je kot uniseks model v črni barvi z rdečimi in belimi kontrastnimi črtami ter je izjemno praktična zaradi univerzalne velikosti. Vezena značka Yamaha doda zadnji pridih slogu REVS.

Black with red and white contrast stripes, its unisex fit is also one-size-fits-all for ultimate practicality. An embroidered Yamaha badge adds a final touch of REVS style.
These overfenders feature a tough, aggressive look and a custom formed design that helps protect you from water, mud, and other trail debris.
