description.en: The ideal Travel gear for your TRACER 9 GT to hit the road in full functional style. The high screen and Comfort Seat provide the extra comfort for those long endless roads. The Top Case give you the perfect tool to take your belongings along with your endeavors together with the TRACER 9 GT Side Cases. Charge your phone easily with the USB Charger and it's Holder Socket. Your passenger will enjoy the comfort of the Backrest.
description.sl-SI: Idealna potovalna oprema za vaš TRACER 9 GT. Odpravite se na pot z uporabnim slogom. Visok zaščitni vizir in udoben sedež nudita več udobja na neskončnih cestah. Zgornji kovček je v kombinaciji s stranskima kovčkoma za TRACER 9 GT odličen za prevoz lastnine na popotovanjih. Telefon enostavno napolnite s polnilnikom USB in vtičnico na nosilcu. Vaš potnik bo užival v udobju naslonjala.

description.en: A smart and elegantly designed garment, the Racing Heritage polo shirt for men with button closure gives you that classic racing look. The organic cotton and elastane blend ensures mobility and comfort, while the off-white body contrasts nicely with the iconic red speed block graphic on the chest and the red colour block on the upper back. The racing heritage look is completed with the white Yamaha logo inside the speed block graphic on the chest and black Yamaha logo on the back.
description.sl-SI: Moška polo majica Racing Heritage za moške z zapenjanjem na gumbe vam z elegantnim oblikovanjem daje klasičen tekmovalni videz. Mešanica ekološko pridelanega bombaža in elastana zagotavlja mobilnost in udobje. Srednji del v beli barvi predstavlja lep kontrast ikonični rdeči grafiki 'Speedblock' na prsih in rdeče obarvanemu delu na zgornji hrbtni strani. Videz v slogu dirkaške dediščine je zaključen z belim logotipom Yamaha znotraj grafike 'Speedblock' na prsih in črnim logotipom Yamaha na zadnji strani.

The Universal Phone Clamp is designed to fit your smartphone with or without standard phone cases. Engineered with high-quality materials, the Universal Phone Clamp will ensure a tight and secure grip on your device while you focus on the road.

Glossy resin-type with Dark-side of Japan exclusive logo and design.

description.sl-SI: Vrhunski potovalni paket za vaš TRACER 9 za udobno in elegantno raziskovanje odprte ceste. Visok vizir in udoben sedež prinašata največje možno udobje na daljših potovanjih. 45-litrski zgornji kovček in stranski torbi so idealna rešitev za shranjevanje vseh vaših potrebščin. S polnilnikom USB in vtičnico na nosilcu enostavno poskrbite, da so vaše naprave napolnjene in dostopne. Vse varno pritrdite z nosilno ploščo za zgornji kovček ter kompleti spodnjih in zgornjih nosilcev, poleg tega pa lahko uporabite še komplet ključev za cilindrično ključavnico za hiter dostop do potrebščin.
description.en: The ultimate Travel Pack for your TRACER 9 to explore the open road in comfort and style. The High Screen and Comfort Seat deliver maximum comfort on those extended journeys. With the 45L Top Case and Side Cases, you have the ideal storage solutions to carry all your gear. The USB Charger and Holder Socket make it easy to keep your devices powered and accessible. Mount everything securely with the Top Case Mounting Plate, Lower and Upper Stay Kits, and enjoy the convenience of the Key Cylinder Set for quick access to your belongings.

description.en:
The powerful CP4 engine and lightweight chassis that deliver the ultimate balance between power, agility and stability make the MT-10 the perfect bike for a weekend away filled with adrenaline and torque.
So we have created the Weekend Pack to make sure you enjoy every moment whether you're on or off the bike. 
Gear up for a revving weekend trip!
description.sl-SI:
Zmogljiv motor CP4 in lahka šasija zagotavljata popolno ravnovesje med močjo, okretnostjo in stabilnostjo, zato je MT-10 popoln motor za vikend, poln adrenalina in navora.
V ta namen smo ustvarili dodatno opremo 'Weekend Pack', da boste uživali v vsakem trenutku, ko ste na motorju ali pa tudi ne. 
Pripravite se na vikend izlet "pri višjih obratih"!

description.en: Stylish and at home at the track or outdoors, the two-tone Paddock Blue Men’s Softshell Jacket is ideal for regular active use. A blend of polyester and spandex for comfort and freedom of movement, this jacket features a full-length zip and three external pockets for ease of use. Embroidered Yamaha Racing branding and back stripe graphic add a final premium feel.

Izdelana je iz poliestra in elastana za udobje in večjo svobodo pri gibanju, ima pa tudi zadrgo po celotni dolžini in tri zunanje žepe za preprosto uporabo. Izvezen logotip Yamaha Racing in grafika črte na hrbtu vzbujata pridih vrhunskosti.
Za tople roke med vožnjo v mrzlem vremenu izberite grelce ročk. Ta par električno ogrevanih ročk nadomešča standardne ročke Yamaha XMAX za ogrevanje na zahtevo, skozi vse leto.
description.en: Choose the Grip Heaters for warm hands in cold riding conditions. This pair of electrically heated hand grips replaces the standard Yamaha XMAX scooter grips for heat on demand, all year round.

Yamalube Brake Cleaner is the ideal fluid for cleaning and degreasing brake and clutch components as well as many other parts on your machine. Its special formula rapidly dissolves and removes oil, grease, tar spots, brake fluid and dirt – and being non-corrosive, it won’t harm rubber, plastic or paint.
description.sl-SI: Čistilo za zavore Yamalube je idealna tekočina za čiščenje in razmaščevanje zavor in komponent sklopke ter številnih drugih delov na vašem vozilu. Posebna formula se hitro raztopi in odstrani olje, mast, madeže katrana, zavorno tekočino in umazanijo – ker ni jedka, ne škodi gumi, plastiki ali barvi.

description.en: Specially formulated to meet Yamaha’s own very high standards, this advanced oil features additives to guard against friction, wear, foam and corrosion. The result is consistent protection for the suspension and the delivery of safer and more precise handling.
description.sl-SI: Posebej izdelano čistilo, ki izpolnjuje lastne visoke standarde družbe Yamaha. Napredni aditivi z lastnostmi olja preprečujejo trenje, obrabo, penjenje in korozijo. Rezultat je dosledna zaščita za vzmetenje in zagotavljanje bolj varnega ter natančnega delovanja.

With its compact dimension, the lightweight and dual leaning front wheels, Tricity represents the best solution for every day commuting. But who said that can’t go hand in hand with a sporty experience? The Sport pack adds a sleek look, while the Tricity loses none of its convenience. The smoke-tinted sport screen comes in a short dynamic shape. This is further enhanced by the backrest base alongside the cushion to ensure passengers are comfortable, while the sportier silhouette heightens the dynamic nature of the scooter.
Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your Tricity.

Te lastnosti pa se lepo skladajo tudi s športno vožnjo. Paket Sport poskrbi za eleganten videz, medtem pa Tricity ohrani svoje udobje. Zatemnjen športni vizir je kratke, dinamične oblike. Za udobje potnikov je še dodatno poskrbljeno z nosilcem za naslon poleg blazine, športna oblika pa poveča dinamičnost skuterja.
Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš Tricity.

description.sl-SI:
TRACER 9 GT 'Travel Pack Pro' je zasnovan za voznike, ki iščejo maksimalno udobje, varnost in funkcionalnost na dolgih razdaljah. Visok vizir v kombinaciji z dodatnim širokim zaščitnim vizirjem omogoča boljšo zaščito pred vetrom, ogrevan udoben sedež in sopotnikov udoben sedež pa vozniku in sopotniku prinašata toploto in sproščenost. Ohranite nadzor s kompletom za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah in sistemom za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah (TPMS) na krmilu, nosilec za GPS pa omogoča jasen pregled nad navigacijo. Zgornji kovček in naslon zagotavljata veliko prostora za shranjevanje in udobje sopotnika, s polnilnikom USB z vtičnico na nosilcu pa poskrbite, da so vaše naprave vedno napolnjene.

Za dodatno zaščito pred kamenčki na cesti se namestita ščitnik hladilnika in zaščita agregata 'Explorer', komplet meglenk LED z nosilcem za meglenke pa zagotavlja vidljivost v vseh pogojih. Ta paket je popoln spremljevalec za vsako pustolovščino na vašem TRACER 9 GT.
description.en:
The TRACER 9 GT Travel Pack Pro is built for riders seeking maximum comfort, safety, and functionality on long-distance rides. The High Screen, paired with the Add-On Wide Screen, enhances wind protection, while the Heated Comfort Seat and Passenger Comfort Seat ensure warmth and relaxation for both rider and passenger. Stay in control with the Tire Pressure Monitoring Kit and TPMS on the handlebar, while the GPS Stay keeps your navigation in clear view. The Top Case and Backrest provide ample storage and comfort for your passenger, and the USB Charger with Holder Socket ensures your devices remain powered.

For added protection, the Radiator Guard and Explorer Engine Guard shield your bike from road debris, and the LED Fog Light Kit with Fog Light Stay ensures visibility in all conditions. This pack  is the ultimate companion for every adventure on your TRACER 9 GT.

Yamaha motorcycles are meant to be used all year long and that is why it is important to have accessories that make every day usage a breeze.
The Urban Pack contains a rear carrier along with a 45 L top case to keep your valuables securely and with ease. While the motorcycle charges you up with energy, the USB outlet is there to charge your electronic devices. And finally, there is a stylish short screen to protect you from wind or whatever the city throws at you!

description.en: Use the SP Connect™ Brake Mount to mount your SP Connect™ Phone Case or Universal Interface to your motorcycle in seconds. You can easily attach the Brake Mount to your maxi scooter by screwing it onto the lid of the brake fluid reservoir. This is also a great mounting solution for other motorcycles with limited access to the handlebars. Due to the multiple adjustment possibilities, your mobile phone is securely positioned in your field of vision, allowing you to navigate, access your playlists or use other apps without taking your eyes off the road.
description.sl-SI: Z zavornim nosilcem SP Connect™ na motorno kolo v nekaj sekundah namestite svoje ohišje za mobilni telefon SP Connect™ ali univerzalni vmesnik. Zavorni nosilec lahko preprosto pritrdite na svoj maksi skuter tako, da ga privijete na pokrov rezervoarja zavorne tekočine. To je tudi odlična rešitev za montažo pri drugih motornih kolesih z omejenim dostopom do krmila. Zaradi več možnosti prilagajanja je vaš mobilni telefon varno nameščen v vidnem polju, kar vam omogoča navigacijo, dostop do seznamov predvajanja ali uporabo drugih aplikacij, ne da bi pri tem pogled umaknili s ceste.

Verige za časa svoje življenjske dobe delujejo v težkih, nevarnih in zelo stresnih okoliščinah, tudi če so čiste. Zato z vsako izboljšavo na področju tehnologije mazanja podaljšujemo življenjsko dobo verige. Ne pozabite, čista in dobro namazana veriga bolj gladko teče. Ne gre pa samo za zaščito pred obrabo, dandanes veliko pozornosti posvečamo tudi lastnosti maziva, ki poskrbi, da sredstvo ostane na mestu nanosa. V tem pršilu Yamalube je formula, ki ji ni para.
description.en: A chain lives a tough, dangerous and extremely stressful life, even when it’s kept clean! So every improvement we make in lube technology is geared to add more life to it, and remember ,a clean, well-lubricated chain is a smoother-running chain! It’s not all about protection against wear though – these days we place great importance on the ‘throw-off’ behavior of the lubricant and in this Yamalube spray is a formula that’s hard to beat..

Made out of heavy duty plastic, these bags are designed to hold shape and stand up on their own. After a day of boating, cleanse your engine with fresh water. Just fill the bag until the water passes the intake inlets and idle your engine in neutral for 5 to 10 minutes. Finally, unscrew the drain plug and let the water flow out.

Je udobnega kroja z raglan rokavi in zadrgo po celotni dolžini, na voljo pa sta tudi sprednja žepa z zadrgo, ki ponujata dovolj prostora. Fiksna kapuca, sešita iz treh tretjin, ščiti pred vremenskimi vplivi, izvezeni napis Yamaha na prsnem košu in grafika navpične črte zadaj pa se dopolnjujeta z belo obrobo na ramenih in poudarjata klasičen videz kolekcije REVS.
description.en: Produced in slick black with red highlights, the stylish REVS Men’s Softshell Jacket is a polyester elastane blend, fleece-lined to keep you comfortable outdoors. A relax fit with raglan sleeves and a full-length zip, it also features two front zip pockets offering ample space. A 3-panel fixed hood keeps the elements out, while embroidered Yamaha chest branding and backstripe graphic combine with white shoulder piping for a classic REVS outdoor look.

A flexible blend of leather and polyester materials ensures mobility and dexterity, with softshell knuckle protection for peace of mind. Touch screen material allows easy smartphone use, while the short cuff and polar fleece lining offer comfort in all urban conditions.

It’s perfect for sports, road and off-road bikes, trail machines, scooters, ATVs, and quads. Maximum engine protection for the hardest riding in the harshest conditions.

name.sl-SI: Moška majica REVS s kratkimi rokavi

description.en: Available in black or grey melange, the REVS t-shirt for men blends contemporary style with classic Yamaha design. Shaped for a comfort fit this crew neck t-shirt is an all-weather, all-round garment for everyday use. Containing a mix of organic and recycled materials, it features bold Yamaha logo branding on the chest and sleeve, with a printed sleeve red stripe and perforated back stripe. An instant, cool REVS classic.
description.sl-SI: Moška majica REVS s kratkimi rokavi, na voljo v črni ali sivi tkanini, združuje sodobni slog s klasičnim Yamahinim oblikovanjem. To vsestransko oblačilo za vsakodnevno uporabo ima udoben kroj in okrogel izrez. Majica je izdelana iz mešanice ekološko pridelanih in recikliranih materialov, ima drzno Yamahino podobo na prsih in rokavu, z natisnjeno rdečo črto na rokavu in prekinjeno črto na hrbtu. Nova REVS klasika.

name.sl-SI: Kratka majica Paddock Blue Essentials za otroke

description.en: Bright, cool and stylish, the Paddock Blue Essentials Kid’s T-Shirt is the perfect garment for young Yamaha fans. 100% cotton construction means a consistently soft feel, with a crew neck ensuring a comfortable fit for any youngster. Printed Yamaha chest and arm branding give an iconic paddock style.
description.sl-SI: Svetla, mladostna in stilska kratka majica Paddock Blue Essentials za otroke je popoln kos oblačila za mlade Yamahine navdušence. Izdelana je iz 100-odstotnega bombaža, kar pomeni, da je na vseh mestih mehka na dotik, okrogli izrez pa se udobno prilega prav vsakemu otroku. Yamahina logotipa na prsih in rokavu poskrbita za ikonski dirkaški slog.

description.en: Modern LED tail light which gives your unit a nice touch of modern flavour in combination with an authentic look.
description.sl-SI: Sodobna zadnja LED-luč, ki daje sodoben pridih enoti s pristnim videzom.

description.en:
The Tricity is an embodiment of convenience, making commuting simple, easy and fun. With such high dose of practicality, the Urban pack is aimed at increasing the options for Customers to offer additional comfort and space through its various accessories. The high screen provides greater protection against wind, meaning your journeys will never be tiring or uncomfortable. To increase the storage space, we included the rear carrier and the 39L top case. The passenger’s comfort is also of upmost importance and hence we include the backrest pad for the top case. 
Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your Tricity.
description.sl-SI:
Tricity je simbol udobja, zato je vsakodnevna vožnja preprosta in zabavna. Paket Urban je izredno praktičen in z različnimi dodatki uporabniku omogoča boljše udobje v vožnji in več prostora. Visok vizir poskrbi za boljšo zaščito pred vetrom, kar pomeni, da vaša vožnja nikoli ne bo utrujajoča ali neudobna. Vključen zadnji nosilec in 39-litrski kovček priskrbita več prostora za shranjevanje. Zelo pomembno pa je tudi udobje potnika, zato smo zgornjemu kovčku priložili tudi blazino za naslon. 
Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš Tricity.

description.en: Enjoy every moment of the city with the Scooter graphic t-shirt for men. Designed in unison with the new Yamaha scooter range, this grey t-shirt benefits from an organic cotton and viscose blend for supreme comfort and mobility. A brightly coloured Yamaha MOVE LIVE LOVE print in a central pop-up style adds an extra stylish twist.
description.sl-SI: Uživajte v mestnem utripu z moško majico z grafiko skuterja. Siva majica je zasnovana v podobi nove serije Yamahinih skuterjev. Izdelana je iz mešanice ekološko pridelanega bombaža in viskoze za vrhunsko udobje in gibljivost. Živahen Yamahin napis MOVE LIVE LOVE dodaja zanimiv vizualen element.

description.sl-SI:
Sprejmite najboljše iz obeh svetov s paketom 'Comfort', ki je zasnovan tako, da združuje drzen in agresiven videz MT-07 z dodatnim udobjem, potrebnim za daljše vožnje. Vizir srednje višine v kombinaciji s ščitniki členkov povečuje zaščito pred vetrom, tako da je vsaka vožnja bolj gladka, udobni sedeži za voznika in sopotnika pa še dodatno izboljšujejo celotno izkušnjo vožnje. 

Vsebuje: Večnamenska osnova, vizir srednje višine, osnova zaključka krmila, zaščita rok, udoben voznikov in sovoznikov sedež.
description.en:
Embrace the best of both worlds with the Comfort Pack, designed to combine the bold and aggressive look of the MT-07 with the extra comfort needed for longer rides. The Middle Screen paired with the Knuckle Deflectors enhance wind protection making every ride smoother, while Comfort Seats for both rider and passenger add to that experience. 

Contains: Multi-Mount Base, Middle Screen, Bar End Base, Knuckle Deflectors, Rider and Passenger Comfort Seats.

Designed exclusively for female riders, the nylon/polyester riding jacket and pants are the ideal sport touring gear. The jacket and pants have a minimalistic design, and feature a removable thermal lining and fixed waterproof lining. This set of sport touring riding gear gives you the comfort and flexibility you need to enjoy every ride, whatever the weather.
description.sl-SI: Ta motoristična jakna in hlače iz najlona/poliestra so zasnovane ekskluzivno za voznice in so idealna oprema za športno potovalno vožnjo. Jakna in hlače imajo minimalistično obliko ter snemljivo toplotno podlogo in fiksno vodoodporno podlogo. Ta komplet motoristične opreme za športno potovalno vožnjo je udoben in prilagodljiv, da lahko uživate v vsaki vožnji, ne glede na vreme.

name.sl-SI: 2023 - Moška majica s kratkimi rokavi Fabio Quartararo

description.en: A standout blue and red t-shirt that fans of ‘El Diablo’ will simply love!  This Fabio Quartararo t-shirt for men is perfect for cheering on France’s first MotoGP World Champion from the grandstands or at home. 100% cotton in Yamaha Factory Racing blue, the t-shirt features the iconic red ‘20’ same as on Fabio’s suit and M1 bike, with a red striped background. White Yamaha Factory Racing and M1 logos on the front, sleeve and neck complete the racy look of this highly comfortable and easy-to-wear item.
description.sl-SI: Izstopajoča majica s kratkimi rokavi v rdeči in modri barvi, ki jo bodo navijači »El Diabla« preprosto oboževali!  Ta majica s kratkimi rokavi Fabio Quartararo za moške je kot nalašč za navijanje za francoskega svetovnega prvaka na prvenstvu MotoGP na tribuni ali doma. Majica s kratkimi rokavi je iz 100-odstotnega bombaža v modri barvi ekipe Yamaha Factory Racing in ima ikonsko rdečo številko »20«, enako kot na Fabijevi obleki in motornem kolesu M1, z rdečimi črtami od zadaj. Bela logotipa ekip Yamaha Factory Racing in M1 spredaj, na rokavih in vratu izpopolnita dirkaški videz tega zelo udobnega in lahkotnega kosa oblačila.

description.en:
Attach your SP Connect Phone Case or other SP ConnectTM compatible devices to your MTB with the BAR MOUNT PRO MTB. 
The mount is CNC milled out of aircraft-grade aluminum and fits standard and oversized handlebars. To further protect your smartphone the mount also has a unique vibration-dampening system that cuts G-forces by up to 40% (depending on bike & phone model). You can mount it with the positioning arm or as a direct clamp mount - both versions allow 360° rotation to find the perfect position.
description.sl-SI:
Priključite svoje ohišje za telefon SP Connect ali druge naprave, združljive s sistemom SP ConnectTM, na vozilo z nosilcem za krmilo PRO MTB. 
Nosilec je narejen iz aluminija, primernega za letalsko industrijo in izrezanega na CNC stroju, ter se prilega standardnim in velikim krmilom. Za dodatno zaščito pametnega telefona ima nosilec tudi edinstven sistem za blaženje tresljajev, ki zmanjša gravitacijske pospeške do 40 % (odvisno od modela motorja in telefona). Namestite lahko nosilec z roko ali neposredno kot objemko z nosilcem – obe različici omogočata 360° vrtenje, da najdete popoln položaj.

description.en: The Ténéré GYTR Handling Kit has been meticulously engineered to get your bike's chassis ready for rally. Featuring race-developed 48mm KYB closed cartridge forks with DLC coated tubes and increased stroke, alongside a GYTR triple clamp assembly and fully adjustable steering damper manufactured by Scotts Performance, this kit ensures superior stability and control over rough terrain. Paired with a Paioli shock absorber, GYTR rally wheels prepared by Haan Wheels, upgraded braking system with Brembo calipers and GYTR ECU for ABS system deletion, these enhancements improve the off-road capability of your Ténéré. Complete with a lightweight chain and sprocket set, new radiator assembly with oil cooler and GYTR radiator guard, as well as a high front fender, this kit equips you to conquer any off-road challenge with confidence and precision.

Commute and explore with comfort and protection in the Scooter Women’s Riding Jacket. Designed in a stylish two-tone grey combo, this fully waterproof jacket offers level 2 shoulder and elbow protection, a removable thermo lining and neoprene-lined collar for both peace of mind warmth in all weathers. A detachable hood offers comfort, with straps to adjust the arm fit. Ventilation on the arms and back keep you cool in warm weather. The jacket also pairs with Yamaha Scooter Riding Gloves for the complete urban mobility outfit.

description.en: Kit out your Yamaha XMAX for winter with the Winter Pack, featuring the XMAX Apron, Heated Seat and Grip Heaters. Essential items for winter weather scooter riding and comfort in colder months.

With its compact dimensions and the excellent fuel efficiency the NMAX thrives in the hustle and bustle of the urban environment. To ensure space and comfort, the Urban pack offers the best experience for riding in those built-up areas. The high screen provides robust protection against wind, while it remains resistant to scratches and impact damage thanks to its hard-coated polycarbonate design. The 39L top case offers all the extra space you need and rests on a beautiful piece of alloy rear carrier, with its integrated design and rigorous testing guaranteeing year-after-year security and peace of mind while riding. The lockset for the top case comes included in the pack, while the back rest provides the rear passenger with optimum comfort. The Urban pack will make the NMAX your best friend in the city. 
Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your NMAX.
description.sl-SI:
S kompaktnimi dimenzijami in odličnim izkoristkom goriva je model NMAX popolna izbira za uporabo v vrvežu urbanega okolja. Paket Urban zagotavlja dovolj prostora in udobja, zato omogoča kar najboljšo vožnjo po gosto pozidanih območjih. Visok vizir zagotavlja zanesljivo zaščito pred vetrom, zaradi polikarbonatne zasnove s trdo prevleko pa je odporen tudi na praske in poškodbe ob trku. 39-litrski zgornji kovček poskrbi za dodaten prostor, nameščen pa je na čudovitem zadnjem nosilcu iz zlitine. Z integrirano zasnovo in po izvedbi striktnih testov zagotavlja varnost in brezskrbnost med vožnjo. Komplet ključavnice za zgornji kovček je priložen, naslon sedeža pa potniku zadaj omogoča optimalno udobje. S paketom Urban bo model NMAX postal vaš najboljši prijatelj za vožnjo po mestu. 
Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš model NMAX.

Seamless sleeves and hem add real style, with embroidered Yamaha chest branding, backstripe graphic and white shoulder piping that offsets this classy look.

description.sl-SI: To je najboljši partner za mazanje vašega motorja, ko se vzpenjate na območja z res nizko temperaturo ali pa se na jasno, ledeno jutro odpravite na teren pri nizkih temperaturah. To je popolnoma sintetično olje vrhunske kakovosti, izdelano posebej zato, da izpolnjuje in presega zelo visoke standarde, ki jih postavljamo za vse 4-taktne agregate pri snežnih saneh Yamaha ter za menjalnike pri dvotaktnih modelih. name.en: SP Connect™ Bar Clamp Mount Pro
name.sl-SI: Nosilec na krmilu SP Connect™ Pro

description.en:
The SP Connect™ Bar Clamp Mount Pro lets you mount your smartphone to your motorcycle in seconds. The Bar Clamp Mount Pro also has a swiveling and rotating head so your smartphone can always be positioned perfectly. 
Just screw this sleek aluminium mount to the bar clamp of your motorbike and you are ready to mount the SP Connect™ PHONE CASE (or UNIVERSAL INTERFACE) by placing it on the mount and turning it 90° clockwise. Your mobile phone is securely positioned in your field of vision, allowing you to navigate, access your playlists.
description.sl-SI:
Z nosilcem na krmilu SP Connect™ Pro lahko v nekaj sekundah namestite svoj pametni telefon na motocikel. Nosilec na krmilu Pro ima tudi vrtljivo in rotacijsko glavo, tako da je lahko vaš pametni telefon vedno kar najbolje nameščen. 
Samo privijte ta eleganten aluminijasti nosilec na nosilec krmila motocikla in že ste pripravljeni na namestitev ohišja za mobilni telefon SP Connect™ (ali univerzalnega vmesnika) tako, da ga postavite na nosilec in obrnete v smeri urnega kazalca za 90°. Mobilni telefon je varno nameščen v vidnem polju, kar vam omogoča navigacijo in dostop do seznamov predvajanja.

Zasnovana v kontrastu črne in rdeče barve REVS, ta udobna jakna ima zapiranje z zadrgo po celotni dolžini, ščitnik za brado in nastavljive manšete za prilagajanje vremenskim razmeram. A 3-panel lined fixed hood and zippered front pockets helps shield you from the elements, while embroidered Yamaha branding on the chest, backstripe graphic and white shoulder piping capture the latest REVS essence.

name.sl-SI: Paket 'Sport Pack Pro Black' za MT-09

description.sl-SI: Vrhunski videz in zmogljivosti so za MT-09 standardne, zdaj pa ga lahko nadgradite s paketom 'Sport Pack Pro Black', ki je zasnovan tako, da bo vaš motocikel še bolj izstopal. Za dopolnitev hitre in vznemirljive izkušnje vožnje z modelom MT-09, črni popolni izpušni sistem Akrapovič poudarja ikonično rjovenje agregata CP3 ter čisti adrenalin, ki ga doživljamo z vsakim zasukom plina. Skupaj z ogledali na krmilu v obliki romba, črno obarvanim kratkim vizirjem in elegantnim nosilcem registrske tablice ti skrbno izbrani dodatki izboljšajo agresiven in športen videz vašega motornega kolesa. Blazinice za rezervoar in stranski oprijem – zasnovane posebej za MT-09 – izboljšajo nadzor in stabilnost pri vožnji v ovinkih, hkrati pa ščitijo rezervoar pred praskami. Ste pripravljeni, da svojo vožnjo popeljete na naslednjo raven?
description.en: Class-leading looks and performance are standard on the MT-09, but now you can take it to the next level with the Sport Pack Pro Black, designed to make your bike stand out from the crowd even more. To complement the fast and thrilling experience of riding the MT-09, the black Akrapovič Full Exhaust System accentuates the CP3’s iconic roar, emphasising the pure adrenaline delivered with every twist of the throttle. Together with the diamond-shaped bar end mirrors, black-tinted fly screen and a sleek licence plate holder, these carefully selected accessories enhance your bike’s sharp and sporty looks. Finally, the tank pad and side grip pads—designed specifically for the MT-09—improve control and stability when tackling corners, while also protecting the tank from scratches. Are you ready to push your ride to the next level?

Vodoodporne hlače so izdelane iz funkcionalnega zunanjega sloja iz mešanice poliestra in poliuretana ter imajo odstranljivo izolacijsko podlogo za spremenljive temperature, ščitniki za boke in kolena pa zagotavljajo samozavest in brezskrbnost na poti. Dva zunanja žepa omogočata shranjevanje nujnih stvari in sta za dodatno zračenje skrita v prezračevalnih zadrgah. Snemljive naramnice, trakovi na ježka za gležnje in elastični patenti na zapestjih, stegnih in kolenih poskrbijo za izjemno udobje na dolgih vožnjah, zadrga pa omogoča, da se hlače združijo z žensko športno-potovalno motoristično jakno.
description.en: A must-have for all-weather touring, the two-tone Sport Touring Women’s Riding Pants offer comfort, protection and durability wherever the road takes you. Made with a technical outer layer blend of polyester and polyurethane, the waterproof pants feature a detachable insulation lining for changing temperatures, will hip and knee protectors provide confidence and peace of mind on the move. Two outer pockets allow you to carry essentials and are hidden inside ventilation zips for extra breathability. Detachable suspenders, Velcro ankle straps and elasticated wrist, thighs and knees offer excellent comfort for long rides, with a zipper to allow the pants to connect to the Sport Touring Women’s Riding Jacket.

description.en: No more stress about your phone sinking to the bottom of the ocean. The Yamaha floating PVC phone case keeps your phone dry and safe, while you enjoy yourself at boating or other sports activities on and off the water.
description.sl-SI: Nič več strahu, da bo telefon potonil na dno oceana. Ploven PVC ovitek Yamaha za mobilne telefone varuje vašo napravo in jo ščiti pred vlago, medtem ko vi uživate na čolnu ali pri drugih športnih aktivnostih na vodi ali na suhem.

description.en: The residues from dust, dirt and countless insects are the penalty we pay for our riding enjoyment – and not just on our helmets and visors, but on headlights and windscreens too! This can be a visibility and safety issue, but these handy wipes (with the polishing cloth included) solve the problem quickly – so keep them in your backpack!
description.sl-SI: Ostanki prahu, umazanija in nešteto žuželk – ne samo na čeladah in vizirjih, ampak tudi na žarometih in vetrnih ščitih – so cena, ki jo plačujemo za naš užitek v vožnji. Omenjeni ostanki lahko otežijo vidljivost in predstavljajo varnostno tveganje, vendar ti priročni vlažni robčki (z vključeno krpo za poliranje) to težavo hitro rešijo – pospravite jih kar v nahrbtnik!

description.en: This rugged Brush Guard is designed to provide additional protection while you’re out on the trail. It was designed to seamlessly integrate with the front profile of the Grizzly while adding a tough, aggressive look. Helps protect the front end, fenders, and headlights.
description.sl-SI: Ta trpežni ščitnik proti praskam je zasnovan, da nudi dodatno zaščito med vožnjo po poti. Zasnovan je bil tako, da se odlično integrira na sprednji profil modela Grizzly in ob tem doda nepopustljiv, agresiven videz. Pomaga ščititi sprednji del, blatnike in žaromete.

Te dodatke odlikuje lahka zasnova, saj so izdelani iz materiala, odpornega na udarce, ki je v 60 % sestavljen iz dolgih steklenih vlaken ter ustreza nacionalnim in mednarodnim tehničnim predpisom o dirkah.
description.en: Protect your R9's crankcase against slides and knocks with the GB Racing Crankcase Protector Set. Lightweight in design, these accessories are built from high-impact 60% long glass fibred nylon that meets national and international technical race regulations.

description.sl-SI:
Če pnevmatika ni raztrgana, poškodovana ali sneta s platišča, lahko težavo prazne pnevmatike ali pnevmatike, ki pušča, s tem preparatom preprosto rešite – Yamalube za hitro popravilo pnevmatik.
Pnevmatiko zatesni in napolni, ne da bi pri tem morali odstraniti pnevmatiko ali kolo, zato je ta pripomoček vaš prijatelj za reševanje obcestnih težav.
description.en:
If it is not torn, damaged or off the rim, a flat or leaking tyre is no problem with this handy solution - Yamalube Quick Tyre Repair.
It seals and inflates a tyre without the need to remove the tyre or the wheel, so it’s your roadside friend in need.

A super soft finish means even the youngest can enjoy playing with it, and the standout racing blue and white design captures the Yamaha spirit. A perfect start to the Yamaha journey.
description.sl-SI: Srčkan in ljubek izdelek, ki so ga navdihnili Yamahini dirkači. Plišasta igrača v barvi Paddock Blue je odlično darilo za malčke. Super mehka zunanjost pomeni, da lahko tudi najmlajši uživajo v igranju s to igračo, modra in bela barva pa izražata Yamahin duh. Popoln začetek spoznavanja sveta z Yamaho.

description.sl-SI: Podajte se na naslednjo pustolovščino z našim kompletom mehkih stranskih torb, ki so zasnovani za popotnike, ki cenijo funkcionalnost in slog. Ta komplet vodotesnih torb združuje robustno vzdržljivost in elegantno, sodobno estetiko ter zagotavlja, da bodo vaše stvari ostale varne in suhe – ne glede na to, kam vas pelje vaše potovanje.
description.en: Embark on your next adventure with our Soft Side Bag Set, designed for travelers who value both functionality and style. This watertight luggage set combines rugged durability with a sleek, modern aesthetic, ensuring your belongings stay safe and dry, no matter where your journey takes you.

description.sl-SI: Pričarajte športni videz Yamahinega skuterja NMAX s kompletom NMAX 'Sport Pack', ki vsebuje športni vizir NMAX, ročico sprednje in zadnje zavore NMAX ter ploščice za zgornji in spodnji del talne plošče NMAX. Izboljšajte linije, slog in funkcionalnost svojega NMAX-a ter osvojite ulice.
description.en: Give your Yamaha NMAX the sporty look with the NMAX Sport Pack, containing the Sport Screen NMAX, Front and Rear Brake Lever MAX, and Top and Floor Footplates NMAX. Enhance the lines, style and function of your NMAX and own the streets.

description.sl-SI: Zaščita agregata BG Racing za primer trčenja ali padca motornega kolesa.
description.en: BG Racing engine protection in case of crash or bike drop.
Short stylish screen to enforce the looks of your MT-125.

description.sl-SI: Zaščitite svojo Yamaho R9 pred poškodbami s temi čudovito oblikovanimi, a vseeno funkcionalnimi ščitniki okvirja. Te trdne visokokakovostne komponente, ki so zasnovane tako, da dopolnjujejo lastnosti modela R9, nudijo zaščito, ne da bi vplivale na nagibni kot motornega kolesa.
description.en: Protect your Yamaha R9 from damage with these beautifully sculpted yet functional Frame Sliders. Designed to complement the asthestics of the R9, these tough high quality components offer protection while not affecting the banking angle of the bike.
The Genuine Yamaha Sliding Glass Rear Window keeps the elements out, maximizes airflow and allows easy cargo access from inside the cab.
description.sl-SI: Originalno Yamahino drsno stekleno zadnje okno zagotavlja zaščito pred vremenskimi vplivi, izboljšan pretok zraka in preprost dostop do prtljažnega prostora iz notranjosti kabine.

S svojim drznim in agresivnim videzom je MT-09 prava paša za oči, 'Sport Pack Black' pa to samo še nadgradi. Nosilec za zaključek krmila in ščitnika členkov zagotavljajo večjo zaščito pred vetrom, hkrati pa prispevajo k agresivnemu videzu sprednjega dela MT-09, skupaj z zatemnjenim kratkim vizirjem. Na zadnji strani preoblikovan nosilec registrske tablice izboljša drzen profil motornega kolesa. Zaključek zagotavljajo stranske blazinice za oprijem na rezervoarju, ki ne le ščitijo pred praskami, temveč nudijo tudi dodaten oprijem za samozavestno vožnjo v ovinkih.
description.en: With its bold and aggressive design, the MT-09 is already a real head-turner and the Sport Pack Black takes it even further. The bar end base and knuckle deflectors provide increased wind protection, while also enhancing the aggressive look of the MT-09’s front end alongside the black-tinted fly screen. At the rear, the streamlined licence plate holder enhances the bike’s sharp profile. The finishing touch is provided by the side tank grip pads that not only protect against scratches but also offer extra grip for confident cornering.

The REVS collection is inspired by vintage Yamaha motorcycles. The design of our REVS Beluga Relax Shorts also embraces the concept of Yamaha's nostalgia. It is perfect to slide in when you are doing exercise or jogging outdoors..
description.sl-SI: Kolekcija REVS je navdih našla pri Yamahinih starodobnih motorjih. Zasnova kratkih hlač REVS Beluga Relax zajema tudi koncept Yamahine nostalgije. So odlične za vadbo ali tek na prostem.

S paketom 'Adrenaline' za R9 nadgradite svojo vožnjo. Dodajte nabor visokokakovostne dodatne opreme, ki izboljša videz in zvok vašega R9. 

Vsebuje: Celoten izpušni sistem R9 Akrapovič, drsniki okvirja, nosilec registrske tablice, ščitnik kovinske ročice sprednje zavore, prevleka zadnjega sedeža, zatemnjen vizir.
description.en:
Rev up your ride with the R9 Adrenaline Pack. Add a range of high-quality accessories to enhance the look and sound of your R9. 

Contains: R9 Akrapovič Full System, Frame Sliders, License Plate Holder, Billet Front Brake Lever Guard, Rear Seat Cover, Smoke Windscreen.

description.sl-SI: 45-litrski zgornji kovček brez ključa je ustvarjen za sodobne pustolovce in popotnike ter je sodobna in elegantna rešitev za shranjevanje. Najsodobnejše zaklepanje brez ključa zagotavlja, da so vaše bistvene stvari varne pri vsaki vožnji.
description.en: Made for the modern adventurer and commuter, the Keyless Top Case 45L is a slick and stylish storage solution. Cutting-edge, keyless locking ensures your essentials are kept safe on every ride.

description.sl-SI: Hidravlični sistemi upravljanja tipa LS 125 PRO. Popoln komplet (standardni sistem, vključno s cilindrom, helm pumpo z zaklepno ventilom, vsemi priključki, lijakom za polnjenje in 10 m cevi)
description.en: Hydraulic steering systems type LS 125 PRO. Complete kit (standard system incl. cylinder, helm pump with lock valve, all fittings, filling funnel and 10m hose)
Stylish sticker set for the rims of 17" wheels.
Custom oil filler cap - replacing the original - for an extra stylish touch to your Yamaha.
description.sl-SI: Po meri izdelan pokrov posode za motorno olje, ki nadomešča originalnega – za dodaten pridih elegance vaše Yamahe.

Dvobarvne moške športno-potovalne motoristične hlače, ki so nepogrešljive za vožnje v vseh vremenskih razmerah, ponujajo udobje, zaščito in trpežnost, kjer koli ste. Vodoodporne hlače so izdelane iz funkcionalnega zunanjega sloja iz mešanice poliestra in poliuretana ter imajo odstranljivo izolacijsko podlogo za spremenljive temperature, ščitniki za boke in kolena pa zagotavljajo samozavest in brezskrbnost na poti. Dva zunanja žepa omogočata shranjevanje nujnih stvari in sta za dodatno zračenje skrita v prezračevalnih zadrgah. Snemljive naramnice, trakovi na ježka za gležnje in elastični patenti na zapestjih, stegnih in kolenih poskrbijo za izjemno udobje na dolgih vožnjah, zadrga pa omogoča, da se hlače združijo z moško športno-potovalno motoristično jakno.
description.en: A must-have for all-weather touring, the two-tone Sport Touring Men’s Riding Pants offer comfort, protection and durability wherever the road takes you. Made with a technical outer layer blend of polyester and polyurethane, the waterproof pants feature a detachable insulation lining for changing temperatures, will hip and knee protectors provide confidence and peace of mind on the move. Two outer pockets allow you to carry essentials and are hidden inside ventilation zips for extra breathability. Detachable suspenders, Velcro ankle straps and elasticated wrist, thighs and knees offer excellent comfort for long rides, with a zipper to allow the pants to connect to the Sport Touring Men’s Riding Jacket.

description.en: A simple but bold expression of Yamaha racing history, the Racing Heritage cap in black or off-white is an everyday essential for year-round wear. Coming in 100% organic cotton, the cap features the classic Yamaha Racing red speed block design on the front with white Yamaha logo and the Yamaha Racing Heritage Club logo on the back. The inner sweatband ensures comfort in warm weather, while the back strap provides full adjustability.
description.sl-SI: Preprost, a drzen odraz Yamahine dirkaške zgodovine: kapa Racing Heritage v črni ali umazano beli barvi je vsakodneven dodatek za uporabo skozi celo leto. Kapa je izdelana iz 100 % ekološko pridelanega bombaža, njena klasična zasnova Yamaha Racing pa vključuje rdečo grafiko 'Speedblock' na sprednji strani ter bel Yamahin logotip in logotip Yamaha Racing Heritage Club na zadnji strani. Notranji trak za vpijanje znoja zagotavlja prijetno uporabo v toplem vremenu, trak na zadnji strani pa zagotavlja želeno nastavitev.

description.en: Specially designed exhaust camshaft for racing purposes and improves performance in conjunction with intake camshaft.

description.sl-SI: Lahka in aerodinamična krilca po navdihu iz MotoGP prinašajo nove ravni pritiska navzdol v že zmagovalni rodovnik. Ta krilca so oblikovana tako, da dopolnjujejo ostre linije R1 in so nameščena ob oklepu, skrbijo za maksimalne učinke elektronike proti dvigovanju prednjega kolesa, hkrati pa povečujejo občutek sprednjega dela med zaviranjem in zavijanjem ter izboljšujejo stabilnost pri visokih hitrostih.
description.en: MotoGP-inspired lightweight and aerodynamic winglets bring new levels of downforce to an already race-winning pedigree. Sculpted to complement the razor-sharp lines of the R1 and positioned perfectly against the fairing, these winglets maximise the effects of the bike’s anti-wheelie electronics while increasing front-end feel during braking and cornering, and improving high-speed stability.

description.sl-SI: Ženska polo majica REVS, v črni barvi z izrazitimi rdečimi in belimi poudarki, je eleganten priložnostni izdelek, ki uteleša slog REVS. Mešanica bombaža in elastana ponuja raztegljivost za udobno prileganje, z ovratnikom z gumbi. Brezšivni rokavi in rob dodajajo izjemen slog, elegantni videz pa dopolnjujejo izvezen napis Yamaha na prsih, grafika navpične črte zadaj in bele obrobe na ramenih.
description.en: Black with striking red and white highlights, the REVS Women’s Polo Shirt is a smart-casual item that embodies the REVS style. A cotton and elastane blend offers stretch for a comfortable fit, with a button closure collar. Seamless sleeves and hem add real style, with embroidered Yamaha chest branding, backstripe graphic and whit shoulder piping that offsets this classy look.
GYTR® Rear Sprocket with 44T for 520 Chain conversion

description.sl-SI: Opremite se za pustolovščine ob koncu tedna s paketom TRACER 7 'Weekend Pack'. Izkusite izboljšano zaščito pred vetrom z visokim vizirjem in zaščitite rezervoar z zaščito za rezervoar »Road to Fuji«, medtem ko je vaša prtljaga varno shranjena v poltrdih stranskih torbah ABS. Ta paket združuje funkcionalnost s slogom za popoln vikend oddih.
description.en: Gear up for your weekend adventures with the TRACER 7 Weekend Pack. Enjoy enhanced wind protection with the High Screen, and protect your tank with the Road to Fuji Tank Pad while having your belongings secured in the Soft ABS Side Cases. This pack combines functionality with style for the perfect weekend break.

Izdelane so iz 100-odstotnega poliamida, so v dirkaški modri barvi s kontrastno belo črto in trakom v retro slogu. Znotraj imajo mrežasto oblogo za udobje v vodi in še elastičen pas z vrvico za prilagajanje velikosti. Kopalke se ponašajo z izvezenim logotipom Yamaha Racing za celovit Yamahin slog.

Made from 100% polyamide in racing blue with contrasting white stripe and retro-style tape, the shorts have a mesh inner lining for comfort in the water and a draw cord elastic waist for comfort. Embroidered Yamaha Racing branding gives a final touch of Yamaha style.

description.en: Rain and wind shouldn't stop you from activities, and neither should they affect your riding pleasure and comfort. We developed the Apron, which uses special welding technology, to keep you warm and dry, so you can be more comfortable and safe during harsh weather conditions.
description.sl-SI: Dež in veter ne bi smela biti ovira pri aktivnostih, prav tako pa ne bi smela vplivati na vaš užitek in udobje pri vožnji. Razvili smo zaščito za sprednji del telesa, ki uporablja posebno tehnologijo varjenja, ki vas ščiti pred mrazom in dežjem, da vam bo tudi v težjih vremenskih pogojih udobno in boste ostali varni.

description.en: With a vintage look and feel recalling classic Yamaha racing design, the Racing Heritage keyring is a stylish accessory for everyday use and convenience. The black leather retro-styled keyring features a metal Yamaha Racing Heritage Club logo emblem and white stitching, while the metal ring allows keys and other essential items to be carried safely.

Retro obesek iz črnega usnja vključuje logotip Yamaha Racing Heritage Club in bele šive, kovinski obroček pa omogoča varno prenašanje ključev in drugih nujnih stvari.

'Sport Pack Pro', ki je zasnovan za izboljšanje zmogljivosti, sloga in funkcionalnosti vašega MT-07, ponuja vrhunsko izbiro Yamahine dodatne opreme. Nova zasnova ekskluzivnega sistema Akrapovič zagotavlja izboljšan zvok in večjo moč, medtem ko kombinacija ogledal na koncu krmila, vsestranskega nosilca na krmilu in kratkega vizirja poskrbi za bolj drzen videz sprednjega dela. Medtem ko blazinica za rezervoar ščiti rezervoar pred praskami, zaporedni LED utripalci v vaš MT-07 prinašajo pridih vrhunske prefinjenosti. 

Vsebuje: Celoten izpušni sistem Akrapovič MT-07, večnamenska osnova, vetrobransko steklo, zaščitna blazinica za rezervoar, ogledala na koncu krmila v obliki diamanta, sekvenčne LED utripalke, nosilec registrske tablice.
description.en:
Crafted to enhance the performance, style and function of your MT-07, the Sport Pack Pro features the ultimate selection of Yamaha accessories. The newly designed exclusive Akrapovič system provides enhanced sound and power, while the Bar-End Mirrors together with the Multi-Mount Base and Fly Screen combo give your front end a bold new look. And while the Tank Pad protects the tank from scratches, the Sequential LED Blinkers bring a touch of cutting-edge sophistication to your MT-07. 

Contains: MT-07 Full Akrapovič Exhaust System, Multi-Mount Base, Fly Screen, Tank Pad, Diamond Bar-end Mirrors, Sequential LED Blinkers, Licence Plate Holder.

description.en: Colour matched with the latest generation of Yamaha Racing motorcycles, the Paddock Blue Men’s Jog Pants are made to withstand regular activity and wear. Blended from cotton  and polyester , these pants are supremely comfortable. A self-fabric waistband allows an easy fit, with two side and one rear pockets for convenience. Subtle Yamaha branding pulls together this eye-catching garment.
description.sl-SI: Tekaške hlače Paddock Blue za moške, ki se barvno ujemajo z zadnjo generacijo motornih koles ekipe Yamaha Racing, so narejene za redno aktivnost in uporabo. Izdelane so iz bombaža in poliestra ter so neverjetno udobne. Pas iz enakega materiala omogoča prijetno prileganje, dva stranska in zadnji žep pa priročnost. Prefinjen Yamahin logotip to privlačno oblačilo lepo poveže.

description.en:
The MT-03 Sport Pack is designed to offer you a complete mix of accessories, to complement the aggressive look and reinforce its performance. The Radiator Cover gives protection against small stone/debris impact, while the Tank Pad adds protection to the fuel tank.
The Sport Screen is designed to provide wind protection to enjoy a thrilling ride. Finally, the License Plate Holder and LED Blinkers add an stylish look, making this motorbike one of the coolest looking bikes in its category.
description.sl-SI:
Komplet MT-03 Sport Pack vključuje popoln nabor dodatne opreme, ki poudarja agresiven videz in učinkovitost vašega motornega kolesa. Pokrov hladilnika zagotavlja zaščito pred poškodbami, ki nastanejo zaradi kamenčkov in/ali drugih delcev, zaščita rezervoarja pa dodatno varuje rezervoar za gorivo.
Športni vizir je zasnovan za zaščito pred vetrom in užitke med razburljivo vožnjo. Nosilec registrske tablice in LED-smerniki pa dodajo eleganten videz, s čimer poskrbijo, da je to eno najprivlačnejših motornih koles v svoji kategoriji.

description.en: Keep your investment looking its best, and protect it from the elements. With fast installation and removal, this cover provides the protection against color fading and the elements.
description.sl-SI: Ohranite svojo naložbo v najboljšem stanju in jo zaščitite pred vremenskimi vplivi. Ta prevleka, ki se hitro namesti in odstrani, zagotavlja zaščito pred bledenjem barv in posledicami vremenskih dejavnikov.

description.en: Protect your feet and lower legs in wet weather conditions from water splashing up from underneath the front wheels with the Mud Flaps. The flexible material ensures the flaps do not damage when leaving a higher curb,
description.sl-SI: Zaščitite stopala in spodnji del nog v mokrih vremenskih razmerah pred tem, da bi voda pod sprednjimi kolesi pljuskala na vas, z zavesicami koles. Prilagodljiv material zagotavlja, da se zavesice ne poškodujejo, ko prečkate višji robnik

description.en: Take your TMAX to the next level with the Sport pack. Containing all the must-have sport accessories, the pack gives an even sportier look to your TMAX. Make it truly yours by adding optional Gilles , Akrapovič and Ohlin’s parts. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your TMAX.
description.sl-SI: Nadgradite svoj model TMAX s kompletom 'Sport'. Komplet vsebuje vso športno dodatno opremo, ki jo preprosto morate imeti in ki vašemu modelu TMAX zagotavlja še bolj športen videz. Svojemu modelu TMAX dodajte dele družb Gilles, Akrapovič in Ohlin ter ga tako povsem prilagodite svojemu okusu. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš model TMAX.

description.en: Ideal for young riders getting to grips with their bike on track, the MX Kid’s Body Armour offers superior and lightweight chest and back protection. Impact absorbing polymer shells are mated to a flexible jersey undershirt, allowing full range of movement without compromising safety. The front and back shells are perforated for ventilation, with a naturally contoured back shell to follow the spine. A kidney belt helps ease the load on the back, while a full zip and auto lock closure ensures a solid protection shell for your child.
description.sl-SI: Ščitnik telesa MX za otroke je popoln za mlajše voznike, ki se šele seznanjajo z motornim kolesom na stezi, ter ponuja vrhunsko in lahkotno zaščito prsi in hrbta. Polimerni drsniki, ki blažijo udarce, v kombinaciji s fleksibilno spodnjo majico omogočajo celostno gibanje, ne da bi pri tem ogrozili varnost. Sprednji in zadnji drsniki imajo odprtine za zračenje, poleg tega je zadnji drsnik oblikovan tako, da se naravno prilega hrbtenici. Ledvični pas lajša obremenitev hrbtenice, zadrga po celotni dolžini in samodejno zapenjanje pa zagotavljata popolno zaščitno opremo za vašega otroka.

Ta črna majica s kratkimi rokavi udobnega kroja je izdelana iz bombaža in elastana v enojnem džersiju ter ima vpadljive rdeče stranske dele in bele obrobe na ramenih. Okrogel izrez in raglan rokavi ponujajo enostavno udobje, natisnjeni napis Yamaha na prsih in grafika navpične črte zadaj pa prinašata vrhunski izdelek kolekcije REVS.

description.sl-SI: Zima je čas zabav, praznikov in praznovanj, paket Winter pa zagotavlja, da enak občutek veselja doživite tudi s svojim modelom Tricity. Da bodo vaše roke prijetno tople, ne glede na vremenske pogoje, smo vključili grelnike ročk. V paket je vključen tudi ščitnik za členke, ki tok dohodnega zraka preusmeri stran od rok ter skupaj z grelniki ročk poskrbi za kar najboljšo zaščito pred hladnim vetrom. Zaščita za sprednji del telesa odlično varuje spodnji del telesa pred mrazom, vetrom in dežjem. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš Tricity.
description.en: Winter is a time for festivity, holiday and celebration, and the Winter pack ensures that you experience that same feeling of joy with your Tricity. To keep your hands warm and toasty, whatever the condition, we have included the grip heaters. Also included are knuckle visors that channel incoming airflow away from your hands, and combined with the grip heaters, provide optimum protection against wind chill. The Apron does an excellent job of protecting your lower body from the cold, wind and rain. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your Tricity.

name.en: Nothing but the Max Zip Hoodie Men
name.sl-SI: Moška jopa s kapuco 'Nothing but the Max' na zadrgo

description.en: Made to be one with Yamaha scooters, the Nothing but the Max zip hoodie for men is a true statement piece. Black organic cotton and recycled polyester are blended into this high-end garment, with a taped and lined hood and bonded front pockets offering comfort in style. Nothing but the Max branding on the chest and hood edge highlight its DNA, while the Yamaha logo on the back brings the look together for an instant classic.
description.sl-SI: Po videzu se ujema z Yamahinimi skuterji: moška jopa s kapuco 'Nothing but the Max' pritegne poglede. Kakovostno oblačilo je izdelano iz črne tkanine iz ekološko pridelanega bombaža in recikliranega poliestra, ima podloženo kapuco z lepljenimi šivi ter lepljena sprednja žepa, zato je udobno in elegantno. Grafika 'Nothing but the Max' na prsih in robu kapuce poudarja bistvo kolekcije, medtem ko Yamahin logotip videz poveže v celoto.

description.en: Stylish and adaptable for daily wear, the Paddock Blue Women’s Sweater/Hoodie is a comfy classic for wearing to race events, the gym and more. Made from a soft blend of polyester   and cotton , this garment features a full-length zip and fixed hood ensure a snug fit. Self-fabric hem and cuffs give a seamless look, with colour contrast black sleeves and external pockets for essentials. Embroidered chest branding and back graphic in white give a classic teamwear look.
description.sl-SI: Ženska jopa Paddock Blue je stilsko in prilagodljivo vsakdanje klasično oblačilo, ki ga lahko udobno nosite na dirkalnih prireditvah, v telovadnici ali kjer koli drugje. Izdelana je iz mehkega poliestra in bombaža, ima zadrgo po celotni dolžini ter fiksno kapuco, ki zagotavlja tesno prileganje. Obšivi in manšete iz enakega materiala poskrbijo za brezhiben videz, rokavi so v kontrastni črni barvi, zunanji žepi pa omogočajo prostor za vaše predmete. Zaradi izvezenega logotipa na prsih in grafike na hrbtu v beli barvi ima jopa klasičen videz oblačila ekipe.

description.en: Featuring a lightweight Neoprene construction, these padded urban gloves are designed for summer riding. Silicon on the palms gives you added grip, and there's an Amara fabric patch for wiping your goggles or visor.
description.sl-SI: Te oblazinjene rokavice iz lahkega neoprena so zasnovane za vožnjo poleti. Silikon na dlaneh izboljša oprijem, zaplata iz tkanine Amara pa je namenjena za čiščenje očal ali vizirja.

description.en: The SP Connect mirror mount allows you to mount your smartphone to your scooter or motorbike in seconds.

name.sl-SI: Paket napihljive deske za veslanje Yamaha 10.0

description.en: The Yamaha 10.0 Air SUP is the perfect all-round SUP on which you can cruise around, after you're done playing with your Yamaha WaveRunner. This SUP comes with all the latest tech which you can expect from a SUP. Heat bonded technology combined with an X-stitching construction make for a lightweight SUP with great stiffness. And with the new EZ-Lockfin on there, you'll be out and enjoying the water in no-time! This makes the 10.0 SUP a necessity for all those who enjoy the water.
description.sl-SI: Yamaha 10.0 Air SUP je odlična vsestranska deska SUP, na kateri lahko sproščeno veslate, ko zaključite igrivo plovbo z vodnim skuterjem Yamaha WaveRunner. Ta SUP je opremljen z vso najnovejšo tehnologijo, ki jo lahko pričakujete od takega izdelka. Tehnologija toplotnega lepljenja in konstrukcija z navzkrižnimi šivi zagotavljata lahek, a vseeno zelo trden SUP. Z novim sistemom smernika EZ-Lockfin boste na vodi uživali še hitreje. Tako je SUP 10.0 obvezna oprema za vse, ki uživate v vodnih športih.

V dolgih dneh na stezi ali pri delu na nogah nič ne prinese več udobja kot dolge nogavice Paddock Blue. Izdelane so iz bombaža, poliamida in elastana ter so trpežne, udobne in raztegljive, kar bo vašim stopalom prineslo izredno ugodje. Nogavice so za oba spola in so na voljo v dveh velikostih, ponašajo se tudi z logotipom Yamaha Racing, s čimer bo hoja prav neverjetna.
description.en: For long days at the track or work spent on your feet, nothing says comfort like the Paddock Blue Crew Socks. A blend of cotton, polyamide and elastane delivers a combination of durability, comfort and stretch that your feet will love. With a unisex fit available in two sizes, these socks carry Yamaha Racing branding that help you walk the walk.

name.en: Hard Cab Enclosure System Glass Front Windshield with Wiper
name.sl-SI: Steklen sprednji vizir z brisalcem kompleta za zapiranje kabine v trdi izvedbi

description.en: Yamaha is offering all the components of the Hard Cab Enclosure System separately for added customer convenience. When rain, snow, dust and/or dirt start flying, a glass front windshield keeps you and your riders protected. Designed for simple installation and a perfect fit, this integrated pre-installed windshield features both a wiper and washer system. A fluid bottle for the washer system is nestled nicely under the hood area for easy filling and no loss of precious storage space.
description.sl-SI: Yamaha za lažjo uporabo vse sestavne dele kompleta za zapiranje kabine v trdi izvedbi ponuja ločeno. Ko ste vi in vaši potniki izpostavljeni dežju, snegu, prahu in/ali umazaniji, vas zaščiti steklen sprednji vizir. Ta vgrajeni prednameščeni vizir je zasnovan tako, da je nameščanje preprosto in da se popolnoma prilega vozilu, vključuje pa tudi sistem za brisanje in pranje stekel. Vsebnik s tekočino za sistem pranja stekel je vgrajen pod pokrovom za lažje polnjenje, pri tem pa ne izgubite dragocenega prostora za shranjevanje.
Popolnoma vodoodporna zaščita vas z varjenimi šivi in izolirano podlogo greje ter poskrbi, da ostanete suhi v vseh vremenskih pogojih, zato se lahko udobno vozite vse leto.
description.en: Featuring welded seams and an insulated lining, the fully-water resistant Apron keeps you warm and dry in all kinds of weather, enabling you to commute in comfort throughout the year.
Freshen up your Golf Car's styling, while  protecting to your wheels. Our exclusive wheel covers have the Yamaha's iconic appearance and will fit ant stock 8" wheel.

Majica je zasnovana za udobno vsakodnevno nošenje na dirkah in doma ter ima modro in črno barvo z belimi detajli, ki jo navdihujeta YZ450FM, ter V-izrez za zračnost. Dodaten dirkaški slog je dodan z ikoničnimi oznakami Yamaha Racing in Monster Energy® na prsih, hrbtu in rokah.
description.en: An essential layer of the Monster Energy® Yamaha Factory MXGP Team wardrobe, the Women’s Replica T-Shirt captures the passion and energy of the MX team. Designed for comfortable, every-day wear at races and home, the tee features YZ450FM-inspired colour contrast blue and black with white detailing and a V-neck for breathability. Extra racing style is added with iconic Yamaha Racing and Monster Energy® branding on the chest, back and arms.

A fixed hood offers extra protection from the elements, with two front zip pockets and two inner pockets for carrying essentials. The inside-attached bag also means you can fold away the jacket for easy carry and storage. Essential for on-the-go riders!
Ohlins FGRT 219 is a high performance fully adjustable front fork for YZF-R1 and MT10. The front fork improves on rider feedback, brake support and general handling of the bike.

Its organic cotton and elastane blend gives a soft feel with mobility, with the staple front panel and printed MT logo a clear eye-catcher. Paket TRACER 9 GT 'Travel Pack' vsebuje ustrezne dodatke, ki poskrbijo za večje udobje na dolgih vožnjah. Zgornji kovček in vsi dodatki, potrebni za namestitev, zagotavljajo neverjeten 45-litrski dodatni prostor za shranjevanje, kamor lahko shranite dve integralni čeladi. description.en: For added comfort during long distance Touring, the TRACER 9 GT Travel Pack provides your motorcycle with just the right extra touches. The High Screen deflects even more wind and elements to provide the rider a pleasant protected position. The Comfort Seat is there to increase the comfort of seating for a longer period of time, making it an excellent addition for longer rides. The Top Case and all accessories needed to mount it provide an incredible 45 L extra storage space that can house two full face helmets if needed. The case can also be detailed to perfection with a color plate to match the color of your TRACER 9 GT.

The TTX GP is the latest shock absorber for hyper sport and sport bikes. It features the TTX twin tube technology and has been developed with the latest technology from Öhlins vast experiences in MotoGP. The compression and rebound damping adjustments are improved by a new adjustment needle with better guidance and different flow restriction behavior. It gives a more precise adjustment and constant function. The adjustment range is also wider and variations between shock absorbers are reduced. And improved chassis feedback as well as improved performance for the rider have been obtained. The new main piston gives the rider much better traction and feeling which means improved control. The TTX GP is further optimized and shares all other benefits with the TTX36 shock absorber.
With the GYTR Cylinder Head Gasket, you can increase compression ratio because of the lower thickness

name.sl-SI: Čelada IXS Trigger (MIPS) za MTB/neutrjene poti

description.en:
Designed for MTB and Gravel riders, TRIGGER AM from iXS represents the very latest in open face helmet design and technology. 
Featuring a lower back and a 3-level adjustable visor, this modern goggle-compatible design is an ideal choice for Moro 07 and Wabash owners. For a high level of all-round head protection its ultra-light construction features a tough external shell fused directly to the internal EPS material using patented double inmould shell technology. 
The Vortex™ molded aeration system features numerous interconnected internal and external air flow channels for highly efficient cooling – and with its full range of horizontal and vertical adjustment the Ergofit™ Ultra system makes it easy to find the most comfortable setting while the Fidlock™ magnetic closure system ensures precision locking. 
Equipped with MIPS Multi-directional Impact Protection System technology and featuring EN1078, CPSC, KC certification, the TRIGGER AM provides high levels of protection and comfort on every ride.
description.sl-SI:
Čelada TRIGGER AM podjetja iXS je zasnovana za kolesarje MTB in kolesarje po neutrjenih poteh ter predstavlja najnovejšo zasnovo in tehnologijo odprtih čelad. 

Ta moderna zasnova je popolna izbira za lastnike modelov Moro 07 in Wabash, saj je združljiva z očali, ima nižji hrbtni del in tristopenjsko nastavljivi ščitnik. Za visoko raven vsestranske zaščite glave ima njena ultra lahka konstrukcija trdo zunanjo lupino, pritrjeno neposredno na notranji material EPS z uporabo patentirane tehnologije lupine z dvojnim kalupom. 

Vdelan prezračevalni sistem Vortex™ ima številne medsebojno povezane notranje in zunanje kanale za pretok zraka za zelo učinkovito hlajenje, sistem Ergofit™ Ultra s celotnim naborom vodoravnih in navpičnih nastavitev omogoča enostavno iskanje najbolj udobne nastavitve, magnetni sistem zapiranja Fidlock™ pa zagotavlja natančno zaklepanje. 

Čelada TRIGGER AM je opremljena s tehnologijo sistema večsmerne zaščite pred udarci (MIPS), ima certifikate EN1078, CPSC in KC ter zagotavlja visoko raven zaščite in udobja na vsaki vožnji.

description.en: High performance leather racing gloves that match the one-piece R-Series leather racing suit. Essential for Supersport riders, the gloves are crafted using a race-tested combination of double-shell cowhide leather and high-tenacity Dupont Kevlar reinforcements for superior abrasion resistance. And featuring aramid fibers between the fingers and an injected slider on palm the gloves provide superlight strength and protection. Perforated leather with ventilated knuckle protectors give the gloves breathability, while the cotton interlining and flexible leather on the fingers offer comfort in all conditions.
description.sl-SI: Visoko zmogljive usnjene dirkalne rokavice, ki se ujemajo z enodelnim usnjenim dirkalnim kombinezonom R-Series. Rokavice so obvezna oprema za voznike supersport motornih koles, izdelane pa so iz dirkaško preizkušene kombinacije dvojnega kravjega usnja in izjemno vzdržljivih ojačitev iz Dupont kevlarja za izjemno odpornost proti odrgninam. Z aramidnimi vlakni med prsti in vbrizganim drsnikom na dlani rokavice zagotavljajo izjemno lahkotno moč in zaščito. Perforirano usnje z ventiliranimi ščitniki za členke daje rokavicam zračnost, medtem ko bombažna podloga in prožno usnje na prstih nudijo udobje v vseh pogojih.

description.en: Versatile riding gear rack with space to store your helmet, riding gear and other associated items safely, but easily accessible at all times. The hooks can be placed in any desired configuration to suit your usage. The upper part contains recesses at the bottom where clothes hangers can be placed, and the helmet support can be adjusted to center the motorcycle or bicycle helmet.

Kljuke lahko postavite v katero koli želeno konfiguracijo, ki ustreza vašim zahtevam. Zgornji del ima vdolbine na dnu, kamor lahko vstavite obešalnike za oblačila, podpora za čelado pa se lahko prilagodi tako, da centrira motoristično ali kolesarsko čelado.

description.en: Upgrade your Side-by-Side with the Hard Cabin Pack for the Wolverine® RMAX™4 1000. Pack includes: Front Glass Windshield with Wiper, Flip up Glass Rear Window, Hard Cabin Front and rear Doors and Cabin Heating Kit.

Nadgradite svoj model Side-by-Side s paketom za trdo kabino za model Wolverine® RMAX™4 1000. Paket vključuje: sprednje vetrobransko steklo z brisalcem, dvižno steklo,

Ta natančno prilegajoč se dodatek z lahkotnim dizajnom in posebnim mat črnim premazom, ki zagotavlja trpežnost, omogoča brezskrbnost pred udarci majhnih kamnov in drugih delcev, ko se odpravite na cesto ali stezo.
description.en: Protect your R9's radiator against road debris impact with the Aluminium Radiator Guard. Lightweight in design and equipped with a special matt-black coating to ensure durability, this precise-fitting accessory offers peace of mind against small stone and debris impact as you take to the road or the track.

Premium quality all-weather women's jacket with detachable hood. The waterproof fabric, padded lining and mesh panels keep you warm and dry throughout the year. The Paddock Blue women's jacket has white Yamaha Racing logos on the chest and sleeve and features various contrasting design elements in black and white.
description.sl-SI: Ženska jakna vrhunske kakovosti za vsako vreme s snemljivo kapuco. Vodoodporna tkanina, oblazinjena podloga in mrežasti deli vas grejejo in sušijo skozi vse leto. Ženska jakna Paddock Blue ima na prsih in rokavih bele logotipe Yamaha Racing ter različne kontrastne oblikovalske elemente v črno-beli barvi.

Lahko se kombinira z mehkimi stranskimi pokrovi, zaščito pred soncem in polikarbonatnimi vetrobranskimi stekli za celovito zaščito.

description.en: Enhance the rear-end of your Yamaha R9 with this genuine License Plate Holder. With a smooth metallic finish, this smart-looking direct replacement for the standard unit includes a LED license plate light and a stylish R9 logo, plus the cables and connectors required to fit original indicators or optional accessory parts.

Featuring a body manufactured from forged aluminium, the VX trail pedal combines a low weight with high levels of durability, making this a perfect option for mountain terrain and gravel trails. Its CNC machined chromoly steel axle is fitted with double sealed cartridge bearings and full roller bearings for highly efficient operation with superior longevity – and the heat treated VX bindings give a precise and predictable fit. Supplied with one pair of SPD compatible cleats.
description.sl-SI:
Terenski pedal VX s kovanim aluminijastim ohišjem združuje nizko težo z visoko stopnjo trpežnosti, zaradi česar je popolna izbira za gorske terene in neutrjene poti. 

Njegova gred iz krom-molibden jekla, izdelana s strojem CNC, je opremljena z dvojno zatesnjenimi ležaji in polnimi valjčnimi ležaji za visoko učinkovito delovanje z vrhunsko življenjsko dobo – toplotno obdelane vezi VX pa se natančno in predvidljivo prilegajo. Priložen je en par bitev, združljivih s SPD.

description.en: Bring out their passion for Yamaha early with the REVS baby gift pack. Comprising a grey bodysuit, beanie hat and cuddly toy, toddlers from 1-18 months will enjoy the comfort of each item. The bodysuit features a cartoon ‘First Steps’ and Yamaha print on the chest, with Yamaha logos on the beanie and toy. Short sleeves feature an iconic REVS red stripe, with press stud fastenings between the legs for quick changing and comfort.
description.sl-SI: Z otroškim darilnim paketom REVS lahko otrokom strast do Yamahe položite že v zibelko. Komplet sestavljajo siv bodi, kapica in mehka igračka, ki bodo razveselili malčke starosti 1–18 mesecev. Na prsnem delu bodija sta natisnjena sličica ‘First Steps’ in napis Yamaha, na kapi in igrački pa Yamahin logotip. Kratki rokavi imajo ikonično rdečo črto REVS, bodi pa se na mednožju zapenja s pritiskači za hitro preoblačenje in udobje.

Vztrajnik GYTR izravna moč vozila in poskrbi za manj agresivno pospeševanje, kadar dodate plin. Povečana vztrajnostna masa pomaga pri ohranjanju zagona skozi zavoje in tako je motor bolj uporaben – še posebej v blatnih in peščenih pogojih.
description.en: By smoothing out the power delivery the GYTR Flywheel delivers a less aggressive hit when you twist the throttle. Its increased inertia mass helps to keep momentum through corners and makes the bike more usable – especially in muddy and sandy conditions.
Custom-made storage specifically designed for the bow storage of VX Series WaveRunners.
description.sl-SI: Po meri izdelan prostor, posebej zasnovan za shranjevanje v premcu vodnih skuterjev WaveRunner serije VX.

Yamahin skuter NMAX pripravite na zimo s kompletom NMAX 'Winter Pack', ki zajema NMAX zaščito za sprednji del telesa in grelnik ročk. Obvezen za vožnjo s skuterjem v hladnem vremenu in udobje v zimskih mesecih.
description.en: Equip your Yamaha NMAX for winter with the NMAX Winter Pack, containing the Apron NMAX and Grip Heater NMAX. A must-have for cold weather scooter riding and comfort in winter months.

description.sl-SI: Lahek moški flis, ki je popoln kot športni drugi sloj, je zasnovan za nošenje pod motoristično jakno v hladnejših podnebjih. Izdelan iz mešanice poliestra in elastana v rjavih in modrih odtenkih, ki jih je navdihnil Ténéré, se flis hitro suši in ima zadrgo po celotni dolžini za nastavljivo udobje. Potisk »Ténéré« na prsih, napis Yamaha na hrbtu in sublimacijski tisk na notranji strani se združijo v eleganten pustolovski videz.
description.en: Perfect as a sporty second layer, the lightweight Adventure Men’s Fleece is designed for wear under a riding jacket in chillier climates. Made from a blend of polyester and elastane in Ténéré-inspired brown and blue tones, the fleece is quick drying and features a full-length zip for adjustable comfort. A Ténéré chest print, Yamaha back branding and a sublimated inner print combine for a stylish adventure look.

The PW50 little champ pack is perfect for new riders. Equip your bike with this pack, containing training wheels, seat cover and sticker kit, and start creating some great memories and family fun!
description.sl-SI: Komplet za male prvake PW50 je kot nalašč za nove voznike. Opremite kolo s tem kompletom, ki vsebuje pomožna kolesa, prevleko za sedež in komplet nalepk, ter začnite ustvarjati lepe spomine in družinsko zabavo!

Moške hlače MX so optimizirane in do potankosti tehnično dodelane za neusmiljeno dirkanje na modelu MX, poleg tega so trpežne in kot nalašč za drvenje po terenu. Lahkotna večdelna sestava zagotavlja dobro zaščito in obenem omogoča svobodno gibanje, na sedežni površini pa imajo hlače tkanino, izjemno odporno proti hrapavim površinam. Nastavljiv pas s silikonskim delom omogoča udobno prileganje vsem voznikom, ko so na nogah. Sublimirani logotipi Yamaha, Alpinestars in GYTR zagotavljajo ikonski videz dirkača na modelu MX.
description.en: Optimised and technically detailed for relentless MX racing, the MX Men’s Pants are hard-wearing and perfect for cutting through the ruts. A lightweight, multi-panel construction gives good protection while allowing freedom of movement, with high abrasion fabric on the seat. An adjustable waist with silicon grip allows the pants to fit all riders comfortably when they get their legs down. Sublimated Yamaha, Alpinestars and GYTR branding ensures an iconic MX racer look.
Designed to prevent breakage during crashes

description.en: Smart and comfortable ultra-light Yamaha Racing t-shirt for women with a bi-color round neckline. Feel part of the Yamaha Racing family with this soft cotton t-shirt, carrying printed Yamaha Racing logos on chest and sleeve as well as various contrasting design elements.
description.sl-SI: Pametna in udobna ženska ultra lahka majica Yamaha Racing, z okroglim izrezom v dveh barvah. S to mehko bombažno majico, ki ima na prsih in rokavih natisnjene logotipe Yamaha Racing ter različne kontrastne elemente, občutite del družine Yamaha Racing.

description.en: The Sport Pack adds a touch of sportiness to your MT-125 with its mix of accessories. The Fly Screen adds an aggressive, yet dynamic look for a true Dark Side of Japan feel. The sleek License Plate Holder sharpens up the rear, while stylish Engine Protectors make sure your engine is safeguarded while you ride as a true Master of Torque! Finally, the Tank Pad protects the tank of the bike from scratches. Are you ready to take the roads by storm?
description.sl-SI: Paket Sport Pack vsebuje razno dodatno opremo in vašemu modelu MT-125 doda pridih športnosti. Kratek vizir dodaja agresiven, a še vedno dinamičen videz, da resnično doživite temno plat Japonske. Vitek nosilec registrske tablice poskrbi za izrazitejši videz zadnjega dela, elegantni ščitniki agregata pa varujejo vaš motor med vožnjo kot resničen gospodar navora! Zaščita rezervoarja pa varuje rezervoar kolesa pred praskami. Ste pripravljeni, da osvojite ceste?

name.sl-SI: Majica z dolgimi rokavi Paddock Blue

description.en: The sporty Paddock Blue long sleeve is the ideal multipurpose shirt for workouts or casual days. The quick-dry, stretchy material features printed Yamaha Racing logos on chest and sleeve, and carries iconic black and white design elements. Get geared up with this long-sleeved shirt, and show your support for Yamaha Racing.
description.sl-SI: Športna majica z dolgimi rokavi Paddock Blue je idealna večnamenska majica, za treninge ali prosti čas. Hitro sušeči raztegljivi material ima natisnjene logotipe Yamaha Racing na prsih in rokavu ter ikonične črno-bele oblikovalske elemente. Opremite se s to majico z dolgimi rokavi in pokažite podporo Yamaha Racing.

description.en: Designed for track use only, the Adrenaline Pack is the quickest way to get increased performance from your R7. The full Akrapovič titanium exhaust system boosts power and saves weight – and the quick shifter enables clutchless gear shifting for racing-style, full-throttle acceleration. The R7 Adrenaline Pack also comes with a set of special racing covers and GB Racing crankcase protector as well as a billet front brake lever guard, tank side grip pads and smoked sports screen – and the rear seat cover and foot pedal adjuster kit enhance your racetrack potential even further. Are you ready for the track?
description.sl-SI: Paket Adrenaline je namenjen le za uporabo na stezi in je najhitrejši način, kako lahko iz svojega R7 dosežete boljše zmogljivosti. Celotni Akrapovičev izpušni sistem iz titana dvigne moč in zniža težo – sistem za hitro prestavljanje pa omogoča prestavljanje brez sklopke za pospeševanje s polnim plinom v dirkaškem slogu. Paket Adrenaline za R7 vsebuje tudi posebne dirkaške pokrove in ščitnik ohišja ročične gredi GB Racing ter ščitnik ročice zavore, stranske obloge rezervoarja za gorivo in zatemnjen športni vizir – pokrov zadnjega sedeža in komplet za nastavitev stopalke pa še dodatno povzdigneta vaš dirkaški potencial. Ste pripravljeni za stezo?

With a spacious capacity of 20 liters, Yamaha’s Adventure Backpack is a must-have accessory when you’re heading out into the mountains or trails for a longer ride. Its ergonomic design features a padded strap harness and adjustable chest and waist bands to ensure a perfect fit with a high level of comfort – and an integrated CE approved back protector provides added safety.  Multiple internal compartments provide plenty of storage for food, drink and more – and a centrally located padded battery compartment gives you the opportunity to enjoy longer rides.

Yamahin pustolovski nahrbtnik je s prostornino 20 litrov obvezna dodatna oprema, ko se odpravite v gore, na pot ali na daljšo vožnjo. Njegova ergonomska zasnova ima podložene naramnice in nastavljiva pasova čez prsa in trebuh, da zagotovi popolno prileganje z visoko stopnjo udobja, dodatno varnost pa zagotavlja integriran ščitnik hrbta s certifikatom CE. 

Več notranjih žepov nudi veliko prostora za shranjevanje hrane, pijače in še več, podložen predal za baterijo, ki se nahaja na sredini, pa vam daje priložnost, da uživate na daljših vožnjah.
