Povzdignite svoje motorno kolo MT-125 na višjo raven s kompletom Sport Pack, ki vključuje izbor dodatkov, posebej zasnovanih za izboljšanje zmogljivosti in sloga. Ta komplet, poleg izboljšanega oprijema in zaščite pred praskami, ki ju omogočajo stranske obloge rezervoarja, poskrbi tudi za bolj agresiven videz, saj vključuje namensko izdelan zatemnjen vizir, črne ročice ter nosilec registrske tablice. Nadgradite svojo vožnjo in izkusite 'temo'.
description.en: Elevate your MT-125 with the Sport Pack, a selection of accessories specifically designed to enhance both performance and style. Allowing you to experience improved grip and scratch protection thanks to the side tank pads, this pack also provides a more aggressive aesthetic through a purpose-built smoked fly screen, black levers and a licence plate holder. Upgrade your ride and feel the Darkness.

A perfect gift for Yamaha Sport Touring fans, the Sport Touring Tracer 9 GT Keyring is ideal for keeping your keys together and easy to find. Made from PVC with a Tracer 9 GT side profile design, it’s guaranteed to catch attention!

description.sl-SI: Mazivo za verigo Yamalube® je idealno za cestna motorna kolesa, saj formula z visoko stopnjo oprijema ustvarja odporen mazalni film, ki lahko vzdrži ekstremne pritiske. Nepogrešljiv dodatek za daljšo življenjsko dobo verige, vrhunsko zmogljivost in učinkovito porabo goriva. Priročna 56-mililitrska embalaža je priročna na daljših poteh in jo lahko napolnite s 300-mililitrsko pločevinko.
description.en: Yamalube® Chain Lube is ideal for road motorcycles, with a high-adhesion formula that creates a 'throw-off' resistant lubricating film able to withstand extreme pressures. Essential for longer chain life, peak performance and fuel efficiency. The 56ml Chain Lube is handy for longer rides and is refillable from the 300ml size.

description.sl-SI: MT-09 je utelešenje vsestranskosti. Ta urbana ikona s športno dušo je namenjena več kot le mestnim vožnjam – ustvarjena je za resno zabavo na ovinkastih gorskih cestah.  Zato smo izdelali 'Touring Pack', ki vam zagotavlja, da imate na voljo vse bistvene stvari za daljše vožnje z vašim motociklom MT-09. Srednji vizir in ščitnika členkov zagotavljajo boljšo zaščito pred vetrom, hkrati pa ohranjajo temeljno agresivno podobo modela MT-09. Za večje udobje paket vključuje udobne sedeže za vas in vašega sopotnika. Potrebujete tudi prtljažni prostor? Mehki stranski torbi s skupno prostornino 28 l, ki jo je mogoče razširiti do 42 l, sta opremljeni z vodoodporno notranjostjo in omogočata dovolj prostora za pakiranje vsega, kar potrebujete za oddih konec tedna.
description.en: The MT-09 is the embodiment of versatility. This urban icon with a sporty soul is meant for more than just city rides—it’s built for serious fun on twisty mountain roads.  That’s why we crafted the Touring Pack, ensuring you have all the essentials for longer rides on your MT-09. The middle screen and knuckle deflectors provide enhanced wind protection, while still maintaining the core aggressive look of the MT-09. For increased comfort, the pack includes comfort seats for both you and your passenger. Need luggage space as well? The soft side bags, offering a total capacity of 28L and expandable up to 42L, come with waterproof inner bags, giving you plenty of room to pack everything you need for a weekend getaway.

name.sl-SI: Olje za tekmovalne namene Yamalube® za dvotaktne motorje za terensko vožnjo (2R)

description.en: Yamalube® 2R is the ultimate oil for ultimate performance. In  extremes of temperature and under the toughest racing conditions, this ester-based premix lubricant really delivers. Motocross, Enduro, Trials, Quads … this is the hot one. Specially recommended when riding the amazing Yamaha YZ in competition.
description.sl-SI: Yamalube® 2R je vrhunsko olje za izredne zmogljivosti. To mazivo je vnaprej pripravljena mešanica, ki temelji na estru, in se odlično obnese pri ekstremnih temperaturah in v najtežjih dirkaških pogojih. Mazivo je primerno za motorna kolesa za motokros, enduro, in za štirikolesnike. Posebej priporočljiva uporaba, če na tekmovanjih vozite motorno kolo Yamaha YZ.

description.sl-SI: Otroške rokavice MX, ki so nepogrešljive v kompletu za mlade voznike modela MX, omogočajo popoln nadzor nad motornim kolesom ter kombinacijo udobja in zaščite. Zračna raztegljiva tkanina zagotavlja celovito zračenje, podložen del na dlaneh pa oprijem in dodatno hrapavo površino pri padcu. Na členkih je neoprenska in termoplastična guma za zaščito pred udarci, nastavljivi zapestniki pa prinašajo udobno prileganje, ki ustreza vsem velikostim.
description.en: An essential part of a young MX riders kit, the MX Kid’s Gloves allow full control of their bike with a combination of comfort and protection. Breathable stretch fabric offers all over ventilation, while the padded palm delivers grip and extra surface abrasion in a fall. The knuckles feature neoprene and thermoplastic rubber for impact protection, and adjustable wrists allow a comfort fit for all sizes.
Sport screen, 30% transparency. Non DOT version.
The handlebar switch can be used as pit limiter, mode change, map change and rear light activation.

High density 50.4V/19.2Ah lithium-ion battery giving a range of 37km*– and range can be extended by purchasing this optional extra battery. Two batteries can be installed on NEO’s simultaneously, extending the riding range up to 68km*.  For more convenience, you can also keep a spare battery at home. This 8kg battery is designed to maintain a high level of efficiency for 1000 cycles/10,000km, and charging can be carried out with batteries fitted to the scooter or when removed. (*Tested in WMTC Class 1 in STD mode, fully charged battery at a temperature of 25°C.)
description.sl-SI: Litij-ionska baterija s 50.4 V/19.2 Ah z visoko gostoto omogoča doseg do 37 km*, ki ga lahko še povečate, če kupite izbirno dodatno baterijo. V vozila NEO's je mogoče namestiti dve bateriji hkrati ter s tem podaljšati doseg za vožnjo do 68 km*.  Za več udobja pa lahko dodatno baterijo hranite tudi doma. Ta 8-kilogramska baterija je zasnovana tako, da ohranja visoko raven učinkovitosti 1000 ciklov/10.000 km, polnjenje pa se lahko izvaja, ko je baterija nameščena v skuter ali ko je odstranjena. (*Testirano v WMTC razred 1, v načinu STD, s popolnoma napolnjeno baterijo pri temperaturi 25 °C.)

The Öhlins NIX 30 Cartridge Kit for standard KYB fork was developed in racing series such as World Supersport and Superstock championships, and offers loads of performance, stability and suppleness. This kit has a unique design, with the compression damping in the left fork leg while the right leg controls rebound damping. This allows not only for a more precise function and better stability, but also the ease of having all adjustments conveniently placed at the top of the fork.
description.sl-SI: Komplet vložkov Öhlins NIX 30 za standardne vilice KYB je bil razvit v sklopu dirkaške serije, kot so svetovno prvenstvo Supersport in prvenstva Superstock, ter omogoča izredno zmogljivost, stabilnost ter okretnost. Ta komplet ima edinstveno zasnovo s kompresijskim blaženjem v levem kraku vilic, medtem ko desni krak nadzoruje povratno blaženje. To omogoča bolj natančno delovanje in boljšo stabilnost, vse prilagoditve pa so priročno nameščene na vrh vilic.
S parom ščitnikov za zaščito oklepa, ki so enostavni za montažo, zaščitite zadnji del svojega skuterja Yamaha XMAX pred praskami.
description.en: Avoid scratches to your Yamaha XMAX with the rear scratch protector, a pair of easy-to-install cowling protectors.

A pure vintage design that’s right at home among the Sport Heritage XSR range, the Faster Sons neck tube in blue and black is perfect for touring and outdoor use. Polyester construction creates a soft touch, while the design is brought to life with iconic speed blocks, heritage stripes and Yamaha branding. An ideal accompanying garment for the Faster Sons range.
description.sl-SI: Cevast šal Faster Sons v modri in črni barvi je idealen za vožnjo in uporabo na prostem. Odlikuje ga vintage videz, zato se lepo poda seriji Sport Heritage XSR. Tkanina iz poliestra je mehka na dotik, poživi pa jo podoba ikonične grafike 'Speedblock', klasičnih črt in Yamahinega logotipa. Idealen dodatek oblačilom iz linije Faster Sons.

description.en: A cool blue eyewear for young ones, the Paddock Blue sunglasses make a real statement of Yamaha passion. A polycarbonate frame ensures a lightweight but strong build, and tinted blue lenses with UV400 protection help protect the eyes.
description.sl-SI: Kul modra sončna očala za otroke Paddock Blue izražajo navdušenje nad Yamaho. Polikarbonatna masa zagotavlja lahek, a vzdržljiv okvir, zatemnjene modre leče z zaščito UV400 pa pomagajo zaščititi oči. Bel Yamahin logotip ob straneh poskrbi za jasno identifikacijo, črna zaščitna vrečka pa omogoča enostavno shranjevanje in prenašanje.

name.sl-SI: Motoristična softshell jakna 2-v-1 Paddock Blue za ženske

description.en: Technical and stylish for Paddock Blue fans that ride, the blue and black Paddock Blue Women’s Riding Softshell offers 2-in-1 functionality for comfort on all roads. A softshell outer with protection pockets and hydro repellent treatment covers the removable armoured riding mesh, featuring Warrior Lite armour for the elbows and shoulders. A fixed hood with snap closure prevents it from moving during the ride, while two outer pockets and one inner pocket give ample room for essential items. A Paddock Blue classic for regular use on two wheels in all weathers.
description.sl-SI: Tehnična in stilska motoristična softshell jakna Paddock Blue za ženske v modri in črni za voznice, ki se navdušujejo nad linijo Paddock Blue, združuje dva izdelka v enem za funkcionalnost in udobje na vseh poteh. Mehkoščitna tkanina softshell je odporna na vodo, na zunanji strani so zaščitni žepi, v notranjosti pa snemljiva zaščitna mrežica, poleg tega jakna vključuje ščitnike Warrior Lite za komolce in ramena. Fiksna kapuca na zapenjanje s pritiskači preprečuje plapolanje med vožnjo, dva zunanja žepa in en notranji pa omogočajo dovolj prostora za vse pomembne predmete. Klasični izdelek linije Paddock Blue za redno uporabo, ko ste na dveh kolesih v vseh vremenskih razmerah.

description.sl-SI: Kolesa z 12-krakimi litimi platišči serije J za vse terene, ki so na voljo v pripravljenem sklopu, zagotavljajo večji oprijem za enostavno vožnjo po brezpotjih.

description.en: Prewired grip heater with unit display/control function
description.sl-SI: Predhodno ožičen grelnik ročk z enoto za funkcijo zaslona/nadzora

name.sl-SI: Rebrasta kapa Paddock Blue za odrasle

description.en: Chunky, colourful and made for warmth, the Paddock Blue Adult Ribbed Beanie offers a cosy unisex fit wherever life takes you. Knitted from 100% cotton, this beanie’s thick two-tone ribbing ensures comfort and a strong shape. A turn up hem features an embroidered Yamaha Racing badge for an unmistakable fashion item.
description.sl-SI: Debela, barvita in topla rebrasta kapa Paddock Blue za odrasle omogoča udobno prileganje za oba spola na prav vseh poteh. Pletena je iz 100-odstotnega bombaža, debela rebrasta plast, obarvana v dva odtenka, pa prinaša udobje in trdno obliko. Na zavihanem robu je izvezen logotip Yamaha Racing, s čimer je to nezamenljiv modni izdelek.

name.sl-SI: Plastična prirubnica za krmo za XTO
name.en: Plastic transom flange for the XTO

description.sl-SI: Hidravlični sistemi za krmiljenje tip LS 3500 PRO. Kompletni kit (standardni sistem vključuje cilindar, črpalka s ključavnico ventilom, vsi priključki, tok za polnjenje in 12m cev)
description.en: Transom flange connector entering the hull for fitment of the 2.5 Inch rigging hose.
GYTR Rear Sprocket with 42T for 520 Chain conversion for Marchesini wheels

name.sl-SI: Mazivo za verigo Yamalube za suhe razmere

description.sl-SI: Mazivo za verigo Yamalube za suhe razmere je bilo posebej razvito za optimalno učinkovitost poganjanja v suhih ali prašnih pogojih. Popolnoma lahka sintetična formula pripomore k odbijanju umazanije in prahu, hkrati pa ohranja optimalno podmazano verigo in vodilo verige – prav tako je popolnoma biorazgradljivo.
description.en: Yamalube Dry Chain Lube has been specially developed to give you optimum pedaling efficiency in dry or dusty conditions. Its lightweight fully synthetic formula helps to repel dirt and dust while maintaining optimum chain and derailleur lubrication – and is fully biodegradable.

description.sl-SI: Originalni Yamahin nosilec rezervne pnevmatike se varno namesti na prtljažnik vozila Wolverine prek tovarniških pritrdišč in lahko nosi do 32-palčno pnevmatiko.
description.en: The Genuine Yamaha Spare Tyre Mount securely installs to the bed of the Wolverine using all factory mounting points to hold up to a 32” tyre size.

name.sl-SI: Monster Energy® Yamaha Factory MXGP Team Replica Sweater Women
name.en: Monster Energy® Yamaha Factory MXGP Team Replica Sweater Women

description.sl-SI: Drzno oblikovan in udoben pulover Monster Energy® Yamaha Factory MXGP Team Women's Replica nudi toploto in vsestranskost za spreminjajoče se razmere ob progi. Pulover je oblikovan po ikonični modro-črni barvi dirkalnika YZ450FM in ima bele poudarke na hrbtni strani in ob straneh. Tesno prilegajoča se kapuca zagotavlja dodatno udobje, zadrga po celotni dolžini in zunanji žepi pa nudijo prostor za osebne predmete. Robovi in manšete iz samosvoje tkanine zagotavljajo tesno prileganje, izvezeni oznaki Yamaha Racing in Monster Energy® pa združujeta ta ekipni izdelek.
description.en: Boldly designed and comfortable, the Monster Energy® Yamaha Factory MXGP Team Women’s Replica Sweater offers warmth and versatility for changing trackside conditions. Styled after the iconic blue and black livery of the YZ450FM race bike, the sweater features white highlights on the back and side. A tight-fitting hood offers extra comfort, with a full-length zip and external pockets with room for personal items. Self-fabric hem and cuffs ensure a snug fit, with embroidered Yamaha Racing and Monster Energy® branding bringing this team item together.
Durable protection for tight approaches, high stumps or rocks on the trail.
description.sl-SI: Trpežna zaščita za vožnjo po ozkih območjih, visoke štore ali kamenje po poti.

description.en: Custom handlebar ends to enhance the design of your Yamaha.
description.sl-SI: Po meri izdelani konci krmila za še lepši videz vaše Yamahe.

description.en: We know how it feels to be left wanting for more space to stow away essentials, so we equipped the Urban Pack with an integrated rear carrier and beautifully designed 39L top case that gobbles up your helmet, extra luggage or anything else that you throw at it. An integral back rest pad gives your passenger a comfortable ride – and the high screen provides added wind protection while keeping your line of sight clear. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your Tricity 300.
description.sl-SI: Poznamo občutek, ko zmanjka prostora za shrambo nujnih potrebščin, zato smo Urbani paket opremili z vgrajenim zadnjim nosilcem in čudovito oblikovanim 39-litrskim kovčkom, ki sprejme vašo čelado, dodatno prtljago ali karkoli drugega, kar želite spraviti vanj. Vgrajen zadnji naslon skrbi za udobno vožnjo potnika – visok zaslon pa deluje kot dodatna zaščita pred vetrom in obenem omogoča čist pogled. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš Tricity 300.

description.en: This dark smoked short screen gives your X-MAX a sporty look.

description.sl-SI: Popestrite slog Yamahinega skuterja NMAX z zaključkom krmila, izdelanim iz eloksiranega aluminija, z vgraviranimi podrobnostmi za dodaten športni pridih.
description.en: Add new style to your Yamaha NMAX with the Handlebar End, made from anodized aluminium and featuring engraved details for an extra sporty touch.
Durable Knuckle guard kit with integrated MT design and including wind deflectors.
description.sl-SI: Komplet trpežnih ščitnikov za členke z vgrajeno MT zasnovo in vključno z odbojniki vetra.

name.en: Ténéré 700 World Raid Enduro Pack White
name.sl-SI: Paket Enduro za model Ténéré 700 World Raid

description.en: Ready for some serious off road riding? Then you are in the right place. Take your Ténéré 700 World Raid to the next level with the Enduro Pack and enjoy the adrenaline rush.
description.sl-SI: Ali ste pripravljeni na resno terensko vožnjo? Potem ste na pravem mestu. Popeljite svoj model Ténéré 700 World Raid na novo raven s paketom Enduro in uživajte v navalu adrenalina.

description.en: We know how annoying and difficult it can be to store small items in the underseat storage. The trunk organizer helps you with storing them, so you can find them easily and have your underseat storage organized.
description.sl-SI: Vemo, kako nadležno in težko je lahko shranjevanje majhnih predmetov v prostoru pod sedežem. Organizator prostora vam pomaga pri shranjevanju stvari, da jih lahko enostavno najdete in imate prostor pod sedežem urejen.

name.en: GYTR Marchesini R6 Aluminium Rear Wheel (Gold)

description.en: Forged aluminium rear wheel with low centre of gravity made for the R1 by Marchesini. The use of multi-directional aluminum alloy forging and the use of shapes optimized for the final geometry of the wheel make it possible to obtain a very light material with exceptional mechanical specifications.
Completely built front wheel
Make your Yamaha look even cooler!
description.sl-SI: Za še bolj izpopolnjen videz vaše Yamahe!

description.en: Tire warmers allow you to get full performance from your machine right from the starting line, and without having to do several laps to warm up your tires.
description.sl-SI: Grelniki pnevmatik omogočajo popolne zmogljivosti vašega motorja takoj od začetka, brez potrebe po dodatnih vožnjah za ogrevanje pnevmatik.
Neopazna, a funkcionalna zaščita šasije pri padcu. Narejena po meri agregata in šasije. Poleg tega pa ti stranski drsniki okrepijo robustni videz vašega R125.
description.en: Discrete, yet functional, chassis protection in case of a fall. Made to fit the engine and chassis layout. These side sliders also provide an added look of toughness to your R125.

name.en: Yamaha Hyper Naked  MT-09 ceramic Mug
name.sl-SI: Keramična skodelica Yamaha Hyper Naked MT-09

description.en: Part of the Iconic mugs collection, this version offers the MT-09 design. Enjoy your coffee or cup of tea in true Yamaha style.
description.sl-SI: Ta različica, ki je del kolekcije skodelic Iconic, ponuja dizajn MT-09. Uživajte v skodelici kave ali čaja v pravem Yamahinem slogu.

name.en: Yamaha's Rear Sequential LED Blinker Kit for the Ténéré 700
name.sl-SI: Yamahin komplet zadnjih sekvenčnih LED utripalk za model Ténéré 700

description.en: Introducing Yamaha's Rear Sequential LED Blinker Kit for the Ténéré 700 – Redefining safety and elegance on the road. Elevate your Ténéré 700 experience with a captivating sequence of LEDs meticulously designed to improve visibility and showcase the distinctive style of your Yamaha. Crafted for seamless integration, this rear blinker set not only signals every move but also makes a bold statement. Ride with confidence as the sequential LED display adds an extra layer of sophistication to your Ténéré 700, ensuring you make a lasting impression on every journey. Immerse yourself in the perfect fusion of safety and style with Yamaha's Rear Sequential LED Blinker Ensemble tailored for the Ténéré 700.
description.sl-SI: Predstavljamo Yamahin komplet zadnjih sekvenčnih LED utripalk za Ténéré 700 - na novo opredeljuje varnost in eleganco na cesti. Izboljšajte svoje doživetje pri Ténéréju 700 z očarljivim zaporedjem diod LED, ki so skrbno oblikovane za izboljšanje vidljivosti in predstavitev značilnega sloga vaše Yamahe. Ta komplet zadnjih utripalnikov, izdelan za brezhibno integracijo, ne signalizira le vsakega giba, temveč daje tudi drzno izjavo. Vozite samozavestno, saj zaporedni prikaz LED dodaja vašemu Ténéréju 700 dodatno plast prefinjenosti in zagotavlja, da boste na vsakem potovanju naredili nepozaben vtis. Potopite se v popolno združitev varnosti in sloga z Yamahinim kompletom zadnjih sekvenčnih LED-blinkerjev, ki je prilagojen za Ténéré 700.
Čistilni gel Yamalube® je okolju prijazno, učinkovito, vsestransko čistilo na vodni osnovi za motorna kolesa, skuterje, izvenkrmne motorje, ATV-je in drugo.
description.en: Yamalube® Cleaning Gel is an eco-friendly, effective, water-based, all-round cleaner for motorcycles, scooters, outboard engines, ATVs and more.

name.sl-SI: Stikalo za zaklepanje zgornjega kovčka brez ključa – skuterji
name.en: Keyless Top Case Locking Switch - Scooters

description.sl-SI: S stikalom za zaklepanje zgornjega kovčka zavarujte svojo prtljago na skuterju. S pritiskom zaklenite in odklenite zgornji kovček brez ključa
description.en: Secure your Scooter luggage with the Top Case Locking Switch. Push to lock and unlock your Keyless Top Case
Base to hold a GPS device.

description.en: Make your Tracer 700 look and sound even cooler!
description.sl-SI: Za še bolj izpopolnjen izgled in zvok vašega modela Tracer 700!

description.en: Part of the GYTR® Clutch Components which are precision machined from aerospace-quality aluminum with a unique hard coating.
description.sl-SI: Del sestavnih delov sklopke GYTR®, ki so natančno izdelani iz aluminija letalske kakovosti, z edinstveno trdo prevleko.
Komplet grelnikov ročk s predpripravljenimi kabli za preprosto namestitev zagotavlja tople roke in prilagodljivost pri vožnji v hladnejšem vremenu. Enostaven za namestitev in nadzor za udobno vožnjo.
description.en: Prewired and ready to connect, the Grip Heater Set ensures warm hands and flexibility on colder rides. Easy to install and control for comfort riding.

name.en: Paddock Blue Essentials Polo shirt Women
name.sl-SI: Ženska polo majica Paddock Blue Essentials

description.en: Buttoned women's Paddock Blue polo shirt with Yamaha Racing logos on chest and sleeve. This smart polo also features various black and white design elements.
description.sl-SI: Ženska polo majica na zapenjanje Paddock Blue z logotipi Yamaha Racing na prsih in rokavu. Ta polo majica ima tudi različne črne in bele oblikovalske elemente.

name.sl-SI: Lahki dušilnik Akrapovič za XMAX 125 v črni barvi

description.en:
Street legal Akrapovič muffler to improve the performance, sound and looks of your XMAX 125. 
This is a non Yamaha branded product and is fully developed and produced by Akrapovic. 
Important note: Installation requires cutting of standard muffler. We advise you to visit your Yamaha dealer for proper installation.
description.sl-SI:
Homologirani dušilnik Akrapovič za boljše zmogljivosti, zvok in videz vašega XMAX 125. 
To ni izdelek Yamahe. V celoti ga je razvilo in izdelalo podjetje Akrapovič. 
Pomembno: Namestitev zahteva rezanje standardnega dušilnika. Svetujemo vam, da za pravilno namestitev obiščete svojega prodajalca Yamaha.

description.en: Made for adventure and exploration, the stainless-steel Ténéré thermos flask is a must-have for off-road trips. The 500ml capacity keeps drinks warm and secure for long trips, with a carry loop on the lid giving extra ease of use. A nice metallic brown finish with racing blue accents and white Ténéré graphics give this flask a true adventurer’s look.
description.sl-SI: Termovka Ténéré iz nerjavnega jekla je odlična za pustolovščine in raziskovanje. Na dolgih izletih varno hrani 500 ml toplega napitka, nosilna zanka na pokrovu pa dodatno poenostavi uporabo. Lepo kovinsko površino v rjavi barvi dopolnjujejo bela grafika serije Ténéré in modri poudarki, ki termovki dajejo pravi pustolovski videz.

description.en: You can also enjoy riding your XMAX during the cold and rainy days with the Winter Pack.  To keep your hands warm , whatever the condition, we have included the grip heaters, which are seamlessly integrated into the design. We also included the hand muffs to amp up the protections which by combining with the grip heaters, provide optimum protection against wind chill.  The Apron does an excellent job of protecting your lower body from the cold, wind and rain, including an integrated seat cover and a zip to detach the apron in warmer weather.   Available from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your XMAX.
description.sl-SI: Z zimskim paketom lahko v vožnji z vozilom XMAX uživate tudi v hladnih in deževnih dneh.  Grelniki ročk, ki so neopazno vgrajeni v zasnovo, ohranjajo vaše roke tople, ne glede na razmere. Vključili smo tudi mufe za roke za boljšo zaščito, ki s kombinacijo grelnikov ročk zagotavljajo optimalno zaščito pred hladnim vetrom.  Zaščita za sprednji del odlično zaščiti spodnji del telesa pred mrazom, vetrom in dežjem, vključno s prevleko za sedež in zadrgo, s katero lahko zaščito v toplejših vremenskih razmerah odstranite.   Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaše vozilo XMAX.

description.en: GYTR® fuel cap tool for the GYTR® Fuel cap (Screw type)

description.sl-SI: Zasnovan je za sodobne voznike, saj omogoča priročno zaklepanje in odklepanje brez težav s klasičnimi ključi. Preprosto imejte pametni ključ pri sebi, da zagotovite (od)zaklepanje stranskega kovčka, kadarkoli greste mimo motocikla.
description.en: Ideated for the modern riders, to enable convenient locking & unlocking without the hassle of traditional keys. Simply have your unit smart key with you to ensure the side case is (un)locked whenever you walk by your vehicle.
Machined triple clamp to improve drivability and stiffness. And provide a higher riding position when combined together with the handlebar clamps.
description.sl-SI: Strojno obdelana trojna objemka za izboljšanje vodljivosti in togosti. V kombinaciji z objemkami za krmilo zagotavlja tudi višji položaj med vožnjo.

OM COVER F80D in F100F sta več kot le zaščitna pokrova; sta popolna mešanica sloga, vzdržljivosti in vrhunske zmogljivosti. Ne glede na to, ali želite zaščititi zunanje pohištvo, opremo ali druge dragocene predmete, ta pokrivala zagotavljajo popolno zaščito pred vremenskimi vplivi. Ne sklepajte kompromisov glede kakovosti. Izberite OM COVER F80D in F100F za zanesljivo, elegantno in dolgotrajno zaščito.
description.en: The OM COVER F80D and F100F are more than just protective covers; they are a perfect blend of style, durability, and superior performance. Whether you need to shield your outdoor furniture, equipment, or other valuable items, these covers deliver the ultimate defense against the elements. Don’t compromise on quality. Choose OM COVER F80D and F100F for reliable, stylish, and long-lasting protection.

description.sl-SI: Ekskluzivna zasnova, nizek sedež, ki omogoča, da voznik lažje doseže stik s podlago.
description.en: Exclusively designed, low seat providing additional space to improve ground access for the rider.

name.sl-SI: Popoln dirkaški izpušni sistem iz titana

description.en: This system provides more power and weight reductions to suite racing requirements
description.sl-SI: Ta sistem zagotavlja več moči in zmanjšanje teže, da se prilagodi tekmovalnim zahtevam.

description.sl-SI: Mehanizem Öhlins NIX 30 za standardne sprednje vilice ali vilice Öhlins FGRT200. Uporabljeno pri modelu R6/R1/MT10

description.en: Provides more grip compared to the standard seat option.

Preprečite poškodbe na Yamahinem skuterju NMAX s ščitnikom oklepa pred praskami – parom ščitnikov, ki omogočata enostavno namestitev in preprečujeta praske na oklepu.
description.en: Avoid damage to your Yamaha NMAX with the Fairing Scratch Protector - a pair of easy-to-install protectors that prevent scratches to your cowling.
All GYTR® parts are precision machined from aerospace-quality aluminium alloys with a unique hard coating.
description.sl-SI: Vsi deli GYTR® so natančno strojno obdelani iz aluminijevih zlitin letalske kakovosti z edinstveno trdo prevleko

name.sl-SI: Kratka majica Paddock Blue Essentials za moške

description.en: Simple and eye-catching, the Paddock Blue Essentials Men’s T-Shirt is a must for every Yamaha fan’s wardrobe. Made from 100% cotton for a consistent soft feel, this tee’s regular fit and crew neck ensure a comfortable fit for any wearer. Printed Yamaha chest and arm branding give an iconic paddock style.
description.sl-SI: Preprosta in privlačna kratka majica Paddock Blue Essentials za moške je nepogrešljiva v garderobi vsakega Yamahinega navdušenca. Izdelana je iz 100-odstotnega bombaža za mehek občutek, sešita je v običajnem kroju in ima okrogli izrez, kar zagotavlja udobno prileganje. Yamahina logotipa na prsih in rokavu poskrbita za ikonski dirkaški slog.

description.en: The Accessory Power Lead Kit wires your preferred accessories to the unit’s five pre-wired switched 12vdc power couplers which are located under the dash of all Wolverine models.
description.sl-SI: Komplet Accessory Power Lead poveže vaše priljubljene dodatke na eno od pet spojk, ki so povezane na enosmerni tok napetosti 12 V, ki se nahajajo pod armaturno ploščo na vseh modelih Wolverine.
Ohranite svojo Yamaho NMAX 'nedotaknjeno' z zaščito konzole, naborom trdih nalepk, ki ščitijo konzolo pred praskami in vašemu skuterju dodajo športni pridih.
description.en: Keep your Yamaha NMAX pristine with the Console Protection, a set of hard-layer stickers that protect the console from scratches and add sporty style to your scooter.

name.sl-SI: Komplet ležajev za sprednje kolo, 22 mm

description.en: Complete replacement kit including seal closed KOYO bearings, seals, distance collar and circlip
description.sl-SI: Celovit nadomestni komplet, ki vsebuje zatesnjene ležaje KOYO, tesnila, distančni obroč in batni obroček

description.en: Catalytic Convertor to be used for different exhaust systems to fulfil EU4 regulations
description.sl-SI: Katalizator se uporablja za različne izpušne sisteme, da izpolnjujejo predpise EU4.

Kapa za odrasle Fabio Quartararo, ki jo morate imeti za toplejše dni ob stezi in zunaj nje, je nepogrešljiv dodatek v garderobi ljubiteljev dirk. Kapa je narejena iz 100-odstotnega bombaža in ima ukrivljen sendvič vrh, na katerem je izvezen Fabiov rdeči logotip „20“. Na sprednji strani v tekmovalno modri barvi je logotip Yamaha Racing v beli barvi, stilsko kapo pa dopolnjujeta logotipa M1 in 20 na hrbtni strani in ob straneh. Zaradi nastavljivega traku je kapa udobna za različne velikosti glave.
description.en: A must-have for warmer days trackside and outside, the Fabio Quartararo Adults Cap is an essential addition to a race fan’s wardrobe. Made from 100% cotton, the cap features a curved sandwich peak embroidered with Fabio’s red ‘20’ logo. A Racing Blue front carries the Yamaha Racing logo in white, with the stylish cap completed by M1 and 20 logos on the back and side. An adjustable strap makes it comfortable for a range of head sizes.

name.sl-SI: Notranja torba za stranska kovčka City

description.en: Inner bag set fitting luggage in the City Side cases
description.sl-SI: Komplet notranjih torb, ki se prilegajo stranskim kovčkom City

description.en: Two zinc D-rings can be easily connected to a suitable lifting mechanism.
description.sl-SI: Obroča v obliki črke D iz cinka je mogoče preprosto pritrditi na primeren dvižni mehanizem.

description.en: The bracket allows mounting of optional fog lights below the main headlight.
description.sl-SI: Nosilec omogoča namestitev dodatnih meglenk pod glavni žaromet.

description.en: Yamaha also takes our young and small water fanatics' safety into consideration. Our Yamaha Lifestyle 100N can ensure our kids' safety while having fun on the water. The bright orange colour featuring the retro-reflecting tapes can be seen clearly on the water and from the shore.
description.sl-SI: Yamaha poskrbi tudi za varnost svojih mladih in majhnih vodnih navdušencev. Rešilni jopič Yamaha 100N zagotavlja varnost otrok med zabavnimi aktivnostmi v vodi. Svetlo oranžno barvo z retro-odsevnimi trakovi lahko vidite tako iz vode, kot tudi z obale.

Z elegantnim paketom 'Street' stilsko dopolnite videz svojega motornega kolesa XSR900. Paket poskrbi za vrhunski končni izgled, s katerim se vaš XSR prelevi v kultno urbano motorno kolo. Sprednji del polepšajte s športnim vizirjem za nadzorno ploščo z zračnikom, ščitnikom žarometa in črnim aluminijastim sprednjim blatnikom. Izboljšajte oprijem na rezervoarju s kolenskimi blazinicami za gladko vožnjo skozi zavoje in vrhunski nadzor ter z nosilcem registrske tablice pričarajte čist in še bolj športen videz zadnjega dela.
description.en: Providing your XSR900 with an extra sleek look is easy with the stylish Street Pack. The pack ensures an extra premium finish that easily customizes your XSR into an urban hero. Style the front end with the sporty air-vented cockpit visor, headlight guard and black aluminum front fender. Increase your grip on the tank with the knee grips pads for those faster corners and ultimate riding control while the license plate holder cleans up the rear end with an even sportier look.

description.sl-SI: S svojim drznim in agresivnim videzom je MT-09 prava paša za oči, 'Sport Pack Silver' pa to samo še nadgradi. Nosilec za zaključek krmila in ščitnika členkov zagotavljajo večjo zaščito pred vetrom, hkrati pa prispevajo k agresivnemu videzu sprednjega dela MT-09, skupaj z aluminijastim vizirjem. Na zadnji strani preoblikovan nosilec registrske tablice izboljša drzen profil motornega kolesa. Zaključek zagotavljajo stranske blazinice za oprijem na rezervoarju, ki ne le ščitijo pred praskami, temveč nudijo tudi dodaten oprijem za samozavestno vožnjo v ovinkih.
description.en: With its bold and aggressive design, the MT-09 is already a real head-turner and the Sport Pack Silver takes it even further. The bar end base and knuckle deflectors provide increased wind protection, while also enhancing the aggressive look of the MT-09’s front end alongside the aluminium visor. At the rear, the streamlined licence plate holder enhances the bike’s sharp profile. The finishing touch is provided by the side tank grip pads that not only protect against scratches but also offer extra grip for confident cornering.
The indicator provides a clear view of the charge condition of the battery.
Cover to replace the original belt cover for added style.

Shoulder and elbow protectors offer confidence and peace of mind when riding, while 6 pockets offer substantial space for items. description.sl-SI:
Komplet TRACER 9 'Travel Pack Pro' je vrhunski sklop opreme za voznike, ki zahtevajo udobje, priročnost in vsestranskost. Visok vizir in dodaten širok zaščitni vizir zagotavljata odlično zaščito pred vetrom, ogrevan udoben sedež in sopotnikov sedež pa prinašata udobje vam kakor tudi sopotniku med dolgimi vožnjami. V opremo so vključeni sistem za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah (TPMS) in ogrevane ročke, da lahko vozite samozavestno ne glede na vremenske razmere. Zgornji kovček in stranska kovčka ponujajo dovolj prostora za shranjevanje vseh vaših bistvenih stvari, medtem ko polnilnik USB in vtičnica držala ohranjata vaše naprave pripravljene in dostopne.

Nosilec za GPS omogoča enostavno uporabo navigacije, zaradi ščitnika hladilnika in zaščite agregata 'Explorer' pa je vožnja še bolj brezskrbna. Komplet meglenk LED in nosilec za meglenke zagotavljata optimalno vidljivost v vseh pogojih. Zavarujte vso svojo opremo z nosilno ploščo za zgornji kovček, kompleti nosilcev in kompletom ključev za cilindrično ključavnico za hiter dostop. S paketom TRACER 9 'Travel Pack Pro' je vsaka pustolovščina brezhibna mešanica sloga, udobja in funkcionalnosti.
description.en:
The TRACER 9 Travel Pack Pro is the ultimate setup for riders who demand comfort, convenience, and versatility. The High Screen and Add-On Wide Screen provide excellent wind protection, while the Heated Comfort Seat and Passenger Seat keep both you and your passenger comfortable during long rides. Equipped with a Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS) and Heated Grips, you can ride confidently, no matter the weather. The Top Case and Side Cases offer ample storage for all your essentials, while the USB Charger and Holder Socket keep your devices ready and accessible.

Navigate easily with the GPS Stay, and ride with peace of mind knowing your bike is protected by the Radiator Guard and Explorer Engine Guard. The LED Fog Light Kit and Fog Light Stay ensure optimal visibility in any conditions. Secure all your gear with the Top Case Mounting Plate, Stay Kits, and Key Cylinder Set for quick access. With the TRACER 9 Travel Pack Pro, every adventure is a seamless blend of style, comfort, and function.

name.sl-SI: Čistilo za čelade in vizirje Yamalube®

description.en: The residues from dust, dirt and countless insects are the penalty we pay for our riding enjoyment – and not just on our helmets and visors, but on headlights, windscreens and body parts too! These residues can be a visibility and safety issue as well as detracting from the visual appeal of our machines. This special cleaner solves the problem quickly – keep it in your backpack!

Omenjeni ostanki lahko otežijo vidljivost in predstavljajo varnostno tveganje, poleg tega pa negativno vplivajo na videz naših vozil. To posebno čistilo omenjene težave hitro reši – pospravite ga kar v nahrbtnik!

description.en:
Yamalube Cleaning Gel is an environmentally neutral, quick, and effective universal cleaner for cleaning motorbikes, Scooters, outboard engines, boats, etc. The optimized water-based formula is biodegradable and therefore environmentally friendly. 
Mode of use: Spray the entire vehicle with the "YAMALUBE Gel Cleaner", let it act for 5 minutes, then rinse it thoroughly with a strong jet of water. 
In case of extreme dirt (e.g., chain grease or encrusted oil) let it act for up to 30 minutes after application. Rinse it out until the foam stops coming out. If necessary, use a sponge.
description.sl-SI:
Čistilni gel Yamalube je okolju neškodljivo, hitro in učinkovito univerzalno čistilo za čiščenje motornih koles, skuterjev, izvenkrmnih motorjev, čolnov itd. Optimizirana formula na vodni osnovi je biorazgradljiva in zato okolju prijazna. 
Način uporabe: Celotno vozilo poškropite s čistilnim gelom YAMALUBE, pustite delovati 5 minut, nato temeljito sperite z močnim curkom vode. 
V primeru trdovratne umazanije (npr. maščoba na verigi ali zasušeno olje) pustite delovati do 30 minut po nanosu. Izpirajte, dokler pena ne preneha iztekati. Po potrebi uporabite gobico.

description.en: With stunning racing blue and contrasting stripes, the Paddock Blue Men’s Jogging Pants offer comfort and urban style. Featuring a blend of cotton  and polyester in a French Terry finish, the pant legs are highlighted with a white stripe and retro style tape to pair with other Streetwear garments. With a tapered fit and elastic waist, the legs also feature a subtle zip opening at the ends for breathability. Embroidered Yamaha Racing branding gives them a final touch of style.
description.sl-SI: Tekaške hlače Paddock Blue za moške v očarljivi dirkaški modri barvi ter s črtami v kontrastni barvi ponujajo udobje in videz mestnega sloga. Izdelane so iz bombaža in poliestra z zunanjo plastjo iz francoskega frotirja, hlačnice krasi bela črta in trak v retro slogu za popolno ujemanje z drugimi oblačili kolekcije Streetwear. Hlače imajo tajliran kroj in elastični pas, na dnu hlačnic je tudi prefinjena odprtina na zadrgo za zračenje. Izvezen logotip Yamaha Racing poskrbi za popoln slog.

description.en: Enhance the coolness of your Yamaha.
description.sl-SI: Izboljša odličen videz vaše Yamahe.

description.en: The MT-09 invented the Hyper Naked category. The breath-taking combination of its high torque CP3 engine and a dynamic sports chassis is designed to get your adrenaline pumping. And since day one it’s been the bike of choice for every rider who appreciates what real motorcycling is all about. In standard trim it’s the most impressive bike in the class – but when you want to take the aggressive looks to the next level the Sport Pack is surely the way to go.
description.sl-SI: Model MT-09 je izumil kategorijo Hyper Naked. Dih jemajoča kombinacija visokega navora agregata CP3 in dinamične športne šasije je zasnovana tako, da vam požene adrenalin. In že od prvega dne je bil ta motocikel prva izbira vsakega voznika, ki ceni bistvo pravega motociklizma. V različici z osnovno opremo je najbolj impresiven motocikel v svojem razredu – če pa želite agresiven videz dvigniti na naslednjo raven, pa je Sport Pack zagotovo prava izbira.

description.sl-SI: Replika moške polo majice Monster Energy® Yamaha Factory MXGP Team je prefinjen izdelek, ki je zasnovan v dirkaškem duhu. Črn trup je poudarjen z dirkaško modrimi rokami, oblikovanimi po vzoru stroja YZ450FM, z belimi črtami na hrbtu in straneh. Posebej izdelan ovratnik z gumbom zagotavlja udobno prileganje, z izvezenima blagovnima znamkama Yamaha Racing in Monster Energy® pa je prava klasika na stezi.
description.en: A smart-casual essential for race days, the Monster Energy® Yamaha Factory MXGP Team Men’s Replica Polo Shirt is a sophisticated item designed with racing spirit. A black torso is highlighted with racing blue arms styled on the YZ450FM machine, with white stripe details on the back and sides. A specially engineered button closure collar ensures a comfort fit, with embroidered Yamaha Racing and Monster Energy® branding for a true pit lane classic.

Just screw this sleek aluminum mount into the stem of your motorbike and you can easily mount the Yamaha phone case or SP ConnectTM compatible devices, by placing it on the mount and turning it 90 clockwise.

Le privijte tanek aluminijasti nosilec na krmilo motocikla in z lahkoto lahko namestite ovitek na telefon SP Connect TM tako, da ga položite na nosilec in zavrtite za 90° v smeri urinega kazalca. Vaš telefon je varno pritrjen v vašem vidnem polju.

Ščitnika za roke s smernikom dopolnjujeta agresiven videz motorja MT-10, zato sta nujen dodatek, ki zagotavlja popolno ravnovesje med slogom, zaščito, udobjem in funkcionalnostjo.

name.sl-SI: Kratka majica Paddock Blue Essentials za ženske

description.en: Simple and striking, the Paddock Blue Essentials Women’s T-Shirt is an essential item for every Yamaha fan’s wardrobe. Made from 100% cotton for a soft feel, this tee’s relaxed fit and V-neck ensure a comfy fit for all wearers. Printed Yamaha chest and arm branding complete a classic racing blue Yamaha look.
description.sl-SI: Preprosta in očarljiva kratka majica Paddock Blue Essentials za ženske je nepogrešljiv kos v garderobi vsake ljubiteljice Yamahe. Izdelana je iz 100-odstotnega bombaža za mehek občutek, ohlapen kroj majice in V-izrez pa zagotavljata udobno prileganje vsem uporabnicam. Natisnjena Yamahina logotipa na prsih in rokavu izpopolnjujeta klasični Yamahin dirkaški videz v modrem.

description.en: Light weight Sporty license plate holder to replace the original, to clean up the looks of your XSR to a more sportive finish.
description.sl-SI: Lahek športen nosilec registrske tablice za zamenjavo originala za bolj športen končni videz modela XSR.

Opremite svoje motorno kolo TRACER 7 s kompletom 'Urban Pack' za vrhunsko mestno udobje. Nosilec zgornjega kovčka in zgornji kovček zagotavljata dovolj prostora za shranjevanje, medtem ko naslonjalo za potnika poskrbi za udobje. S kompletom 'Urban Pack', ki je dopolnjen z visokim vizirjem za dodatno zaščito pred vetrom, nadgradite mestno vožnjo s praktičnostjo in slogom.
description.en: Equip your TRACER 7 with the Urban Pack for ultimate city convenience. The Top Case Carrier and Top Case provide ample storage, while the Backrest adds comfort for your passenger. Completed with a High Screen for added wind protection, the Urban Pack enhances your urban ride with practicality and style.
GYTR Pinion gear for GYTR Gear box

Built to feel sporty with comfort in mind, the TMAX cap for adults has contemporary design right through its construction. Made in 100% organic cotton that ensures soft comfort, the cap features an adjustable strap, air flow holes and an inner sweatband for easy wear wherever you are. A 3D TMAX logo on the front is highlighted with Yamaha branding on the peak. A colour contrast sandwich peak gives the finishing touch to a subtly stunning cap.
description.sl-SI: Izdelana za udobno nošenje: kapa TMAX za odrasle je sodoben izdelek za sodobne uporabnike. Izdelana je iz 100 % ekološko pridelanega bombaža, ki zagotavlja mehkobo pri uporabi, poleg tega ima nastavljiv trak, odprtine za pretok zraka in notranji trak, ki vpija znoj, za prijetno nošenje, ne glede na to kje se nahajate. 3D-logotip TMAX na sprednji strani je dopolnjen z Yamahinim logotipom na ščitniku. Ščitnik z obrobo v kontrastni barvi pa zaokroži celotno podobo te zanimive kape.

Z univerzalnim ovitkom za telefon lahko uporabite vsak pametni telefon (največja velikost telefona je navedena spodaj) na kateri koli SP Connect™.  Namestite, da bi lahko z vrtljivim zaklepnim mehanizmom svoj telefon varno pritrdili na kolo, v avtomobil, na vozilo za golf itd. Preprosto potisnite pametni telefon v ovitek, zavihajte odprtino in zaprite zavihek. Tako bo vaš telefon zaščiten pred dežjem, znojem, blatom in prahom, uporabnost zaslona na dozik pa ostane enaka.
description.en: With the Universal phone case, you can use just about any smartphone (max phone size indicated) on any of the mounts to secure your phone to your motorcycle or scooter. With its twist-lock mechanism to install. Simply push the smartphone into the case and roll up the opening and close the tab. This way your phone remains protected from rain, sweat, mud, and dust, still offering the same touchscreen usability.​

name.sl-SI: Športna kapa Paddock Blue za odrasle

description.en: Simple and stylish, the Paddock Blue Team Cap is a classic addition to every Yamaha fan’s collection. Made from 100% cotton, the cap is one size fits all and presented in racing blue with a colour contrast peak. Breathing holes allow ventilation, with an adjustable strap for comfort. Printed Yamaha branding on the front and sides ensures an iconic style.
description.sl-SI: Preprosto in stilsko športno kapo Paddock Blue si lahko nadene prav vsak navdušenec za klasičen dodatek Yamahini kolekciji. Izdelana je iz 100-odstotnega bombaža, na voljo je v univerzalni velikosti in je obarvana v dirkaško modro s kontrastno barvo na vrhu. Odprtine omogočajo zračenje, nastavljiv trak pa udobje. Natisnjeni Yamahini logotipi spredaj in na strani zagotavljajo ikonski slog.

Kapa za odrasle Jonathan Rea je nepogrešljiva za sončne dni dirkanja in je obvezna oprema za ljubitelje šestkratnega prvaka. 100-odstotni bombaž v modri barvi Paddock Blue, kapa unisex z ukrivljenim črnim vrhom, mrežastim zadnjim delom, nastavljivim trakom in prezračevalnimi odprtinami za celodnevno udobje.  Videz dopolnjujeta izvezena napisa "65" na sprednji strani in "JR" na zadnji strani. Natisnjeni logotipi Yamaha zaključujejo podrobnosti, ki jih v svoji zbirki potrebuje vsak Jonnyjev navijač!
description.en: Essential for sunny race days, the Jonathan Rea Adults Cap is a must-have accessory for fans of the 6-time Champion. 100% cotton in Paddock Blue, the unisex cap features a curved black peak, mesh back, adjustable strap and ventilation holes for day-long comfort.  The look is completed with an embroidered ‘65’ on the front and ‘JR’ on the back. Printed Yamaha logos on finish off the detailing that every Jonny fan needs in their collection!

description.sl-SI: Izboljšajte svoj TRACER 7 s športnim paketom. Zaporedni smerniki LED izboljšajo vidljivost in slog, sistem za hitro prestavljanje CP2 pa zagotavlja gladko in hitro menjavo prestav. Dopolnite videz s poenostavljenim nosilcem registrske tablice.
description.en: Elevate your TRACER 7 with the Sport Pack. Sequential LED Blinkers enhance visibility and style, while the Quick Shifter CP2 ensures smooth, fast gear changes. Complete the look with the streamlined License Plate Holder.

Here’s a great solution for those dirty parts on anything from a motorcycle, an outboard, an ATV or a snowmobile. Yamalube Parts Cleaner is a very potent, multi-purpose cleaner and degreaser for all metal parts and components, and most plastics too.
description.sl-SI: Predstavljamo odlično rešitev za umazane dele motornega kolesa, izvenkrmnega motorja, ATV-ja ali celo motornih sani. Čistilo za čiščenje delov Yamalube je močno, večnamensko čistilno in razmaščevalno sredstvo za vse kovinske dele in komponente ter tudi za večino plastičnih delov.

The WaveRunner Storage Pack mounts with a self-adhesive hook-and-loop fastener above the floor in a storage compartment so it won't be submersed if any water inadvertently gets in the compartment. Easy to remove when you get back to shore. Fits all WaveRunner models.
description.sl-SI: Torba za shranjevanje za WaveRunner se pritrdi na ježka nad tlemi v prostoru za shranjevanje, zato se ne potopi, če v prostor vstopi voda. Ko se vrnete na obalo, jo lahko preprosto odstranite. Primerna za vse modele vodnih skuterjev WaveRunner.
Zadnji blažilnik izboljšuje vodljivost, stabilnost in zavijanje, da bo vaša vožnja še boljša in samozavestnejša.

description.en: Ride in comfort and safety with these triple-layered textile pants. Featuring removable waterproof and winter linings and a fixed mesh lining, the Tara pants are breathable in all weather conditions with ventilation in the pockets and leg sides. Reinforced panels on the front and inside leg offer extra protection while adjustable legs give comfort to riders of all heights. Pair with the Adventure jacket using the full-length waist zip.
description.sl-SI: Troslojne hlače iz blaga vam zagotavljajo udobno in varno vožnjo. Hlače Tara imajo snemljivo vodoodporno in zimsko podlogo ter fiksno mrežasto podlogo, hkrati pa dihajo v vseh vremenskih razmerah ter v žepih in na stranskem delu nog zagotavljajo zračenje. Ojačane plošče na sprednjem in notranjem delu nog zagotavljajo dodatno zaščito, hlače pa so prilagodljive, zato voznikom vseh velikosti zagotavljajo udobje. Z zadrgo za pas za celotno dolžino jih lahko kombinirate s pustolovsko jakno.

Vodoodporne in izolirane ženske motoristične rokavice Sport Touring so idealne za vožnjo v hladnem vremenu. Tribarvne rokavice so izdelane iz mešanice kozjega usnja in funkcionalnih materialov, varnost in toploto pa zagotavljata zaščita členkov in izolacija Primaloft. Neoprenski zavihki in deli za prste poskrbijo za odlično prožnost, udobje zapestja v vseh položajih pa omogoča prilagodljivo zapenjanje z ježkom. Za popolno potovalno opravo jih kombinirajte s športno-potovalno motoristično jakno in hlačami.
description.en: Waterproof and insulated, the Sport Touring Women’s Riding Gloves are ideal for cold weather riding. Made from a blend of goat leather and technical materials, the three-tone gloves feature shell knuckle protection and Primaloft insulation for safety and warmth. Neoprene cuffs and finger parts allow excellent flexibility, with Velcro wrist adjustment for changeable comfort. Pair with the Sport Touring Riding Jacket and Pants for the essential touring outfit.

description.en: Yamaha‘s WaveRunner covers are designed to help protect your watercraft‘s appearance. Each cover features superior construction and materials to help provide long life as well as a custom fit. Features include Vacu-Hold® design, which creates a vacuum inside the cover during transit to draw the cover down snugly to the WaveRunner. Benefits include reduced air-induced stress on the seams, and less aerodynamic drag.
description.sl-SI: Yamahine prevleke za WaveRunner so namenjene za zaščito videza vašega plovila. Vsaka prevleka je natančno zasnovana in izdelana iz materialov, ki zagotavljajo dolgotrajno uporabo in popolno prileganje. Lastnosti prevleke vključujejo tehnologijo VACU-Hold®, ki znotraj prevleke med transportom ustvarja vakuum, da se prevleka lahko tesno prilega WaveRunnerju. Prednosti vključujejo zmanjšano obrabo šivov zaradi ujetega zraka in manjši aerodinamični upor.

description.sl-SI: Stopite na ulico modni z bombažno kapo za odrasle kolekcije Hyper Naked, sešito iz petih petin. Kapa, ki je zasnovana za vse pripadnike temne plati, je univerzalne velikosti ter ima nastavljivo kovinsko sponko, mrežasto hrbtno stran in prezračevalne luknjice za optimalno udobje. Vezeni logotipi Yamaha, MT in DSOJ so subtilni, a vpadljivi in dodajo kanček barve, ki pritegne pozornost, kamor koli vas pot popelje.

Made for every dark side fan, the cap is one-size-fits-all and features an adjustable metal clip, mesh back and ventilation holes for optimum comfort. Predstavljamo naše ekskluzivne ščitnike za roke, ki so skrbno izdelani z mislijo na dinamičnega kolesarja. Ti ščitniki so zasnovani za najbolj aktivne navdušence in se ponašajo z ergonomsko zasnovo, ki zagotavlja popolno prileganje. Ne le da zagotavljajo optimalno zaščito pred vetrom, temveč njihov stil zaprte zanke zagotavlja tudi izboljšano zaščito in vzdržljivost pred drobci. description.en:
Introducing our exclusive handguards, meticulously crafted with the dynamic rider in focus. Engineered for the most active enthusiasts, these handguards boast ergonomic design to ensure a perfect fit. Not only do they provide optimal wind protection, but their closed loop style also delivers enhanced safeguarding and durability against debris. Elevate your riding experience with the perfect blend of style and functionality

Komplet platformnih pedalov VICE, ki jih po Yamahinih specifikacijah izdeluje podjetje VP Components, omogoča boljši prenos moči ter večji razpon položajev stopal in telesa za izboljšano stabilnost, kakor tudi večjo zmogljivost pri spuščanju po hribih ali vožnji po stezah. Ti pedali s plosko površino, ki imajo na vsaki strani 12 zatičev za oprijem, omogočajo, da kar najbolje izkoristite model Moro 07. Komplet platformnih pedalov VICE zagotavlja večjo zmogljivost in odlično vzdržljivost, saj ima trpežno aluminijasto ohišje, izdelano s strojem CNC, ter zatesnjene kroglične ležaje in ležaje LSL.
description.en: Manufactured to Yamaha’s specification by VP components, the VICE platform pedal set gives you better power transfer and a greater range of foot and body positions for enhanced stability and stronger performance on the downhill or trail. With a flat surface equipped with 12 replaceable grip pins per side, these pedals enable you to get the most out of your Moro 07. Featuring a durable extruded and CNC machined aluminum body with LSL and sealed ball bearings, the VICE platform pedal set provides increased performance with superb durability.

An adjustable plastic strap, ventilation holes and sweatband offer comfort in all climates.

name.en: Öhlins Cartridge Kit Race - NIX 22 USD
name.sl-SI: Komplet vložkov za dirkanje Öhlins – NIX 22 USD

description.en: The Öhlins NIX 22 USD cartridge kit comes directly from experience gained in the World Supersport 300 championship. It doesn’t matter if you are heading for a World Championship title or if you are taking your bike to the local race track. This cartridge kit will give you loads of performance, stable damping characteristics and fantastic comfort. The kit has a unique NIX design with compression damping and pre-load adjustment on the left leg, rebound damping and pre-load adjustment on the right leg, while all adjustments are easily made at the top cap.
description.sl-SI: Komplet vložkov Öhlins NIX 22 USD je neposreden odraz izkušenj, pridobljenih na prvenstvu World Supersport 300. Ni pomembno, ali se borite za naslov svetovnega prvaka ali pa s kolesom dirkate na lokalnem dirkališču. Ta komplet vložkov vam zagotavlja boljše zmogljivosti, zanesljivo blaženje in izredno udobje. Komplet ima edinstveno zasnovo NIX s kompresijskim blaženjem in nastavljivo predobremenitvijo za levo nogo ter povratnim blaženjem in nastavljivo predobremenitvijo za desno nogo, vse nastavitve pa lahko enostavno prilagajate na zgornjem pokrovčku.

description.sl-SI: Če pogrešate 80-a leta, je 'Racer Pack' popolna rešitev za to! Čistilo za zavore Yamalube® je idealno za čiščenje in razmaščevanje zavor in komponent sklopke ter drugih delov. Posebna formula, ki ni jedka, hitro raztopi olje, mast, katran, zavorno tekočino ter umazanijo in je varna za uporabo na gumi, plastiki in barvi.
description.en: Yamalube® Brake Cleaner is ideal for degreasing and cleaning brake, clutch and other components. Its non-corrosive formula rapidly dissolves oil, grease, tar, brake fluid and dirt and is safe to use on rubber, plastic and paint.

Rain and wind shouldn't stop you from activities, and neither should they affect your riding pleasure and comfort. We developed the Apron, which uses special welding technology, to keep you warm and dry, so you can be more comfortable and safe during harsh weather conditions.
description.sl-SI: Dež in veter ne bi smela biti ovira pri aktivnostih, prav tako pa ne bi smela vplivati na vaš užitek in udobje pri vožnji. Razvili smo zaščito za sprednji del telesa, ki uporablja posebno tehnologijo varjenja, ki vas ščiti pred mrazom in dežjem, da vam bo tudi v težjih vremenskih pogojih udobno in boste ostali varni.

name.sl-SI: Komplet Sport Pack Pro za MT-07

description.sl-SI: Za voznike, ki želijo maksimalno izkoristiti svoje motorno kolo MT-07, smo pripravili komplet Sport Pack Pro. Poleg vseh prednosti, ki jih ponuja komplet Sport Pack, Sport Pack Pro vključuje še nekaj pozorno izbranih dodatkov iz naše ponudbe. Celoten izpušni sistem Akrapovič zagotavlja večje zmogljivosti in vrhunsko izkušnjo zvoka, za izjemno upravljanje pa je dodano še zadnje vzmetenje Öhlins. Skupaj s hitrim menjalnikom, stranskim oblazinjenjem rezervoarja, nosilcem registrske tablice in zaporednimi smerniki, ta paket popelje vašo vožnjo na vrhunsko raven in daje vašemu MT-07 značilen športni videz.
description.en: For riders who want the maximum out of their MT-07, we put together the Sport Pack Pro. Along with all the goodies that the Sport Pack has to offer, the Sport Pack Pro adds in a few more carefully selected accessories from our range. The full system Akrapovič exhaust provides increased performance and a visceral sound experience, whereas the Öhlins rear suspension has been added for superior handling. Together with the quickshifter, side tank pads, licence plate holder and sequential blinkers, this pack takes your ride to the ultimate level and gives your MT-07 a distinctive sporty look.

The Sport Pack adds a touch of sportiness with its mix of accessories. The fly screen gives the front an unmistakably understated yet strong look, while the LED lights (front and rear) add to the equation. The sleek license plate holder sharpens up the rear. Finally, the side tank pad set not only protects the tank from scratches, but also gives that extra grip when you are setting the corners on fire! Are you ready to take the roads by storm?

Vizir daje sprednjemu delu komaj opazen in razpoznaven, vendar hkrati močan videz, za kar še dodatno poskrbijo LED-žarometi (sprednji in zadnji). Vitek nosilec registrske tablice poskrbi za izrazitejši videz zadnjega dela. Stranska zaščita za rezervoar varuje rezervoar pred praskami, poleg tega pa nudi dodaten oprijem pri premagovanju ovinkov! description.en: Designed for competitive riders who want to progress quickly through the ranks and make a name for themselves. This state-of-the-art kit comes with everything you need to upgrade your bike into a ready-to-race unit with improved performance.
description.sl-SI: Zasnovan za tekmovalce, ki bi radi po lestvici z uvrstitvami hitro napredovali navzgor ter si ustvarili ime. Ta najmodernejši komplet ima vse, kar potrebujete za nadgradnjo motocikla v dirkaško enoto z boljšo zmogljivostjo.

Otroške hlače MX, ki so nepogrešljiv kos oblačila za mlajše voznike, so tehnične, zelo funkcionalne in zaščitne. Izdelane so iz poliestra in kozjega usnja, njihova zunanja površina pa zagotavlja odlično zaščito, ne da bi omejevala gibanja nog. Na sedežnem delu, kolenih in v pasu so raztegljive za svobodnejše gibanje. Mreža na spodnjem delu omogoča zračenje, ko je čas za akcijo, kozje usnje na notranjem delu kolen pa odpornost na toploto in dober oprijem. Prilagodljiv in oprijemljiv pas zagotavlja varno prileganje.
description.en: Essential for junior riders, the MX Kid’s Pants are technical, highly functional and protective. A mix of polyester and goat leather on the outer pants offers excellent protection without compromising leg movement, with stretch fabric on the seat, knees and waist for extra movement. Ventilated mesh on the lower legs allows breathability in the heat of action, while the goat leather inner knees offer heat resistance and grip. An adjustable and grippy waistband ensures a secure fit.

description.en: Design for ATV, enduro and dirt riding conditions, Yamaha's Off Road riding set is manufactured from 100% ripstop material for added durability. The jacket features removable sleeves, 2 waterproof inner pockets and 5 front pockets. The ventilated jacket offers excellent flexibility and carrying capacity. The pants feature 2 cargo pockets, with a zip and Velcro adjustment.
description.sl-SI: Yamahin komplet Off Road je zasnovan za vožnjo z ATV, enduro ali po blatu in je narejen iz 100-odstotnega materiala, ki preprečuje trganje, za boljšo trpežnost. Jakna ima snemljive rokave, 2 vodotesna notranja žepa in 5 sprednjih žepov. Prezračevana jakna omogoča odlično prilagodljivost in nosilnost. Hlače imajo 2 velika žepa z zadrgo ter ježkom za prilagoditev velikosti.

Nadgradite motorno kolo TRACER 9 GT+ s potovalnim kompletom 'Travel Pack', ki prinaša udobje in priročnost. Visok vizir ponuja odlično zaščito pred vetrom, medtem ko zgornji kovček z naslonjalom zagotavlja dovolj prostora za shranjevanje in udobje za dolge vožnje. Ta komplet je kot nalašč za vsako potovanje, saj združuje praktičnost in slog.
description.en: Enhance your TRACER 9 GT+ with the Travel Pack, designed for comfort and convenience. The High Screen offers excellent wind protection, while the Top Case with Backrest provides ample storage and comfort for long rides. Perfect for every journey, this pack combines practicality with style.

Choose from our new large range of towables to have fun with family and friends on your next trip on the water! This 1 person wing tube was made with 420 denier nylon cover and 20 gauge PVC, for optimal durability.
description.sl-SI: Izberite iz naše nove široke ponudbe vlečnih tub ter uživajte z družino in prijatelji na svoji naslednji dogodivščini na vodi! Ta vodna tuba z zavihki za 1 osebo ima vrhnjo plast iz najlona s 420 denom in PVC-jem, debeline 0,81 mm, za optimalno trpežnost.

description.en: Helps tune up the injection and ignition system for even greater power

description.en: You can intensify the sporty spirit of your XMAX with the Sport Pack consisting of a sport screen, license plate holder, aluminium adjustable levers and aluminium foot panels – the perfect combination of sport style and flair. Make it truly yours by adding optional Gilles , Akrapovič and Ohlin’s parts. Available from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your XMAX.
description.sl-SI: Športni duh vašega vozila XMAX lahko okrepite s športnim paketom, ki vključuje športni vizir, nosilec registrske tablice, aluminijaste prilagodljive ročice in aluminijaste plošče stopalk – popolna kombinacija športnega sloga in elegance. Svojemu vozilu dodajte dele družb Gilles, Akrapovič in Ohlin ter ga tako povsem prilagodite svojemu okusu. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaše vozilo XMAX.
Kakovosten zadnji nosilec za 39-litrski in 50-litrski zgornji kovček iz aluminija.
description.en: High-quality rear carrier for 39L and 50L top case made of finished aluminium.

Engineered for optimum comfort on trials, the MTB Men’s Gloves offer both flexibility and protection. A stretchy single layer spandex upper is combined with a synthetic suede palm for grip and control, with perforations for ventilation in changeable conditions. An essential item for committed mountain bikers.
description.sl-SI: Moške rokavice MTB, zasnovane za največje udobje na zahtevnem terenu, omogočajo fleksibilnost in zaščito. Raztegljiv sloj iz elastana na zgornji strani je združen s slojem iz sintetičnega semiša na delu dlani za oprijem in nadzor, poleg tega rokavice vključujejo odprtine za zračenje v spremenljivih razmerah. Nepogrešljiv izdelek za zagrete gorske kolesarje.
Z zgornjimi nosilci stranskih kovčkov optimizirajte prtljago za TRACER 9 in uživajte v vožnji. Enostaven plavajoči sistem za optimalno dinamiko vožnje.
description.en: Optimise your TRACER 9 packing and enjoy the ride with the Upper Side Case Stays. An easy-fit, floating system for optimum riding dynamics.
Beautiful two tone anodized footrests for optimal sportivity.
description.sl-SI: Čudovite dvobarvne anodizirane stopalke za optimalen športni učinek

description.en: Highly increase your riding comfort.
description.sl-SI: Izredno izboljša udobje pri vožnji.

description.en: Perfect for discreetly carrying essential items around track or town, the Paddock Blue Crossbody Bag offers 3 litres of compact storage. Created from a mix of polyester and nylon in blue, its ripstop pattern allows lightweight strength while the single outer pocket features a zip with an additional removable keyring for extra utility.
description.sl-SI: Perfect for discreetly carrying essential items around track or town, the Paddock Blue Crossbody Bag offers 3 litres of compact storage. Created from a mix of polyester and nylon in blue, its ripstop pattern allows lightweight strength while the single outer pocket features a zip with an additional removable keyring for extra utility.

name.sl-SI: Stekleno zadnje okno kompleta za zapiranje kabine v trdi izvedbi

description.en: Yamaha is offering all the components of the Hard Cab Enclosure System separately for added customer convenience. Accessing the cargo area is one of the key factors in the fully functional Wolverine X4. This glass rear window opens utilizing familiar gas struts like those of a SUV to hold the glass up while the window is open (window must be closed while in drive).The fully lockable window keeps your items secure from unwanted company. When paired with the Rear Cargo Box to maximize rear cargo space, you have a truly versatile package ready to conquer the outdoors!
description.sl-SI: Yamaha za lažjo uporabo vse sestavne dele kompleta za zapiranje kabine v trdi izvedbi ponuja ločeno. Ena ključnih značilnosti polnofunkcionalnega modela Wolverine X4 je dostop do prtljažnega prostora. To stekleno zadnje okno se odpre s pomočjo že poznanih plinskih vzmeti, kot so tiste pri športnih terencih, ki zadržijo steklo v zgornjem položaju, ko je okno odprto (med vožnjo mora biti okno zaprto). Ker se da okno v celoti zakleniti, so vaši predmeti varni pred nepridipravi. Če uporabljate zadnji tovorni kovček, ki poveča prtljažni prostor zadaj, je vaš vsestranski paket opreme pripravljen na dogodivščine na prostem!

Stranska ogledala, ki jih je zasnovala, razvila in preizkusila Yamaha, zagotavljajo odličen pogled in najboljšo vzdržljivost. Širokokotno stekleno območje za pogled brez popačenja zagotavlja veliko jasnost in vidnost zadaj. Zlaganje v avtomobilskem slogu zagotavlja dodatno udobje pri vleki zaprtih prikolic ali na tesnih poteh, saj po ponovnem odpiranju ogledal ni treba znova prilagajati vidnega polja. Izjemno trpežne tlačno lite aluminijaste osi zagotavljajo trpežnost, ki jo pričakujete od Yamahe.
description.en: The Yamaha-designed, developed, and tested Side View Mirrors provide an excellent view and unmatched durability. The wide-angle, distortion-free glass viewing area provides great clarity and rearward visibility. Automotive-style fold-away action provides added convenience when pulling in enclosed trailers or on tight trails by reducing the need to readjust the viewing area after folding back. Ultra-tough die-cast aluminum pivots provide the durability you come to expect from Yamaha.

Our FusionFit™ Bed Attachment Kit will help keep your tools always at-the-ready. Yamaha's FusionFit™ accessory system provides a tool-less design that allows you to "click and go" with only a quarter turn. An integrated padlock slot gives you the option to easily secure your cargo and go

The Paddock Blue hybrid jacket is made of a durable and light polyester fabric. And its special seamless tunneling and soft padding make this the perfect jacket to keep you warm in colder weather conditions. The jacket has two black upper panels, white Yamaha Racing logos on chest and sleeve and also features various black and white design elements
description.sl-SI: Hibridna jakna Paddock Blue je izdelana iz trpežne in lahke tkanine iz poliestra. Njena posebna brezšivna zasnova in mehka podloga skrbita, da je ta jakna popolna za gretje v hladnem vremenu. But they are also in itself a great front end upgrade and option to improve responsiveness and performance of the fork. Öhlins offers a wide range of linear springs to suit each individual type of bike, rider weight and personal preferences for installation into the standard front fork.

Poleg tega poskrbijo tudi za odlično nadgradnjo sprednjega dela ter možnost za izboljšanje odzivnosti in zmogljivosti vilice. Öhlins zagotavlja širok nabor linearnih vzmeti, ki so primerne za vsako posamezno vrsto motornega kolesa, težo voznika in osebne želje za namestitev v standardne sprednje vilice.

description.sl-SI: Popolnoma sintetično olje Yamalube® 0W-30 za 4-taktne snežne sani je vrhunsko mazivo za vožnjo po snegu in poteh pri nizkih temperaturah. Njegova popolnoma sintetična formula je zasnovana za ekstremne razmere in ščiti dele motorja v vremenskih razmerah pod ničlo.
description.en: Yamalube® Fully Synthetic 0W-30 4-Stroke Snowmobile Oil is the ultimate lubricant for low temperature snow and trail riding. Its fully-synthetic formula is designed to handle extreme conditions, protecting engine parts in sub-zero climates.

description.en: Durable, stylish and easy to handle, the Paddock Blue Race Trolley is perfect for trips to race tracks around the world and everywhere in between. A tough 100% polyester outer in iconic Racing Blue is branded with the Yamaha Racing logo, with 123 litres of storage ideal for long-haul travel. A telescopic pull handle and wheels make for easy use, with top and side handles for carrying. Adjustable straps and buckles allow you to accommodate for storage.
Optional OEM footpeg for a more sporty feel and appearance.

name.en: MOVE LIVE LOVE T-Shirt Unisex Adult

description.sl-SI: Začutite pridih urbane mobilnosti Yamaha z majico s kratkimi rokavi za odrasle (uniseks) s potiskom motiva MOVE LIVE LOVE. Temno siva majica s kratkimi rokavi ima živahno barvito grafiko, ki se ujema z Yamahino serijo skuterjev. Izdelana je iz mešanice bombaža in elastana, zato omogoča maksimalno udobje in gibljivost pri vsakodnevni uporabi. Motiv MOVE LIVE LOVE je dopolnjen z zunanjim slojem iz tkanine z encimi za retro-vintage učinek.
description.en: Capture the Yamaha Urban Mobility spirit with the MOVE LIVE LOVE Unisex Adult’s T-Shirt. Dark grey with a bright, colourful printed aligned with the Yamaha scooter range, this tee’s cotton and elastane blend offers maximum comfort and movement for everyday wear. The MOVE LIVE LOVE print is complimented with an enzyme wash finish for a retro-vintage flourish.

description.sl-SI: Standardni 45-litrski zgornji kovček brez barvnih ploščic
description.en: Standard Top Case 45L without colour plates.

Convert your XSR900 to a ideal long-trip Roadster with the Weekend Pack. Fitting your bike with two 13,5 litre soft bags holding up to 5 kilograms each will allow you to pack your traveling essentials and go the extra mile. Easily fitting the bags with waterproof liners will protect your luggage from unfortunate weather conditions. The pack comes with an USB charger to charge your navigation or phone during the trip.
description.sl-SI: S kompletom 'Weekend Pack' pretvorite svoj XSR900 v popolno cestno motorno vozilo za dolga potovanja. Če na motorno kolo namestite dve 13,5-litrski mehki torbi z največjo obremenitvijo 5 kilogramov, boste lahko spakirali osnovne stvari za potovanja in se zapeljali še dlje. Z enostavno namestitvijo vodoodpornih oblog zaščitite svojo prtljago v slabih vremenskih razmerah. V kompletu je na voljo tudi polnilnik USB, s katerim boste med potovanjem lahko polnili navigacijski sistem ali telefon.

Z Akrapovičevim popolnim izpušnim sistemom v črni barvi zagotovite svojemu modelu Yamaha TMAX izboljšano zmogljivost, zvok in slog. Cevi iz nerjavečega jekla se povežejo s črnim titanovim dušilcem zvoka z lasersko vgraviranim logotipom TMAX za eleganten dodatek.
description.en: Give your Yamaha TMAX a boost of performance, sound and style with the Akrapovič Full System - Black. The stainless steel header pipes connect to the black-finished titanium muffler, with a laser engraved TMAX logo for a stylish addition.
Ohlins rear shock YA570 S46DR1  for MT09/XSR900
description.sl-SI: Zadnji blažilnik Ohlins YA570 S46DR1 za MT09/XSR900

description.en: Designed for comfort and speed, the REVS jog pants for men are both stylish and highly wearable. Made in black from a cotton and polyester blend, they feature two bonded front pockets and a single rear pocket. Red detailing stripes on each leg and a left thigh Yamaha logo highlight its REVS heritage. Tapered legs create a tight fit ideal for exercise, with self-fabric hems keeping their shape.
description.sl-SI: Moške tekaške hlače REVS so zasnovane za udobje in hitrost, zato so hkrati elegantne in funkcionalne. Izdelane so v črni barvi iz mešanice bombaža in poliestra, imajo dva varjena sprednja žepa in en žep na zadnji strani. Detajl z rdečimi črtami na vsaki hlačnici in Yamahin logotip na levem stegnu poudarjajo zasnovo linije REVS. Zoženi hlačnici poskrbita za prileganje, idealno za vadbo, obrobi iz enake tkanine pa pripomoreta k ohranjanju oblike.

description.en: Fast and gentle cleaning for a sparkling clean result. The QUICK CLEANER does not require any additional water! Excellent for plastics, glass, paint, metals, windshields and visors. With the 360° spray system, the QUICK CLEANER can be used in all positions. Mode of use: Spray "YAMALUBE QUICK CLEANER" on a clean dry wipe and wipe the motorcycle/ATV/Outboard engine with it. Caution: Do not rub the motorcycle/ATV/Outboard engine with hard dirt particles.
description.sl-SI: Hitro in nežno čiščenje za bleščečo čistočo. Pri čiščenju s HITRIM ČISTILOM ne potrebujete dodatne vode! Odlično za plastiko, steklo, barvo, kovine, vetrobranska stekla in vizirje. S sistemom pršenja za 360° lahko HITRO ČISTILO uporabljate v vseh položajih. Način uporabe: Razpršite HITRO ČISTILO YAMALUBE na čisto suho krpo in z njo obrišite motorno kolo/ATV/izvenkrmni motor. Pozor: Motornega kolesa/ATV-ja/izvenkrmnega motorja ne drgnite s trdimi delci umazanije.

name.en: Storage cover for the EX series
name.sl-SI: Prevleka za shranjevanje za serijo EX

description.en: Keep your investment looking its best, and protect it from the elements. This cover provides the ultimate protection against fading and the elements. It comes with the Vacu-Hold strapless tow system, eliminating billowing and buffeting. Therefore, the cover conforms to the shape of your WaveRunner.
description.sl-SI: Ohranite svojo naložbo v najboljšem stanju in jo zaščitit pred vremenskimi vplivi. Ta prevleka zagotavlja neprekosljivo zaščito pred bledenjem in posledicami vremenskih dejavnikov. Ima sistem Vacu-Hold za pripenjanje brez trakov, ki odpravlja napihovanje in plapolanje prevleke. Zato se popolnoma prilega obliki vašega WaveRunnerja.

name.sl-SI: Kovinski zadnji pokrov agregata v dveh barvnih odtenkih

description.en: Cover to replace the original engine cover for an extra stylish look.
description.sl-SI: Pokrov, ki nadomešča originalni pokrov agregata, za bolj eleganten videz.
Za tople roke med vožnjo v mrzlem vremenu izberite grelce ročk. Ta par električno ogrevanih ročk nadomešča standardne ročke Yamaha TMAX za ogrevanje na zahtevo, skozi vse leto.
description.en: Choose the Grip Heater for warm hands in cold riding conditions. This pair of electrically heated hand grips replaces the standard Yamaha TMAX scooter grips for heat on demand, all year round.

description.sl-SI:
TRACER 9 GT 'Travel Pack Pro' je zasnovan za voznike, ki iščejo maksimalno udobje, varnost in funkcionalnost na dolgih razdaljah. Visok vizir v kombinaciji z dodatnim širokim zaščitnim vizirjem omogoča boljšo zaščito pred vetrom, ogrevan udoben sedež in sopotnikov udoben sedež pa vozniku in sopotniku prinašata toploto in sproščenost. Ohranite nadzor s kompletom za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah in sistemom za nadzor tlaka v pnevmatikah (TPMS) na krmilu, nosilec za GPS pa omogoča jasen pregled nad navigacijo. Zgornji kovček in naslon zagotavljata veliko prostora za shranjevanje in udobje sopotnika, s polnilnikom USB z vtičnico na nosilcu pa poskrbite, da so vaše naprave vedno napolnjene.

Za dodatno zaščito pred kamenčki na cesti se namestita ščitnik hladilnika in zaščita agregata 'Explorer', komplet meglenk LED z nosilcem za meglenke pa zagotavlja vidljivost v vseh pogojih. Ta paket je popoln spremljevalec za vsako pustolovščino na vašem TRACER 9 GT.
description.en:
The TRACER 9 GT Travel Pack Pro is built for riders seeking maximum comfort, safety, and functionality on long-distance rides. The High Screen, paired with the Add-On Wide Screen, enhances wind protection, while the Heated Comfort Seat and Passenger Comfort Seat ensure warmth and relaxation for both rider and passenger. Stay in control with the Tire Pressure Monitoring Kit and TPMS on the handlebar, while the GPS Stay keeps your navigation in clear view. The Top Case and Backrest provide ample storage and comfort for your passenger, and the USB Charger with Holder Socket ensures your devices remain powered.

For added protection, the Radiator Guard and Explorer Engine Guard shield your bike from road debris, and the LED Fog Light Kit with Fog Light Stay ensures visibility in all conditions. This pack  is the ultimate companion for every adventure on your TRACER 9 GT.
