description.en: Comfortable for the summer yet uncompromising in its protection, the blue Faster Sons denim riding shirt for men is a must-have for casual road trips. Fully CE-certified and equipped with DuPont™ Kevlar on the shoulders, with additional elbow protection, this body-fitted shirt offers all the comfort and style a rider could want from safe riding gear. A front zip closure is secured with press studs, with two outer and two inner pockets for valuables. Subtle Yamaha branding on the chest and a Faster Sons logo arm patch finish off a super stylish look that belongs to the road.
description.sl-SI: Udobna za poletje, vendar brezkompromisna v zaščiti. Modra srajca Faster Sons iz džinsa za moške je idealna izbira za priložnostne vožnje. Ima certifikat CE in je na ramenih okrepljena s kevlarjem z DuPont™ ter z dodatno zaščito komolcev. Ta telirana srajca ponuja vse udobje in slog, ki bi si ga lahko voznik želel od opreme, varne za vožnjo. Sprednja zadrga je zavarovana še s pritiskači, dodana sta še dva zunanja in dva notranja žepa za shranjevanje pomembnih stvari. Diskreten Yamahin logotip na prsih in našitek z logotipom Faster Sons zaključita eleganten videz, idealen za cestno vožnjo.

description.en: Protectors placed on either side of the MT-125 to prevent accidental damage to the engine as much as possible.

name.sl-SI: Kovček na kolesih Paddock Blue za otroke

description.en: Perfect for holidays and trips long or short, the Paddock Blue Kids Ride-on Suitcase is a fun and quirky bag that little Yamaha fans will love. Featuring a special R1-inspired graphic, kids can ride their unique wheeled luggage and imagine being on two wheels. Offering a spacious 19 litres of space with a cool interior lining, a divider and straps make it easy for parents to help their kids pack while the shoulder strap doubles as a carrying strap. Easy movement is afforded by 360° front wheels. A must-have luggage item for kids that love to ride and travel.
description.sl-SI: Otroški kovček na kolesih Paddock Blue je zabaven in poseben kos prtljage, ki bo osvojil najmlajše Yamahine navdušence, ter je popolna izbira za počitnice in krajše ali daljše izlete. Na tem edinstvenem kovčku na kolesih, ki ga krasi grafika po vzoru modela R1, se otroci lahko vozijo in si predstavljajo, da so na dvokolesniku. Kovček ima prostornih 19 litrov s trendovsko notranjo podlogo, pregrado in pasove za lažje pakiranje, naramni trak pa se lahko uporabi tudi kot trak za nošenje. Sprednja 360-stopinjska kolesa omogočajo preprosto premikanje. To je obvezen kos prtljage za otroke, ki imajo radi vožnjo in potovanja.

Ventilation at the zipper and Cordura stretch fabric enhance movement, with two waterproof cargo pockets for essential items. A silicone strip on the rear improves grip in the saddle. A must-have for ATV riders looking to off-road in style.

Hlače so izdelane iz funkcionalne zunanje plasti iz mešanice poliestra, elastana in kozjega usnja, zato imajo vodoodporno membrano Drystar, ki se lahko popolnoma zloži, zaščito stopnje 1 na bokih in kolenih ter ojačana območja nog in sedalnega dela. Velika žepa omogočata shranjevanje nujnih potrebščin, prezračevalne zaplate na stegnih pa zagotavljajo učinkovito zračenje v vročem vremenu. Snemljive naramnice in ramenski pas pomagajo ohranjati hlače v položaju, medtem ko dolga zadrga za pas omogoča združitev z avanturistično motoristično jakno, za učinek vrhunske pustolovske oprave.
description.en: Essential for adventuring in all weathers, the stylish, dark-toned Adventure Men’s Riding Pants offer comfort, protection and durability wherever the adventure takes you. Made with a technical outer layer blend of polyester, elastane and goat leather, the pants feature a waterproof Drystar membrane that can be folded back on itself, level 1 hip and knee for protection, and reinforced leg and seat areas. Cargo pockets let you carry essential items, while thigh ventilation panels afford good breathability in hot weather. A detachable suspender and shoulder belt help keep the pants in position, while a long waist zip allows them to connect with the Adventure Riding Jacket for the ultimate adventure apparel outfit.

A unique formulation with a high wet boiling point (min 180ºC). So even in the most extreme driving conditions it will protect against vapour lock and help prevent brake or clutch failure. Suitable for all types of hydraulic brake and clutch systems.
description.sl-SI: Edinstvena formulacija z visoko točko mokrega vrelišča (vsaj 180º C). Torej bo tudi v najbolj ekstremnih razmerah varoval pred paro in preprečeval okvaro zavore ali sklopke. Primeren za vse vrste hidravličnih sistemov za zavore in sklopke.

description.en: Increases durability of clutch components

name.en: Steel Mesh Air Intake Covers MT-07

With its compact dimensions and the excellent fuel efficiency the NMAX thrives in the hustle and bustle of the urban environment. To ensure space and comfort, the Urban pack offers the best experience for riding in those built-up areas. The high screen provides robust protection against wind, while it remains resistant to scratches and impact damage thanks to its hard-coated polycarbonate design. The 39L top case offers all the extra space you need and rests on a beautiful piece of alloy rear carrier, with its integrated design and rigorous testing guaranteeing year-after-year security and peace of mind while riding. The lockset for the top case comes included in the pack, while the back rest provides the rear passenger with optimum comfort. The Urban pack will make the NMAX your best friend in the city. Available now from your Yamaha dealer who will be happy to fit these high quality Genuine Accessories to your NMAX.
description.sl-SI: S kompaktnimi dimenzijami in odličnim izkoristkom goriva je model NMAX popolna izbira za uporabo v vrvežu urbanega okolja. Paket Urban zagotavlja dovolj prostora in udobja, zato omogoča kar najboljšo vožnjo po gosto pozidanih območjih. Visok vizir zagotavlja zanesljivo zaščito pred vetrom, zaradi polikarbonatne zasnove s trdo prevleko pa je odporen tudi na praske in poškodbe ob trku. 39-litrski zgornji kovček poskrbi za dodaten prostor, nameščen pa je na čudovitem zadnjem nosilcu iz zlitine. Z integrirano zasnovo in po izvedbi izjemno strogih testov zagotavlja varnost in brezskrbnost med vožnjo. Komplet ključavnice za zgornji kovček je priložen, naslon sedeža pa potniku zadaj omogoča optimalno udobje. S paketom Urban bo model NMAX postal vaš najboljši prijatelj za vožnjo po mestu. Obrnite se na pooblaščenega prodajalca izdelkov Yamaha, ki bo to visokokakovostno originalno dodatno opremo z veseljem namestil na vaš model NMAX.

description.en: Give the next generation the ideal start to becoming a Yamaha fan with the REVS Baby Giftpack. Featuring a cotton-elastane blended pyjama top and shorts with ‘First Ride’ prints, the pyjama set is extremely soft for a comfortable sleep. A pair of cotton, polyester and elastane socks also offer warmth for a toddler’s feet.

description.sl-SI: Naša kolekcija WaveRunner 2018 je kombinacija visokotehnoloških materialov in moderne oblike, ki zagotavlja najboljše doživetje na vodi. Te vodne smuči so kot nalašč za zabavo na jezeru ali morju!

Evoke the soul of the Dark Side of Japan, with the Sport Pack for the MT-10. 
Created to give you a full on immersive experience with your MT-10, the Sport Pack will catch your attention, while the Genuine accessories give your bike the sharp look.
Akrapovič exhaust takes the already attractive exhaust note and turns into aural delight. Did we mention the clean looks, increase in performance and the reduction in weight? Well those can also be attributed to the exhaust!
description.sl-SI:
S kompletom Sport Pack za vozilo MT-10 prebudite temno plat Japonske. 
Komplet Sport Pack je bil ustvarjen za zagotavljanje popolne vozne izkušnje z vašim modelom MT-10 in bo pritegnil vašo pozornost, originalna dodatna oprema pa bo poskrbela za agresiven videz vozila.
Akrapovičev izpuh pa že tako prijeten zvok izpuha ponese na popolnoma novo raven. Ali smo omenili čiste linije, boljšo učinkovitost in manjšo težo? Tudi te značilnosti lahko pripišemo omenjenemu izpuhu.

description.en: Specially formulated to meet Yamaha’s own very high standards, this advanced oil features additives to guard against friction, wear, foam and corrosion. The result is consistent protection for the suspension and the delivery of safer and more precise handling.
description.sl-SI: Posebej izdelano čistilo, ki izpolnjuje lastne visoke standarde družbe Yamaha. Napredni aditivi z lastnostmi olja preprečujejo trenje, obrabo, penjenje in korozijo. Rezultat je dosledna zaščita za vzmetenje in zagotavljanje bolj varnega ter natančnega delovanja.

Trpežna, zračna in zelo funkcionalna zemeljsko rjava in modra moška jakna kolekcije ATV je kot nalašč za podvige na prostem in terensko vožnjo. Vodoodporna jakna, izdelana iz poliestrske tkanine ripstop Dynax, ima odstranljive rokave in prezračevanje v podlogi in na hrbtu za vrhunsko udobje v toplih ali hladnih podnebjih. Dva notranja in trije zunanji žepi ponujajo prostor za bistvene predmete, z nastavljivimi manšetami za večje udobje vožnje. Odsevni trak na hrbtni strani izboljša vidljivost za dodatno varnost in brezskrbnost na poteh.
description.en: Durable, ventilated and highly functional, the earth brown-blue ATV Men’s Riding Jacket is perfect for outdoor exploits and off-roading. Made from polyester ripstop Dynax fabric, the water-resistant jacket features removable sleeves and ventilation in the liner and on the back for superior comfort in warm or cold climates. Two inner and three outer pockets offer space for essential items, with adjustable cuffs for enhanced riding comfort. Reflective tape on the back improve visibility for extra safety and peace of mind on the trails.
Heavier flywheel. Helps to get power off the ground and keep your momentum up through corners and tricky sections, resulting in faster lap times and more race wins.
description.sl-SI: Težji vztrajnik. Pomaga izboljšati oprijem in ohranjati zagon skozi zavoje in težavne odseke, kar pomeni boljše čase kroga in več zmag na dirkah.
Zagotovite maksimalno zaščito svojega motornega kolesa Ténéré 700 z zaščitnimi cevmi Adventure. Varno se prilega okoli rezervoarja, radiatorja in ohišja za varnost na zahtevnih vožnjah.
description.en: Give your Ténéré 700 maximum protection with the Adventure Bars. Fits securely around the tank, radiator and body for safety on rugged rides.

description.en: The Adventure riding jacket and pants are available as a set and can zip together. The set is available in a version for men and women. Designed for long distance riding comfort with high level of protection. The set has removable thermal lining and fixed waterproof lining that give all-weather flexibility. The fabric is a mix of polyester, polyamide, polyurethane and nylon. The jacket has 6 exterior and 4 interior pockets. The pants have 2 cargo pockets. This Adventure set is built to handle the longest and toughest ride.

Zasnovan je za udobno vožnjo na dolgih razdaljah z visoko stopnjo zaščite. Komplet ima snemljivo toplo podlogo in fiksno vodoodporno podlogo, zaradi česar je primeren za vse vremenske razmere. Tkanina je mešanica poliestra, poliamida, poliuretana in najlona. Jakna ima 6 zunanjih in 4 notranje žepe. Hlače imajo 2 velika žepa. Ta komplet Adventure je ustvarjen za najdaljše in najzahtevnejše vožnje.

description.sl-SI: Paket TRACER 9 GT 'Travel Pack' vsebuje ustrezne dodatke, ki poskrbijo za večje udobje na dolgih vožnjah. Visok vizir še bolje ščiti pred vetrom in drugimi vplivi ter vozniku zagotavlja prijeten položaj. Udoben sedež poskrbi za večje udobje pri daljšem sedenju, zato je to dobra izbira za dolge vožnje. Zgornji kovček in vsi dodatki, potrebni za namestitev, zagotavljajo neverjeten 45-litrski dodatni prostor za shranjevanje, kamor lahko shranite dve integralni čeladi. Kovček lahko dodatno prilagodite tako, da se barvna plošča ujema z barvo modela TRACER 9 GT.
description.en: For added comfort during long distance Touring, the TRACER 9 GT Travel Pack provides your motorcycle with just the right extra touches. The High Screen deflects even more wind and elements to provide the rider a pleasant protected position. The Comfort Seat is there to increase the comfort of seating for a longer period of time, making it an excellent addition for longer rides. The Top Case and all accessories needed to mount it provide an incredible 45 L extra storage space that can house two full face helmets if needed. The case can also be detailed to perfection with a color plate to match the color of your TRACER 9 GT.
Radiator guard for Ténéré 700 World Raid GYTR

description.en: Black with subtle red and grey highlights, the REVS polo shirt for women is a sophisticated garment reflecting the REVS DNA. Its organic cotton and elastane construction creates a feminine silhouette, with a knitted two-colour collar and button closure emphasising REVS style. Seamless sleeves and hem add real comfort, with classic Yamaha chest branding and printed red stripes on the sleeve and back reflecting the neck line.
description.sl-SI: Črna s subtilnimi rdečimi in sivimi poudarki: ženska polo majica REVS je prefinjeno oblačilo, ki odraža bistvo linije REVS. Tkanina iz ekološko pridelanega bombaža in elastana je udobno krojena, dodana sta pleten dvobarvni ovratnik in gumbnica, ki poudarjata slog serije REVS. Brezšivni rokavi in obroba omogočajo občutek udobja, na sprednji strani je Yamahin logotip, na rokavih in hrbtu pa so natisnjene rdeče črte, ki se ujemajo z vratnim izrezom.

name.sl-SI: Moška majica s kratkimi rokavi Ténéré World Raid

description.en: The Ténéré World Raid is a cross continent event for those with a true sense of adventure. This special Ténéré World Raid T-Shirt is unmistakably connected to the Ténéré adventure spirit. A must have for the fearless adventurers!
description.sl-SI: Ténéré World Raid je dogodek, ki se odvija na več celinah, namenjen tistim z občutkom za avanture. Posebna majica s kratkimi rokavi Ténéré World Raid je jasno povezana s pustolovskim duhom Ténéré. Obvezna oprema za vse neustrašne pustolovce.

description.en: A must-have in extra racing safety, the MX Adult Body Armour is a technical and reassuring item for every racer. Built with protection and flexibility in mind, this upper armour covers the shoulders, elbows and back with impact-absorbing shells on top of a lightweight and breathable stretch undershirt. Adjustable all over for comfort, the armour fits perfectly with the MX Men’s Jersey to keep the racing look and heighten protection.
description.sl-SI: Ščitnik telesa MX za odrasle je nepogrešljiv tehnični in zanesljiv kos opreme za dodatno varnost na dirkah. Ščitnik za zgornji del telesa je izdelan z ozirom na zaščito in fleksibilnost ter pokriva ramena, komolce in hrbet. Opremljen je z drsniki, ki blažijo udarce, pod njimi pa je lahka in zračna spodnja majica. Ker je nastavljiv, omogoča vsestransko udobje, poleg tega se povsem prilega moškemu dresu MX, zaradi česar lahko ohranite dirkaški videz in okrepite zaščito.

description.en: Unveiling Yamaha's Rear Sequential LED Blinker Set – Redefining safety and elegance on the road. Elevate your ride with a mesmerizing sequence of LEDs designed to enhance visibility and showcase your Yamaha's distinctive style. Meticulously engineered for seamless integration, these rear blinkers not only signal your every move but also make a powerful statement. Ride with confidence as the sequential LED display adds an extra layer of sophistication to your Yamaha, ensuring you leave a lasting impression wherever your journey takes you. Experience safety and style harmoniously with Yamaha's Rear Sequential LED Blinker Set.
description.sl-SI: Predstavitev Yamahinega kompleta zadnjih sekvenčnih LED utripalk - nova definicija varnosti in elegance na cesti. Svojo vožnjo povzdignite s hipnotičnim zaporedjem diod LED, zasnovanim za izboljšanje vidljivosti in predstavitev značilnega sloga vaše Yamahe. Ti zadnji utripalniki, skrbno izdelani za brezhibno integracijo, ne sporočajo le vsakega vašega koraka, temveč dajejo tudi močno izjavo. Vozite samozavestno, saj zaporedni prikaz LED dodaja vaši Yamahi dodatno plast prefinjenosti in zagotavlja, da boste pustili trajen vtis, kamorkoli vas bo pot zanesla. Doživite varnost in slog v harmoniji z Yamahinim kompletom zadnjih sekvenčnih utripalnikov LED.

Designed for long distance riding comfort with high level of protection. The set has removable thermal lining and fixed waterproof lining that give all-weather flexibility. The fabric is a mix of polyester, polyamide, polyurethane and nylon. The jacket has 6 exterior and 4 interior pockets. The pants have 2 cargo pockets. This Adventure set is built to handle the longest and toughest ride.

description.sl-SI: Ostanki prahu, umazanija in nešteto žuželk – ne samo na čeladah in vizirjih, ampak tudi na žarometih in vetrnih ščitih – so cena, ki jo plačujemo za naš užitek v vožnji. Omenjeni ostanki lahko otežijo vidljivost in predstavljajo varnostno tveganje, vendar ti priročni vlažni robčki (z vključeno krpo za poliranje) to težavo hitro rešijo – pospravite jih kar v nahrbtnik!
description.en: The residues from dust, dirt and countless insects are the penalty we pay for our riding enjoyment – and not just on our helmets and visors, but on headlights and windscreens too! This can be a visibility and safety issue, but these handy wipes (with the polishing cloth included) solve the problem quickly – so keep them in your backpack!

description.en: A must-have for Yamaha’s Sport Heritage fans, the Sports Heritage Women’s T-Shirt is a striking and cool piece of vintage-style apparel. Made from cotton and elastane with a faded look in classic burnt orange and white, this V-neck tee features Sports Heritage badges on the sleeves and a Yamaha print on the chest. A casual, easy wearing item for every day style.
description.sl-SI: Kratka majica Sports Heritage za ženske je očarljivo in odlično oblačilo v starinskem slogu, ki ga navdušenke Yamahinih vozil v segmentu Sport Heritage preprosto morajo imeti. Izdelana je iz bombaža in elastana z bledim videzom v klasični zapečeni oranžni in beli barvi, V-izrezom, oznako Sports Heritage na rokavih in potiskom Yamaha na prsih. Lahkoten izdelek za prosti čas v vsakodnevnem slogu.

description.en: Specially designed roller protection for CP3 engines. This three point stable fixation slider will limit damage done to your engine during a low sider. The protection is made from machined anodised aluminium  and features a Yamaha logo for that styling finish.
description.sl-SI: Posebej zasnovana zaščita za valjčke za motorje CP3. Ta tritočkovni stabilni pritrdilni drsnik bo omejil poškodbe motorja pri zdrsu. Ta zaščita je izdelana iz strojno obdelanega anodiziranega aluminija in ima logotip Yamaha za zagotavljanje športnega končnega videza.

description.en: Designed to be fitted while using your engine, this cover provides the ultimate protection against scratches and UV rays. The tight fit allows on and off water usage. Perfect on the waves, perfect on the trailer.
description.sl-SI: Ta prevleka je zasnovana za namestitev med uporabo vašega skuterja in zagotavlja neprekosljivo zaščito pred praskami in UV-žarki. Tesno prileganj prevleke omogoča nameščanje na vodi ali na kopnem. Odlična na valovih, odlična na prikolici.

name.sl-SI: Monster Energy® Yamaha MotoGP Team Replica Polo Moški
name.en: Monster Energy® Yamaha MotoGP Team Replica Polo Men

description.sl-SI: Replika moške polo majice ekipe Monster Energy® Yamaha MotoGP je stilski kos, ki ga nosijo dirkači po vsem svetu. Srajca je izdelana iz 100-odstotnega poliestra v dirkaški črni in modri barvi ter je oblikovana po vzoru motorja M1 in ima natisnjene logotipe Yamaha Racing, Monster Energy® in sponzorjev, stranske strani s kamuflažnim potiskom pa zagotavljajo dodatno ostrino. Ovratnik z zadrgo zagotavlja udobno prileganje.
description.en: A must-have items for race days, the Monster Energy® Yamaha MotoGP Team Men’s Replica Polo Shirt is a stylish item worn by the race ream around the world. 100% polyester in Racing Black and Blue and styled on the M1 bike, the shirt is printed with Yamaha Racing, Monster Energy® and sponsor logos, with camo print side panels for extra edge. A zip closure collar ensures a comfort fit.
Electrical heated hand grips to replace the standard unit grips
description.sl-SI: Električno ogrevane ročke, ki nadomeščajo standardne ročke

Popolnoma sintetično olje Yamalube® 15W50 za štiritaktne motorje je visoko zmogljiva rešitev za športna, cestna in terenska motorna kolesa, skuterje, ATV-je ter štirikolesnike s štiritaktnim motorjem. Odlična vsestranska zaščita ločenih in vgrajenih menjalnikov ter mokrih sklopk, tudi pri ekstremnih vrtljajih in temperaturah.
description.en: Yamalube® Fully Synthetic 15W50 4-Stroke Oil is the high-performance solution for 4-stroke sports, road and off-road motorcycles, scooters, ATVs and quads. Excellent all-round protection for separate and integrated gearboxes and wet clutches, even at extreme revs and temperatures.

description.sl-SI: Otroški dres MX, ki ga je podjetje Alpinestars posebej zasnovalo za udobje bodočih dirkačev na modelu MX, omogoča izvrstno svobodo gibanja in pokritost. Izdelan je iz 100-odstotnega poliestra, kar zagotavlja odvajanje vlage in raztegljivost, športni ovratnik pa svobodno premikanje glave. Sublimirana logotipa Yamaha in Alpinestars otrokom ponujata videz, v katerem bodo z veseljem dirkali.
description.en: Specially designed by Alpinestars to help MX riders of the future race in comfort, the MX Kid’s Jersey offers excellent freedom of movement and coverage. 100% polyester construction helps with moisture wicking and allows plenty of stretch, with a sport collar for ample head movement. Sublimated Yamaha and Alpinestars branding gives the kids a look they’ll love to race in.

name.en: Nothing but the Max T-Shirt Men
name.sl-SI: Moška majica 'Nothing but the Max' s kratkimi rokavi

description.en: Focused on its central Nothing but the Max chest logo, the design of the Nothing but the Max t-shirt for men reflects the Sport Scooter lifestyle with high quality construction. A 50/50 blend of organic cotton and viscose ensure incredible comfort for everyday wear, available in two colours for wider choice. Yamaha branding on the left shoulder highlights its premium feel and scooter spirit.
description.sl-SI: Z glavnim detajlom, napisom 'Nothing but the Max' na sprednji strani, ta majica za moške odraža športen življenjski slog voznikov skuterjev. Mešanica 50 % ekološko pridelanega bombaža in 50 % viskoze zagotavlja neverjetno udobje pri vsakodnevnem nošenju in je na voljo v dveh barvah. Yamahin logotip na levi rami poudarja vrhunsko znamko.
